<H1>
<IMG SRC="/shared/images/pp100100.jpg" ALIGN=BOTTOM > Pacific Power 
</H1>

<P></P>
<HR>
<P></P>

Pacific Power is your authoritative source for information about all forms
of <A HREF="/pacpow/docs/pow_nsw.html"> <U>electricity production in New
South Wales </U></A> and the latest innovations in solar and
<A HREF="/pacpow/docs/new_inf.html"> <U>alternative technologies</U></A> 
for electricity generation.<P>

Find out about environmental studies in Australia, and the facts related to 
modern issues such as the <A HREF="/pacpow/docs/greenhse.html">
<U>control of greenhouse gas emissions</U></A>Find out about information available
to your school on video cassette, and other <A HREF="/pacpow/docs/videos.html"><U> school project materials 
from Pacific Power.</U></A> Check out the information about tours for 
individuals and school groups to <A HREF="/pacpow/docs/tours.html" 
<U>New South Wales Power Stations. </U></A><P></P>
<P></P>
<HR>
<P></P>
<U>
<LI>For detailed information on electricity production, check out the 
following resources:
<OL>
	<LI><A HREF="/pacpow/docs/new_ch1.html"> New And Alternative Technologies Chapter 1</A>
	<LI><A HREF="/pacpow/docs/new_ch2.html"> New And Alternative Technologies Chapter 2</A> 
