<H3>MEETING THE NEW SOUTH WALES POWER DEMAND</H3>
<HR>

<P>
Pacific Power provides one of the state's most vital public services.
<P>
There would be few people who don't turn to electricity at least
sometime during a normal day.
<P>
But with a safe and reliable electricity supply now a common expectation,
few people take the time to consider just what it is we rely on
when we turn a power switch.
<P>
This booklet seeks to provide a brief overview of our electricity
supply industry, explaining what electricity is, and how it is
brought to the home and the workplace.<HR>

<H3>CONTENTS</H3>

<H4>Overview of the New South Wales power supply system</H4>

