few people take the time to consider just what it is we rely on
when we turn a power switch. This is the right place to visit for 
an overview of Pacific Power, explaining <A HREF="/pacpow/docs/ppinfo.html"> 
what electricity is, and how it is brought to the home and the workplace.</A>
