<H2>Voice of America, 96-12-20</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/usa/voa">Voice of America: Selected Articles</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-18.voa.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-22.voa.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Voice of America &lt;<A HREF="gopher://gopher.voa.gov">gopher://gopher.voa.gov</A>&gt;</H4>
