<H2>Athens News Agency: News in Greek (AM), 96-12-21</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/ape">Athens News Agency: News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-20_1.ape.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-21_1.ape.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Athens News Agency at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.forthnet.gr/ape">http://www.forthnet.gr/ape</A>&gt;</H4>
<H4>Aqhna, Ellada, 21/12/1996 (APE)</H4>
<HR>
<H3>EIDHSEIS STA ELLHNIKA</H3>
<H4>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#01">[01]</A> Titloi eidhsewn.
<LI><A HREF="#02">[02]</A> Eidhseis analytika.
<LI><A HREF="#03">[03]</A> Aqlhtikes eidhseis.
<LI><A HREF="#04">[04]</A> Times synallagmatos.
<LI><A HREF="#05">[05]</A> Kairos.
</UL>
</H4>
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</A> TITLOI EIDHSEWN</H3>
Kanonika ekteloyntai ta dromologia olwn twn ploiwn meta thn anastolh ths
apergias twn naytergatwn.
<P>Pentamelh epitroph agrotwn ths Syntonistikhs Epitrophs Makedonias -
Qrakhs qa dexqei th Deytera to apogeyma o Kwstas Shmiths.
<P>Anypoxwrhtoi oi agrotes ths Qessalias oi opoioi dhlwnoyn oti qa
parameinoyn sta odofragmata kai thn periodo twn eortwn.
<P>Synedriazei ayrio sth Rhgillhs h Ektelestikh Epitroph ths Neas
Dhmokratias.
<P>O Proedros ths Dhmokratias, Kwsths Stefanopoylos, synantatai to meshmeri
sto Kairo me ton Xosni Moymparak.
<P>Oloklhrwnetai ta mesanyxta sth Boylh me onomastikh chfoforia h syzhthsh
epi toy proypologismoy toy 1997.
<P>Me ton agwna Janqhs - Panaqhnaikoy anoigei to apogeyma h aylaia ths
agwnistikhs gia to prwtaqlhma ths A eqnikhs kathgorias.
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</A> EIDHSEIS ANALYTIKA</H3>
Kanonika ekteloyntai ta dromologia olwn twn ploiwn meta thn anastolh twn
kinhtopoihsewn twn naytergatwn. H Panellhnia Naytikh Omospondia anakoinwse
oti o klados qa epanalabei tis kinhtopoihseis meta tis 7 Ianoyarioy an h
kybernhsh den ylopoihsei th desmeysh ths sxetika me tis foroapallages twn
naytikwn. Hdh apo xqes to brady sta limania ths xwras, arxisan na
diakinoyntai ekatontades forthga aytokinhta kai xiliades epibates, poy
eixan egklwbistei logw ths apergias twn naytikwn.
<P>Pentamelh epitroph agrotwn ts Syntonistikhs Epitrophs ths Makedonias kai
ths Qrakhs qa dexqei th Deytera to apogeyma o Prwqypoyrgos, Kwstas Shmiths.
H synanthsh ayth entassetai sto plaisio enos eyryteroy dialogoy gia ta
problhmata ths gewrgias. Sto metajy, anypoxwrhtoi emfanizontai oi agrotes
ths Qessalias oi opoioi dhlwnoyn oti qa parameinoyn sta odofragmata kai thn
periodo twn eortwn.
<P>Synedriazei ayrio sth Rhgillhs h Ektelestikh Epitroph ths Neas
Dhmokratias kai qa asxolhqei me tis diadikasies diejagwghs toy synedrioy.
Plhrofories anaferoyn oti o k. Ebert qa epiferei mikres allages stis
protaseis Barbitsiwth.
<P>O Proedros ths Dhmokratias, Kwsths Stefanopoylos, synantatai stis 12 to
meshmeri sto Kairo me ton Aigyptio omologo toy, Xosni Moymparak. Epikentro
twn synomiliwn anamenetai na einai oi dimereis sxeseis kai oi ejelijeis
sthn perioxh ths notioanatolikhs Mesogeioy. Symfwna me plhrofories, toso o
k. Stefanopoylos, oso kai o ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn, Qeodwros Pagkalos, stis
synomilies me toys Aigyptioys omologoys, qa toys enhmerwsoyn gia ta eqnika
mas qemata, to Kypriako kai tis ellhnotoyrkikes sxeseis.
<P>Oloklhrwnetai ta mesanyxta sth Boylh me onomastikh chfoforia h syzhthsh
epi toy proypologismoy toy 1997. Sthn apogeymatinh synedriash anamenetai na
laboyn to logo o Prwqypoyrgos, Kwstas Shmiths kai arxhgoi twn kommatwn ths
antipoliteyshs.
<A NAME="sports"></A><H3><A NAME="03">[03]</A> AQLHTIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
Me ton agwna Janqhs - Panaqhnaikoy anoigei to apogeyma h aylaia ths
agwnistikhs gia to prwtaqlhma ths A eqnikhs kathgorias. To paixnidi qa
metadoqei stis 3 apo to syndromhtiko kanali Soyper - Spor. Sto metajy, o
Entoyarnt Iorntaneskoy ths Steaoya, feretai ws o jenos paikths, poy qa
antikatasthsei ton Xoyan Xose Mporeli. Pantws kykloi twn ``prasinwn``
tonisan oti den yfistantai pros to paron qema metagrafhs toy 17xronoy mesoy
ths Steaoya.
<P>Kanonika qa diejaxqei ayrio to brady sto Stadio Karaiskakh to paixnidi
gia to prwtaqlhma metajy Olympiakoy kai PAOK, afoy oi ergazomenoi sthn EOA
anesteilan tis kinhtopoihseis toys.
<H3><A NAME="04">[04]</A> TIMES SYNALLAGMATOS</H3>
Oi epishmes times pwlhshs twn jenwn nomismatwn,poy dinei h Trapeza ths
Ellados einai: dolario HPA pros 250,29 draxmes, lira Agglias pros 417,73,
lira Kyproy pros 529,05, galliko fragko pros 47,66, elbetiko fragko pros
187,54, germaniko marko pros 161,05,tis ekato italikes liretes pros 16,39,
ta ekato gien Iapwnias pros 219,41 kai thn ECU pros 309,72 draxmes.
<H3><A NAME="05">[05]</A> KAIROS</H3>
H baqmiaia epikrathsh boreiodytikwn anemwn kai oi topikes proskaires
broxes qa einai ta kyria xarakthristika toy shmerinoy kairoy. Se olh th
xwra arxika problepontai nefwseis me broxes, enw argotera o kairos qa
beltiwqei. H qermokrasia qa kymanqei sta hpeirwtika kai to Ionio apo 6 ews
18 baqmoys kai sta nhsia toy Aigaioy apo 14 ews 19 baqmoys Kelsioy. Sthn
Attikh gia shmera problepontai nefwseis me piqanh broxh. H qermokrasia sthn
Aqhna qa kymanqei apo 12 ews 17 baqmoys Kelsioy. Gia th Qessalonikh
problepontai nefwses me topikh broxh, enw h qermokrasia qa kymanqei apo 8
ews 14 baqmoys Kelsioy.
<P>(P.D.)
