<TITLE>Athens News Agency: News in Greek (PM), 96-12-20</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<center><a href="/info"><IMG SRC="/gifs/hrnet.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="[HR-Net Banner]"></a><BR></center>

<H2>Athens News Agency: News in Greek (PM), 96-12-20</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/ape">Athens News Agency: News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-20.ape.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-21.ape.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Athens News Agency at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.forthnet.gr/ape">http://www.forthnet.gr/ape</A>&gt;</H4>
<H4>Aqhna, Ellada, 20/12/1996 (APE)</H4>
<HR>
<H3>EIDHSEIS STA ELLHNIKA</H3>
<H4>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#01">[01]</A> Titloi eidhsewn.
<LI><A HREF="#02">[02]</A> Eidhseis analytika.
<LI><A HREF="#03">[03]</A> Aqlhtikes eidhseis.
<LI><A HREF="#04">[04]</A> Times synallagmatos.
<LI><A HREF="#05">[05]</A> Kairos.
</UL>
</H4>
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</A> TITLOI EIDHSEWN</H3>
Na parameinoyn sta mploka apofasisan oi agrotes ths Qessalias. Anesteilan
tis kinhtopoihseis oi synadelfoi toys ths Makedonias kai Qrakhs. Sthn idia
kateyqynsh kai oi agrotes ths Peloponhsoy.
<P>Lynoyn ta ploia, anastelloyn tis kinhtopoihseis toys oi naytikoi meta th
qetikh synanthsh me toys armodioys ypoyrgoys.
<P>Metra gia thn prostasia twn katanalwtwn apo toys foyskwmenoys
logariasmoys ths EYDAP ejhggeile h kybernhsh.
<P>Neo xastoyki ths Tansoy Tsiler apo th Mosxa. Den katafere na apotrecei
thn pwlhsh oplikwn systhmatwn sthn Kypro.
<P>Thn Kyriakh epi taphtos sthn Ektelestikh Epitroph ths Neas Dhmokratias oi
diadikasies gia ton tropo diejagwghs toy synedrioy.
<P>Dyo nekroi kai dyo traymaties se sygkroysh trenoy me IX aytokinhto sthn
Pella.
<P>Sthn Aigypto o proedros ths Dhmokratias gia tetrahmerh epishmh
episkech.
<P>To xrisma twn efedrwn ajiwmatikwn twn Enoplwn Dynamewn phran shmera oi
Olympionikes mas ths Atlanta.
<P>Arsh toy trapezikoy aporrhtoy ths Ellhs Stah, zhta h ejetastikh epitroph
ths boylhs.
<P>Beltiwsh apo ta dytika qa paroysiasei ayrio o kairos. Metrioi oi anemoi,
to qermometro qa deijei apo 6 mexri 19 baqmoys.
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</A> EIDHSEIS ANALYTIKA</H3>
Th synexish twn kinhtopoihsewn toys apofasisan omofwna oi qessaloi
agrotes,xwris mexri stigmhs na ginei gnwsto, ean qa epitrecoyn toys
ekdromeis na perasoyn, enocei twn Xristoygennwn.Antiqeta,oi agrotes ths
Makedonias kai Qrakhs apofasisan thn anastolh twn kinhtopoihsewn kai
zhthsan synanthsh me ton prwqypoyrgo.Analogo klima epikratei kai sthn
Peloponnhso.Hdh anoije to mploko sth syragga Artemisioy kai thn idia stash
anamenetai na thrhsoyn oi agrotes toy Aigioy.
<P>Qetikes einai oi ejelijeis sto metwpo twn kinhtopoihsewn twn naytikwn,
meta tis qetikes apanthseis sta aithmata toys,poy elaban apo toys ypoyrgoys
kyrioys Soymakh kai Dry.H omospondia twn naytikwn apofasizei thn anastolh
twn kinhtopoihsewn.Shmera ta ploia paremeinan demena sta limania,enw den
eleican ta mikroepeisodia sto limani ths Hgoymenitsas.
<P>Tria metra gia thn prostasia twn katanwlwn ths EYDAP,anakoinwse o
yfypoyrgos PEXWDE Xrhstos Berelhs.Sygkekrimena, sygkrotoyntai oligomelh
synergeia ths EYDAP,gia thn ayqhmeron ejyphrethsh twn katanalwtwn,enw qa
pernoyn apo to mikroskopio twn ypologistwn oi foyskwmenoi logariasmoi kai
prin thn ekdosh toys, qa eidopoieitai o katanalwths.
<P>Sto Kairo gia tetrahmerh epishmh episkech,brisketai o proedros ths
Dhmokratias, Kwsths Stefanopoylos,synodeyomenos apo ton ypoyrgo Ejwterikwn,
Qeodwro Pagkalo. Se mhnyma toy, pros toys apodhmoys, enocei twn eortwn,
tonizei pws o xronos poy perase afhnei se problhmatikh ekkremothta ta
eqnika mas qemata, an kai kateblhqhsan ikanes prospaqeies kai shmeiwqhkan
bhmata qetikhs antimetwpishs toys. O k.Stefanopoylos ejairei th
drasthriopoihsh twn apodhmwn gia thn prowqhsh twn eqnikwn mas qematwn kai
synista omocyxia, egrhgorsh kai synergasia olwn gia na dikaiwqoyn oi
prosdokies mas.
<P>Me patagwdh apotyxia stefqhke h prospaqeia ths Tansoy Tsiler na apotrecei
thn pwlhsh toy pyraylikoy systhmatos S-300, apo th Rwsia sthn Kypro.H
rwsikh kybernhsh dieceyse kathgorhmatika tis dhlwseis ths kyrias Tsiler,
oti phre sxetikh diabebaiwsh apo ton prwqypoyrgo ths Rwsias, Biktor
Tsernomirntin.
<P>Synedriazei thn Kyriakh h Ektelestikh Epitroph ths Neas Dhmokratias gia
na syzhthsei tis protaseis sxetika me ton tropo diejagwghs toy synedrioy. O
k. Ebert feretai apofasismenos na thrhsei sklhrh stash apenanti stoys
eswkommatikoys toy antipaloys,enw o Giwrgos Soyflias me epistolh sta melh
toy Politikoy symboylioy, toys kalei na analaboyn tis eyqynes toys gia
antiproswpeytiko synedrio.
<P>Frikto qanato brhkan o 48xronos Xaralampos Ermidhs kai h peqera toy,
Elpida Aqanasakh, otan to aytokinhto sto opoio epebainan, parasyrqhke apo
amajostoixia toy OSE,sthn perioxh ths Pellas.Sobara traymatisqhkan h
syzygos toy Kwnstantina kai o 14xronos gios toy Alejandros.
<P>Thn arsh toy trapezikoy kai forologikoy aporrhtoy ths dhmosiografoy Ellhs
Stah,zhta h ejetastikh epitroph ths Boylhs, poy diereyna thn ypoqesh toy
kazino sto Floisbo,meta thn arnhsh ths na dwsei dieykriniseis gia ta
perioysiaka ths stoixeia.
<P>To xrisma toy efedroy ajiwmatikoy twn triwn oplwn twn Enoplwn Dynamewn,
phran oi Olympianikes mas ths Atlanta, Nikos Kaklamanakhs, Akakios
Kaxiasbili, Iwannhs Melissanidhs,Nikh Mpakogiannh,Lewnidas Kokkas,Balerios
Lewnidhs kai Pyros Dhmas.
<A NAME="sports"></A><H3><A NAME="03">[03]</A> AQLHTIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
O Entoyarnt Iorntaneskoy,gios toy Roymanoy omospondiakoy proponhth Anxel,
einai o jenos paikths poy qa antikatasthsei ton Argentino Xoyan-Xose
Mporeli ston Panaqhnaiko,symfwna me thlegrafhma toy Gallikoy praktoreioy
eidhsewn. H symfwnia anamesa stis dyo pleyres ekleise prin dyo peripoy
mhnes, kata thn diarkeia ths synanthshs poy eixan o Anxel Iorntaneskoy me
ton proedro ths PAE Panaqhnaikos Giwrgo Bardinogiannh,o opoios eixe
proteinei parallhla ston Roymano proponhth na analabei thn texnikh hgesia
twn prasinwn,alla o Iorntaneskoy protimhse na krathsei to posto toy
omospondiakoy proponhth. Opws anaferetai sto thlegrafhma toy Gallikoy
Praktoreioy, o Entoyarnt Iorntaneskoy prokeitai na ypogracei syntoma
symbolaio ston Panaqhnaiko.
<H3><A NAME="04">[04]</A> TIMES SYNALLAGMATOS</H3>
Oi epishmes times pwlhshs twn jenwn nomismatwn,poy dinei h Trapeza ths
Ellados einai: dolario HPA pros 250,29 draxmes, lira Agglias pros 417,73,
lira Kyproy pros 529,05, galliko fragko pros 47,66, elbetiko fragko pros
187,54, germaniko marko pros 161,05,tis ekato italikes liretes pros 16,39,
ta ekato gien Iapwnias pros 219,41 kai thn ECU pros 309,72 draxmes.
<H3><A NAME="05">[05]</A> KAIROS</H3>
Sto Aigaio qa periorisqoyn ayrio oi broxes kai oi sporadikes kataigides,
grhgora omws o kairos qa beltiwqei apo ta dytika pros ta anatolika. Oi
anemoi qa einai notioi metrioi kai topika sto Aigaio isxyroi, stadiaka omws
apo ta dytika qa strafoyn se boreiodytikoys kai qa ejasqenhsoyn. H
qermokrasia sta boreia qa kymanqei 6 me 14 baqmoys, sto Ionio kai ta
ypoloipa hpeirwtika 8 me 18 kai sto Aigaio 13 me 19 baqmoys Kelsioy. Arxika
nefwseis me topikh broxh, alla grhgorh beltiwsh, metrioys anemoys kai
qermokrasia 10 me 16 kai 6 me 13 antistoixa, qa exoyn ayrio Aqhna kai
Qessalonikh.
<P>(M.M.)
<HR>
