<HEAD>
<TITLE>Athens News Agency: News in Greek (PM), 96-12-21</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<center><a href="/info"><IMG SRC="/gifs/hrnet.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="[HR-Net Banner]"></a><BR></center>

<H2>Athens News Agency: News in Greek (PM), 96-12-21</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/ape">Athens News Agency: News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-21.ape.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-22.ape.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Athens News Agency at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.forthnet.gr/ape">http://www.forthnet.gr/ape</A>&gt;</H4>
<H4>AQHNA,Ellada,21/12/1996 (APE)</H4>
<HR>
<H3>EIDHSEIS STA ELLHNIKA</H3>
<H4>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#01">[01]</A> Titloi eidhsewn.
<LI><A HREF="#02">[02]</A> Eidhseis analytika.
<LI><A HREF="#03">[03]</A> Aqlhtikes eidhseis.
<LI><A HREF="#04">[04]</A> Times synallagmatos.
<LI><A HREF="#05">[05]</A> Kairos.
</UL>
</H4>
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</A> TITLOI EIDHSEWN</H3>
Apoce apofasizoyn oi agrotes ths Qessalias an qa epimeinoyn h oxi stis
kinhtopoihseis toys.
<P>Anoigei o dialogos gia to agrotiko. Th Deytera o prwqypoyrgos blepei toys
agrotes ths Makedonias, PASEGES ,GESASE kai SYDASE.
<P>Synwstismos sta limania. Kanonika ekteloyntai ta dromologia twn
ploiwn.
<P>Ta mesanyxta h chfish toy pio sklhroy proypologismoy.
<P>Ises apostaseis apo Aqhna kai Agkyra, thrhse o Aigyptios Proedros, kata
th synanthsh toy me ton k. Stefanopoylo.
<P>To Synedrio ths Neas Dhmokratias, epi taphtos ayrio sthn Ektelestikh
Epitroph.
<P>Me 3-1 nikhse o Panaqhnaikos sthn Janqh thn topikh omada.
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</A> EIDHSEIS ANALYTIKA</H3>
Se nea synedriash poy pragmatopoieitai ayth thn wra sth Larisa, h
Panqessalikh Syntonistikh Syntonistikh Epitroph agrotwn,anamenetai na
apofasisei thn peraiterw poreia twn kinhtopoihsewn. Symfwna me plhrofories
h tash poy epikratei einai na epitrapei h dieleysh twn IX aytokinhtwn me
toys ekdromeis twn Xristoygennwn, oxi omws kai twn forthgwn aytokinhtwn.Oi
agrotes toy Aigioy apofasisan to apogeyma thn anastolh twn kinhtoopoihsewn
toys kai apoxwrhsan apo ta mploka.
<P>Thn idia wra h kybernhsh anoigei dialogo me toys agrotes,arxhs genomenhs
me tis syndikalistikes agrotikes organwseis.Etsi o prwqypoyrgos qa
synanthqei th Deytera stis 2:30 to meshmeri me ta proedreia PASEGES,GESASE
kai SYDASE kai stis 6 to apogeyma qa dei toys agrotes ths Makedonias kai
Qrakhs,poy anesteilan tis kinhtopoihseis toys.Sklhrh glwssa stoys agrotes
ths qessalias, xrhsimopoihse o ypoyrgos Dikaiosynhs Eyaggelos Giannopoylos,
tonizontas oti h kybernhsh den prokeitai na kanei pisw kai an qeloyn
sygkroysh qa prepei na analaboyn tis eyqynes toys. O k. Giannopoylos
aphyqyne ekklhsh sto kratos twn tempwn,opws eipe, na anoijoyn toys
dromoys.
<P>Synwstismos epikratei apo to prwi sta limania olhs ths xwras, kaqws meta
th lhjh twn kinhtopoihsewn twn naytikwn,parathreitai megalh kinhsh,kyriws
apo forthga poy metaferoyn agrotika proionta,apo kai pros ta nhsia.Gia thn
kalyterh ejyphrethsh toy epibatikoy koinoy, ektelesqhkan kai ektakta
dromologia,enw analoga metra phre kai h Olympiakh ejaitias ths ayjhmenhs
epibatikhs kinhshs.
<P>Me thn onomastikh chfoforia, poy qa diejaxqei ligo meta ta mesanyxta,
oloklhrwnetai h penqhmerh syzhthsh epi toy proypologismoy. H apogeymatinh
synedriash arxise me omilia toy prwqypoyrgoy, qa akoloyqhsoyn oi
topoqethseis twn politikwn arxhgwn kai h syzhthsh qa oloklhrwqei me th
deyterologia toy k.Shmith. H genikh grammateas toy KKE Aleka Paparhga
xarakthrise ton proypologismo qatserikoy typoy, enw o Dhmhtrhs Tsobolas
ekane logo gia proypologismo ftwxeias. Sthn prwinh synedriash o k.
Gerasimos Arsenhs tonise thn anagkh enos olilhrwmenoy programmatos me
safeis kai ejeidikeymenoys stoxoys, poy na prowqei tis oikonomikes
koinwnikes kai anaptyjiakes epiloges. O yfypoyrgos Oikonomikwn Giwrgos Drys
afhse anoixto to endexomeno timariqmopoihshs ths forologikhs klimakas gia
to 1997, enw o Kwstas Geitonas shmeiwse oti h kybernhsh prowqei thn
koinwnikh politikh.
<P>Ises apostaseis apo Aqhna kai Agkyra,thrhse o proedros ths Aigyptoy Xosni
Moymparak, kata th synanthsh poy eixe me ton Proedro ths Dhmokratias Kwsth
Stefanopoylo. O k. Moymparak diatypwse thn eyxh na ejomalynqoyn oi
ellhnotoyrkikes sxeseis kai proqymopoihqhke na analabei mesolabhtiko rolo,
efoson toy zhthqei. Oi dyo proedroi ektos apo tis ellhnotoyrkikes sxeseis
syzhthsan qemata poy aforoyn to Kypriako, to Mesanatoliko, kaqws kai tis
dimereis sxeseis. Parallhla me tis synomilies Stefanopoyloy kai Moymparak,
diejhxqhsan kai oi synomilies twn ypoyrgwn twn dyo xwrwn twn kyriwn
Pagkaloy kai Moysa, opoy h syzhthsh peristrafhke gyrw apo to
Mesanatoliko.
<P>To synedrio ths Neas Dhmokratias, anamenetai na prokalesei neo kyklo
eswkommatikhs antiparaqeshs, kaqws ayrio sthn Ektelestikh Epitroph, poy
sygkalese o k. Ebert, qa syzhthqoyn oi oroi diejagwghs toy synedrioy. H
eswkommatikh antipoliteysh, antedrase, ektimwntas oti oi diadikasies toy
synedrioy qa prepei na syzhthqoyn kai pali sto politiko symboylio toy
kommatos, ypo dieyrymenh synqesh. Sto metajy 21 prwhn boyleytes ths Neas
Dhmokratias, metajy aytwn oi kyrioi Koybelas, Xatzhgakhs, Anagnwstopoylos
kai alloi, me koinh epistolh toys zhtoyn th diejagwgh enos timioy kai
antiproswpeytikoy synedrioy.
<P>Anoixta apo tis 10.30 to prwi mexri tis 5 to apogeyma qa parameinoyn
ayrio ta emporika katasthmata kai ta kreopwleia.
<A NAME="sports"></A><H3><A NAME="03">[03]</A> AQLHTIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
O Panaqhnaikos se agwna ths 13hs hmeras gia to prwtaqlhma ths prwths
eqnikhs,poy egine sthn Janqh, nikhse 3-1 thn topikh omada. Ta termata twn
nikhtwn petyxan o Nikos Lymperopoylos sto 55`, o Kristof Bazexa sto 84` kai
o Giwrgos Nasiopoylos sto tetarto lepto twn kaqysterhsewn (94`), enw dyo
lepta nwritera (92`) h Janqh eixe shmeiwsei to monadiko ths gkol me ton
Xaralampo Zekeridh.Ayrio qa ginoyn ta paixnidia Olympiakoy-PAOK, Aqhnaikoy -
Kalamatas, Panaxaikhs - Hraklh, Edessaikoy - OFH, Kabalas - Iwnikoy kai Arh
- Kastorias. To programma qa oloklhrwqei th Deytera me thn anametrhsh
Panhleiakoy - Apollwna.
<P>Stoys agwnes ths 12hs agwnistikhs toy prwtaqlhmatos ths A1 sto mpasket
shmeiwqhkan ta ejhs apotelesmata: Peristeri-Apollwnas Patrwn 97-79, PAOK -
Papagoy 68-52, Larisa - Arhs 55-73,Paniwnios-BAO 104-46 Ayth thn wra
brisketai se ejelijh to mats Hraklh - Panaqhnaikoy kai Peiraikoy-
Olympiakoy.Telos, ayrio stis 6.30 o Peiraikos qa ypodexqei sto Papastrateio
ton Olympiako.
<H3><A NAME="04">[04]</A> TIMES SYNALLAGMATOS</H3>
Oi epishmes times pwlhshs twn jenwn nomismatwn,poy dinei h Trapeza ths
Ellados einai: dolario HPA pros 250,29 draxmes, lira Agglias pros 417,73,
lira Kyproy pros 529,05, galliko fragko pros 47,66, elbetiko fragko pros
187,54, germaniko marko pros 161,05,tis ekato italikes liretes pros 16,39,
ta ekato gien Iapwnias pros 219,41 kai thn ECU pros 309,72 draxmes.
<H3><A NAME="05">[05]</A> KAIROS</H3>
Sxedon aiqrios qa einai ayrio o kairos se oloklhrh th xwra kai mono sta
dytika to apogeyma qa synefiasei. Oi anemoi qa einai dytikoi asqeneis mexri
metrioi kai h qermokrasia sta boreia qa kymanqei 5 me 16 baqmoys, sto Ionio
kai ta ypoloipa hpeirwtika 8 me 19 kai sto Aigaio 12 me 20. Sxedon aiqrio
kairo, asqeneis anemoys kai qermokrasia 11 me 18 kai 6 me 15 antistoixa qa
exoyn ayrio Aqhna kai Qessalonikh.
<P>(D.K.)
<HR>
