<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Athens News Agency: News in Greek (AM), 96-12-20</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<center><a href="/info"><IMG SRC="/gifs/hrnet.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="[HR-Net Banner]"></a><BR></center>

<H2>Athens News Agency: News in Greek (AM), 96-12-20</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/ape">Athens News Agency: News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-19_1.ape.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-20_1.ape.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Athens News Agency at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.forthnet.gr/ape">http://www.forthnet.gr/ape</A>&gt;</H4>
<H4>Aqhna, Ellada, 20/12/1996 (APE)</H4>
<HR>
<H3>EIDHSEIS STA ELLHNIKA</H3>
<H4>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#01">[01]</A> Titloi eidhsewn.
<LI><A HREF="#02">[02]</A> Eidhseis analytika.
<LI><A HREF="#03">[03]</A> Aqlhtikes eidhseis.
<LI><A HREF="#04">[04]</A> Times synallagmatos.
<LI><A HREF="#05">[05]</A> Kairos.
</UL>
</H4>
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</A> TITLOI EIDHSEWN</H3>
Klimakwnoyn tis kinhtopoihseis toys oi agrotes ths Qessalias.
<P>Antiparaqesh Prwqypoyrgoy kai arxhgoy ths ajiwmatikhs antipoliteyshs gia
tis agrotikes kinhtopoihseis.
<P>Apergoyn gia 24 akomh wres oi naytergates.
<P>Sthn Aigypto apo shmera o Proedros ths Dhmokratias gia tetrahmerh epishmh
episkech.
<P>Kamia organwsh den anelabe thn eyqynh gia th bombistikh energeia sth Siti
Mpank toy Xalandrioy.
<P>Thn arsh toy trapezikoy kai forologikoy aporrhtoy ths Ellhs Stah zhthse h
Ejetastikh Epitroph ths Boylhs.
<P>Ektos agwnistikhs o Tzortzebits gia tesseris mhnes.
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</A> EIDHSEIS ANALYTIKA</H3>
Klimakwsh twn kinhtopoihsewn apofasise xqes to apogeyma h Syntonistikh
Epitroph Agwna agrotwn meta thn akarph synanthsh, poy eixe sthn Aqhna me
kybernhtiko klimakio. H morfh twn kinhtopoihsewn qa apofasisqei shmera se
syskech ths Panqessalikhs Epitrophs,sth Larisa. O ypoyrgos Gewrgias,
Stefanos Tzoymakas kalese toys agrotes na anoijoyn toys dromoys kai qa
synanthqoyn amesws me ton Prwqypoyrgo, Kwsta Shmith, gia qesmiko dialogo
ston agrotiko tomea.
<P>Ojeia antiparaqesh metajy toy Prwqypoyrgoy kai toy arxhgoy ths
ajiwmatikhs antipoliteyshs, proklhqhke xqes sth Boylh, gia to agrotiko.
Aformh apotelesan xarakthrismoi toy k. Ebert gia thn omilia toy ypoyrgoy
Gewrgias, Stefanoy Tzoymaka, o opoios tonise oti h kybernhsh den eixe kai
den exei alles dynatothtes gia na ikanopoihsei ola ta aithmata twn
agrotwn.
<P>Demena sta limania qa einai ta karabia mexri ayrio to prwi stis 6, meta
thn apofash ths Panellhnias Naytikhs Omospondias gia synexish twn
kinhtopoihsewn.H omospondia, exei programmatisei gia tis 11 panaytiko
syllalhthrio ston Peiraia.
<P>Anaxwrei to prwi gia thn Aigypto, opoy qa pragmatopoihsei tetrahmerh
epishmh episkech o Proedros ths Dhmokratias, Kwsths Stefanopoylos. Ayrio to
meshmeri o k. Stefanopoylos qa exei synomilies me ton Aigyptio omologo toy,
Xonsi Moymparak, sthn opoia qa syzhthqoyn oi ejelijeis sto Mesanatoliko kai
qa ton enhmerwsei kai gia ta eqnika mas qemata.
<P>Kamia organwsh den exei analabei mexri stigmhs thn eyqynh gia th
bombistikh epiqesh to brady ths Tetarths, apo thn opoia katestrafh to
ypokatasthma ths trapezas Siti Mpank toy Xalandrioy kai proklhqhkan
ektetamenes zhmies sta gyrw katasthmata.Symfwna me ektimhseis ths
astynomias drastes prepei na einai melh ths ``17 Noembrh``.
<P>Th dikastikh syndromh gia thn arsh toy trapezikoy kai toy forologikoy
aporrhtoy ths dhmosiografoy Ellhs Stah apofasise na zhthsei h ejetastikh
epitroph ths Boylhs. H epitroph apofasise epishs na kalesei gia nea
kataqesh ton antiproedro toy Areioy Pagoy Eyaggelo Riko kai ton nomiko
symboylo toy kratoys Hlia Papadopoylo.
<A NAME="sports"></A><H3><A NAME="03">[03]</A> AQLHTIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
Arnhqhke oti dwrodokhse diaithtes o proedros ths omadas twn Lykwn, Kwstas
Hliadhs, o opoios kateqese sthn ejetastikh epitroph ths EPO sxetika me to
skandalo twn sthmenwn agwnwn sthn D' eqnikh.Sthn epitroph kateqese kai o
diaithths Hlias Ntaflos, o opoios epishs arnhqhke oti dexqhke protash apo
ton syndesmo Peiraia na moirazontai xrhmata apo agwnes poy qa ton orizan na
dieyqynei.
<P>Poly megalyteros ap' oti arxika eixe ektimhqei, einai telika o
traymatismos toy Serboy mesoepiqetikoy toy Olympiakoy, Prentragk
Tzortzebits. O Tzortzebits qa meinei ektos agwnistikhs drashs gia tesseris
peripoy mhnes, afoy meta ton traymatismo toy sthn Beroia, ypesth rhjh
prosqioy xiastoy kai rhjh ejw mhniskoy.
<H3><A NAME="04">[04]</A> TIMES SYNALLAGMATOS</H3>
Oi epishmes times pwlhshs twn jenwn nomismatwn,poy dinei h Trapeza ths
Ellados einai: dolario HPA pros 249,88 draxmes, lira Agglias pros 417,65,
lira Kyproy pros 529,88, galliko fragko pros 47,53, elbetiko fragko pros
187,29, germaniko marko pros 160,63,tis ekato italikes liretes pros 16,33,
ta ekato gien Iapwnias pros 219,19 kai thn ECU pros 309,06 draxmes.
<H3><A NAME="05">[05]</A> KAIROS</H3>
Nefwseis me topikes broxes kai kataigides qa shmeiwqoyn shmera apo ta
dytika kai syntoma qa epektaqoyn sta ypoloipa hpeirwtika kai to boreio
Aigaio. Oi anemoi qa pneoyn notiodytikoi asqeneis mexri metrioi kai
argotera sta dytika isxyroi. H qermokrasia sta boreia qa kymanqei apo 5 ews
14 baqmoys, sto Ionio kai ta ypoloipa hpeirwtika apo 8 ews 18 kai sto
Aigaio apo 13 ews 19 baqmoys Kelsioy. Nefwseis me piqanh broxh to brady,
asqeneis mexri metrioys anemoys kai qermokrasia poy qa kymanqei apo 10 ews
16 kai apo 6 ews 13 baqmoys Kelsioy antistoixa, qa exoyn Aqhna kai
Qessalonikh.
<P>(P.D.)
<HR>
