<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Athens News Agency: News in Greek (AM), 96-12-19</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<center><a href="/info"><IMG SRC="/gifs/hrnet.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="[HR-Net Banner]"></a><BR></center>

<H2>Athens News Agency: News in Greek (AM), 96-12-19</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/ape">Athens News Agency: News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-18_1.ape.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-19_1.ape.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Athens News Agency at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.forthnet.gr/ape">http://www.forthnet.gr/ape</A>&gt;</H4>
<H4>Aqhna, Ellada, 19/12/1996 (APE)</H4>
<HR>
<H3>EIDHSEIS STA ELLHNIKA</H3>
<H4>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#01">[01]</A> Titloi eidhsewn.
<LI><A HREF="#02">[02]</A> Eidhseis analytika.
<LI><A HREF="#03">[03]</A> Aqlhtikes eidhseis.
<LI><A HREF="#04">[04]</A> Times synallagmatos.
<LI><A HREF="#05">[05]</A> Kairos.
</UL>
</H4>
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</A> TITLOI EIDHSEWN</H3>
Sobares zhmies apo ekrhjh aytosxedioy ekrhktikoy mhxanismoy ta mesanyxta
se ypokatasthma ths Siti Mpank sto Xalandri.
<P>Syllalhthrio twn agrotwn Qessalias sthn Aqhna. Pros ektonwsh oi
kinhtopoihseis toys sth Makedonia kai ston Ebro.
<P>Realistiko xarakthrizei ton proypologismo o ypoyrgos Eqnikhs
Oikonomias.
<P>Tetrahmerh epishmh episkech Stefanopoyloy apo ayrio sthn Aigypto.
<P>Anoije xqes h xwmaterh twn Anw Liosiwn.
<P>Aneth nikh me 73-51 petyxe h eqnikh mas omada mpasket epi ths antistoixhs
ths Bosnias gia ta prokrimatika toy Eyrwmpasket 1997.
<P>Kekleismenwn twn qyrwn qa diejaxqei sthn Aqhna stis 7 Ianoyarioy h
epanalhch toy agwna Arh- Mpesiktas ystera apo apofash ths FIMPA.
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</A> EIDHSEIS ANALYTIKA</H3>
Sobares zhmies xwris eytyxws na yparjoyn anqrwpina qymata proklhqhkan apo
isxyrotath ekrhjh aytosxedioy ekrhktikoy mhxanismoy, poy eixan topoqethsei
katw apo to mhxanhma aytomaths analhchs xrhmatwn, shmeiwqhke 20 lepta meta
ta mesanyxta sto ypokatasthma ths Siti Mpank sthn odo Kwsta Barnalh, sto
Xalandri. Apo thn ekrhjh katastrafhke olosxerws to ypokatasthma, enw zhmies
apo to wstiko kyma epaqan ta gyrw katasthmata kai mikroteres zhmies
dyo aytokinhta. Mexri stigmhs kamia organwsh den exei analabei
epishma thn eyqynh gia thn ekrhjh.
<P>Syllalhthrio exoyn programmatisei gia shmera sthn Aqhna oi agrotes ths
Qessalias se mia ystath prospaqeia na diadhlwsoyn ta aithmata toys kai na
epidiwjoyn synanthsh me ton Prwqypoyrgo, Kwsta Shmith. Oi agrotes, to
meshmeri qa sygkentrwqoyn sthn plateia Baqhs, ap' opoy qa pragmatopoihsoyn
poreia pros th Boylh kai sto Megaro Majimoy.Pros ektonwsh bainoyn oi
agrotikes kinhtopoihseis, enw apokleismenoi paramenoyn eqnikoi komboi sth
Qessalia kai sto Aigio.
<P>Realistiko kai ektelesimo xarakthrise ton proypologismo o ypoyrgos
Eqnikhs Oikonomias kai Oikonomikwn, Giannos Papantwnioy, sth diarkeia ths
xqesinhs syzhthshs sth Boylh.Thn idia wra oi naytikoi epimenoyn stis
kinhtopoihseis toys, enw mikroepeisodia shmeiwqhkan xqes sthn Hgoymenitsa
kai ston Peiraia. Oi ergazomenoi sthn politikh aeroporia ejhggeilan gia
ayrio Paraskeyh 24wrh apergia.
<P>Tetrahmerh epishmh episkech sthn Aigypto qa pragmatopoihsei apo ayrio o
Proedros ths Dhmokratias Kwsths Stefanopoylos ystera apo prosklhsh toy
Proedroy Xosni Moymparak.Oi k.k.Stefanopoylos kai Moymparak qa exoyn
idiaiteres synomilies to Sabbato, sthn aigyptiakh prwteyoysa, poy qa
epikentrwqoyn toso stis dimereis sxeseis Aqhnwn- Kairoy, oso kai sta dieqnh
problhmata.
<P>Anoije xqes kai leitoyrgei kanonika h xwmaterh Anw Liosiwn. To dhmotiko
symboylio apofasise na anasteilei gia ena mhna to kleisimo logw toy
eortasmoy twn Xristoygennwn. Elhfqhsan epishs ypoch oi dhlwseis toy
prwqypoyrgoy oti oi nees xwmateres den qa ginoyn sth Dytikh Attikh.
<P>Qeamatikh meiwsh paroysiazoyn apo ta mesanyxta oi times twn ygrwn
kaysimwn. H benzinh pwleitai fqhnotera kata 2,80 drx. to litro, to ntizel
kinhshs kata 2,20 drx kai to ntizel qermanshs kata 2,70 drx. to
litro.
<A NAME="sports"></A><H3><A NAME="03">[03]</A> AQLHTIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
Aneth nikh me 73-51 epi ths antistoixhs ths Bosnias petyxe h eqnikh mas
omada mpasket andrwn gia ta prokrimatika toy Eyrwmpasket '97.H Ellhnikh
omada eixe hdh ejasfalisei thn prokrish ths sta telika ths diorganwshs, poy
qa diejaxqoyn sthn Ispania. Synolika kai me th xqesinh exei 7 nikes se 8
agwnes.
<P>Thn epanalhch toy agwna Arh-Mpesiktas gia ton gyro twn ``32`` toy
Kypelloy Korats apofasise h FIMPA. H synanthsh qa diejaxqei stis 7
Ianoyarioy sthn Aqhna kekleismenwn twn qyrwn. Orgismena antedrase h
Mpesiktas kai apeilei na mhn elqei sthn Aqhna, an den ginei dekth h efesh
poy qa kataqesei.
<H3><A NAME="04">[04]</A> TIMES SYNALLAGMATOS</H3>
Oi epishmes times pwlhshs twn jenwn nomismatwn,poy dinei h Trapeza ths
Ellados einai: dolario HPA pros 248,60 draxmes, lira Agglias pros 416,43,
lira Kyproy pros 529,88, galliko fragko pros 47,40, elbetiko fragko pros
187,32, germaniko marko pros 160,26,tis ekato italikes liretes pros 16,26,
ta ekato gien Iapwnias pros 218,97 kai thn ECU pros 308,56 draxmes.
<H3><A NAME="05">[05]</A> KAIROS</H3>
Stadiakh beltiwsh,qa paroysiasei shmera o kairos, enw sporadikes broxes
kai liges kataigides qa shmeiwqoyn sto Aigaio. Oi anemoi qa pneoyn asqeneis
mexri metrioi kai h qermokrasia sta boreia qa fqasei toys 14 baqmoys, sto
Ionio kai ta ypoloipa hpeirwtika toys 18 kai sto Aigaio toys 19 baqmoys
Kelsioy. Liges nefwseis, asqeneis mexri metrioys anemoys kai qermokrasia
poy qa fqasei toys 16 kai toys 13 baqmoys Kelsioy antistoixa, qa exoyn
Aqhna kai Qessalonikh.
<P>(P.D.)
