<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Athens News Agency: News in Greek (PM), 96-12-18</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<center><a href="/info"><IMG SRC="/gifs/hrnet.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="[HR-Net Banner]"></a><BR></center>

<H2>Athens News Agency: News in Greek (PM), 96-12-18</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/ape">Athens News Agency: News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-18.ape.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-19.ape.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Athens News Agency at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.forthnet.gr/ape">http://www.forthnet.gr/ape</A>&gt;</H4>
<H4>Aqhna, Ellada, 18/12/1996 (APE)</H4>
<HR>
<H3>EIDHSEIS STA ELLHNIKA</H3>
<H4>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#01">[01]</A> Titloi eidhsewn.
<LI><A HREF="#02">[02]</A> Eidhseis analytika.
<LI><A HREF="#03">[03]</A> Aqlhtikes eidhseis.
<LI><A HREF="#04">[04]</A> Times synallagmatos.
<LI><A HREF="#05">[05]</A> Kairos.
</UL>
</H4>
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</A> TITLOI EIDHSEWN</H3>
Apoklimakwnontai oi agrotikes kinhtopoihseis. Anoigoyn ta mploka sth
Makedonia, paramenoyn se Qessalia kai Aigio. Met'empodiwn h kaqodos twn
Qessalwn agrotwn sthn Aqhna.
<P>Apozhmiwseis 10 dis drx gia toys agrotes anakoinwse o Stefanos Tzoymakas
ki ejhggeile sygklhsh toy symboylioy agrotikhs politikhs.
<P>Mploka kai sta limania apo toys naytikoys, opoy logw ths apergias toys
paramenoyn demena ta ploia. Mikroepeisodia se Peiraia kai Hgoymenitsa.
<P>Ellhnotoyrkika kai Kypriako sto epikentro twn synomiliwn toy Qeodwroy
Pagkaloy me to Bretano omologo toy sto Londino.
<P>Qeamatikh ptwsh apo 2,20 ews kai 2,80 drx to litro, apo ta mesanyxta stis
times twn ygrwn kaysimwn.
<P>Ston eisaggelea o fakelos me ta perioysiaka stoixeia ths dhmosiografoy
Ellhs Stah.
<P>Peripoy 9 ekat. drx h leia dyo lhsteiwn se Aqhna kai Qessalonikh.
<P>Kekleismenwn twn qyrwn qa epanalhfqei o agwnas mpasket toy Arh me thn
toyrkikh Mpesiktas.
<P>Stadiakh beltiwsh qa paroysiasei o kairos s'oloklhrh th xwra. Asqeneis
mexri metrioi oi anemoi. To qermometro qa deijei apo 5 mexri 19 baqmoys
Kelsioy.
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</A> EIDHSEIS ANALYTIKA</H3>
Apoklimakwnontai oi agrotikes kinhtopoihseis,kaqws to ena meta to allo ta
mploka sth Makedonia anoigoyn,enw paramenoyn sth Qessalia kai to Aigio.Oi
qessaloi agrotes katebainoyn ayrio sthn Aqhna gia syllalhthrio,enw oi
forthgatzhdes etoimazontai na dhmioyrghsoyn antimploka, gia na mh fqasoyn
oi agrotes sthn prwteyoysa.O Stefanos Tzoymakas dhlwse oti qa synanthsei
toys agrotes ean to zhthsoyn, enw o kybernhtikos ekproswpos apekleise
synanthsh toy prwqypoyrgoy me toys agrotes,oso paramenoyn kleistoi oi
dromoi.
<P>O ypoyrgos Gewrgias anakoinwse th xorhghsh apozhmiwsewn se osoys agrotes
exoyn plhgei apo tis kairikes synqhkes kai ejhggeile th sygklhsh toy
symboylioy agrotikhs politikhs, gia tis 10 Ianoyarioy.O k.Tzoymakas dhlwse
epishs oti qa diateqoyn peripoy 10 dis drx, poy qa metaferqoyn apo kondylia
toy deyteroy paketoy Ntelor gia apozhmiwseis stis perioxes Qessalias,
Karditsas, Trikalwn, Larisas, Boloy, Janqhs, Mytilhnhs kai allwn
perioxwn.
<P>Sth boylh synexizetai h syzhthsh toy proypologismoy,enw thn idia wra
epimenoyn stis kinhtopoihseis toys oi naytikoi, me apotelesma na paramenoyn
demena ta ploia.Sta limania ths Hgoymenitsas kai toy Peiraia shmeiwqhkan
mikroepeisodia,otan naytergates prospaqhsan na empodisoyn ploia na
proseggisoyn to limani.Gia thn Paraskeyh oi ergazomenoi sthn politikh
aeroporia ejhggeilan 24wrh apergia.
<P>Syzhthsh efolhs ths ylhs, eixan o proedros ths Dhmokratias kai o
prwqypoyrgos.Ejetasqhkan oi agrotikes kinhtopoihseis, h poreia twn eqnikwn
mas qematwn kai ths oikonomias,enw o k.Shmiths enhmerwse ton proedro ths
Dhmokratias gia ta apotelesmata toy Eyrwpaikoy Symboylioy Koryfhs sto
Doyblino.
<P>Se ejelijh briskontai oi diapragmateyseis metajy twn antartwn kai toy
ypoyrgoy Eswterikwn toy Peroy, prokeimenoy na afeqoyn eleyqeroi oi 200
omhroi poy kratoyntai sthn iapwnikh presbeia ths Lima, metajy twn opoiwn
kai o ellhnas presbhs Alkibiadhs Karokhs.Oi antartes eisebalan sthn
presbeia zhtwntas na apeleyqerwqoyn 500 kratoymenoi maxhtes ths organwshs
toys.
<P>Ta ellhnotoyrkika kai to Kypriako, htan sto epikentro twn synomiliwn poy
eixe sto Londino o Qeodwros Pagkalos me ton Bretano omologo toy
k.Rifkint.Kai oi dyo symfwnhsan oti qa thrhqei to xronodiagramma gia entajh
ths Kyproy sthn Koinothta, anejarthta apo thn poreia epilyshs toy
Kypriakoy.Erwthqeis gia tis dhlwseis peri fobwn ellhnotoyrkikhs syrrajhs
sto Aigaio, o k.Rifkint tonise oti miloyse genika kai exontas ypoch toy to
epeisodio sta Imia.
<P>Qeamatikh meiwsh paroysiazoyn apo ta mesanyxta oi times twn ygrwn
kaysimwn.H benzinh qa pwleitai fqhnotera kata 2,80 drx. to litro, toy
ntizel kinhshs 2,20 drx kai toy ntizel qermanshs kata 2,70 drx.
<P>Ston eisaggelea diabibase h ejetastikh epitroph ths boylhs,gia to Kazino
toy Floisboy,ta praktika poy aforoyn ta peroysiaka stoixeia ths
dhmosiografoy Ellhs Stah kai thn arnhsh ths na kataqesei sthn
epitroph.
<P>Peripoy 9 ekatommyria drx htan h leia twn drastwn poy ekanan dyo lhsteies
se Aqhna kai Qassalonikh.H prwth egine sthn Eqnikh Trapeza sthn odo Liosiwn
kai h deyterh se kosmhmatopwleio ths Qessalonikhs.
<A NAME="sports"></A><H3><A NAME="03">[03]</A> AQLHTIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
Me ikanopoihsh dexqhkan ston Arh thn apofash ths FIMPA na epanalhfqei o
agwnas ths omadas me thn Toyrkikh Mpesiktas gia toys 32 toy Kypelloy Korats,
poy eixe ginei 11 Dekembrioy,sth qessalonikh kai diakophke ligo meta apo
thn enarjh toy b'hmixronoy, logw epeisodiwn. H FIMPA poy orise thn
epanalhch toy agwna 7 Ianoyarioy, sthn Aqhna, ``kekleismenwn twn qyrwn``,
timwrhse me apokleismo triwn agwnistikwn hmerwn ton Aggelidh kai tessarwn
ton Alejanter, enw o Arhs san diorganwths ths synanthshs timwrhqhke akomh
me prostimo 45.000 markwn, dhladh peripoy 6,8 ekatommyriwn draxmwn.
<P>Oxi qa katsei na skasei o Ntoysan Mpagebits.Kai ti egine? H htta apo thn
Beroia den einai katastrofh. Kapote qa xaname, afoy sto podosfairo einai
mesa kai oi nikes kai oi httes,tonise o Ntoysko kai prosqese: ``Xwris na
qelw na ypotimhsw thn Beroia, h opoia einai mia poly kalh omada,nomizw oti
xasame tzampa&quot;.Oson afora ton Baresanobits,to symbolaio toy opoioy lhgei
ton Dekembrio, o Mpagebits, tonise, oti o paikths qa parameinei sthn
omada.
<P>H eqnikh mas omada podosfairoy katelabe thn 35-h qesh sthn pagkosmia
katatajh toy 1996, opws anakoinwse shmera sthn Zyrixh h FIFA. To eqniko mas
sygkrothma kerdise dyo qeseis apo thn antistoixh katatajh toy prohgoymenoy
mhna kai ``ekleise`` thn xronia me 46.15 baqmoys, enw exase mono mia qesh
sxetika me thn antistoixh pagkosmia katatajh toy 1995. Thn prwth qesh
katelabe gia trith synexomenh xronia h pagkosmia prwtaqlhtria omada ths
Brazilias me 68.38 baqmoys.
<H3><A NAME="04">[04]</A> TIMES SYNALLAGMATOS</H3>
Oi epishmes times pwlhshs twn jenwn nomismatwn,poy dinei h Trapeza ths
Ellados einai: dolario HPA pros 248,60 draxmes, lira Agglias pros 416,43,
lira Kyproy pros 529,88, galliko fragko pros 47,40, elbetiko fragko pros
187,32, germaniko marko pros 160,26,tis ekato italikes liretes pros 16,26,
ta ekato gien Iapwnias pros 218,97 kai thn ECU pros 308,56 draxmes.
<H3><A NAME="05">[05]</A> KAIROS</H3>
Stadiakh beltiwsh, apo ta dytika, qa paroysiasei ayrio o kairos enw
sporadikes broxes kai liges kataigides qa shmeiwqoyn sto Aigaio, alla
syntoma o kairos qa beltiwqei. Oi anemoi qa einai notiodytikoi asqeneis
mexri metrioi kai h qermokrasia sta boreia qa kymanqei 5 me 14 baqmoys, sto
Ionio kai ta ypoloipa hpeirwtika 8 me 18 kai sto Aigaio 13 me 19. Liges
nefwseis, tis prwines wres ayjhmenes, asqeneis mexri metrioys anemoys kai
qermokrasia 10 me 16 kai 6 me 13 antistoixa, qa exoyn ayrio Aqhna kai
Qessalonikh.
<P>(M.M.)
