<HR>
<H3>OI EIDHSEIS ANALYTIKA</H3>
<H3><A NAME="A1">[A]</A> ESWTERIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</a> METRA YCOYS 5,68 DIS. DRX. EJHGGEILE O K. LALIWTHS GIA THN ANAKOYFISH TWN PLHGENTWN APO TH QEOMHNIA STHN JANQH</H3>
<P>     Metra kostoys 5,68 disekatommyriwn drx. gia thn anakoyfish
kai yposthrijh twn plhgentwn apo thn prosfath qeomhnia katoikoys
ths Janqhs kai toy paragwgikoy dynamikoy toy nomoy,kaqws kai gia
thn amesh apokatastash twn ypodomwn kai toy oikistikoy istoy
ejhggeile o ypoyrgos PE.XW.D.E., Kwstas Laliwths,o opoios shmera
episkefqhke tis plhgeises perioxes, epikefalhs kybernhtikoy
klimakioy. Sto klimakio symmeteixan epishs o ypoyrgos Makedonias-
Qrakhs, Filippos Petsalnikos, o yfypoyrgos Eswterikwn, Dhmosias
Dioikhshs kai Apokentrwshs, Lampros Papadhmas, o Genikos
Grammateas toy ypoyrgeioy Eqnikhs Oikonomias, Apostolos Fwtiadhs,
kaqws kai o ypodioikhths ths Agrotikhs Trapezas, Aqanasios
Papagewrgioy kai o dioikhths twn ELGA, k. Zerboylakhs.
<P>     To poso ayto qa diateqei sto prwto tetramhno toy 1996. Ta
3,15 dis.drx. aforoyn se apozhmiwseis kai erga enisxyshs kai
anakoyfishs twn plhgentwn, enw ta 2,53 dis. drx. qa diateqoyn gia
erga ameshs apokatastashs twn ypodomwn kai toy oikistikoy istoy.
<P>     Anakoinwnontas ta metra, o k. Laliwths tonise oti apoteloyn
symplhrwmatikes parembaseis sto Programma Anaptyjhs toy nomoy
Janqhs, ycoys 112 dis.drx., poy exei arxisei to 1994 kai
problepetai na oloklhrwqei to 1999.
<P>     Analytikotera, gia thn amesh stegastikh apokatastash twn
oikogeneiwn poy ta spitia toys exoyn katastrafei problepetai h
enoikiash katalymatwn kai jenodoxeiwn kai h paroxh lyomenwn
spitiwn. Symfwna me ton ypoyrgo, hdh exei proegkriqei h organwsh
kataylismoy me lyomena spitia gia 18 oikogeneies sthn koinothta
Glaykhs.
<P>     Sxetika me thn apokatastash kai thn antimetwpish twn zhmiwn
poy exoyn ypostei katoikhmenoi xwroi, problepetai dwrean
stegastikh arwgh kai dieykolynseis gia xamhlotoka katanalwtika
daneia.H arwgh ayth qa anerxetai mexri toy posoy twn 2
ekatommyriwn drx. kata periptwsh kai qa xorhgeitai meta apo
aysthro elegxo me krithria ton ariqmo twn melwn ths oikogeneias,
to embadon ths katoikias kai thn ektash ths zhmias poy exei
proklhqei. Symfwna me ta stoixeia toy YPEXWDE, zhmies exoyn
ypostei 1432 spitia kai to kostos toys anerxetai sta 300
ekatommyria drx. Apo ta 1432 spitia, ta 60 exoyn katastrafei
olosxerws, enw alla 18 xarakthrizontai idiaitera epikindyna kai
katedafistea.
<P>     Gia thn anakataskeyh twn katestrammenwn katoikiwn problepetai
dwrean kratikh arwgh ycoys 33% toy synolikoy kostoys kai xorhghsh
atokwn daneiwn 15etoys diarkeias gia to ypoloipo poso. To anwtato
orio daneiodotoymenhs epifaneias einai ta 120 t.m. kai h
ypologizomenh timh monados einai oi 110.000 drx. ana t.m.
<P>     Sta 850 ekatommyria ektimwntai oi zhmies poy exoyn ypostei oi
paragwgikes monades toy nomoy,gia thn antimetwpish twn opoiwn
problepontai h xorhghsh kondyliwn apo to Programma Dhmosiwn
Ependysewn. Qa yparjei epidothsh 30% toy synolikoy ycoys ths
zhmias kai se periptwsh poy o dikaioyxos xreiastei daneio gia to
ypoloipo ths apokatastashs,problepetai epidothsh toy 40% toy
synolikoy epitokioy.(Ta metra ayta aforoyn se ktiriakes
egkatastaseis, mhxanologiko ejoplismo, emporeymata kai
apoqhkeymena trofima).
<P>     Gia thn idia kathgoria plhgentwn problepontai epishs
forologikes elafrynseis, opws h paratash ths proqesmias ypobolhs
dhlwsewn apodoshs toy FPA, toy foroy misqwtwn yphresiwn kai twn
loipwn parakratoymenwn forwn mexri tis 30 Maioy toy 1997 (h
proqesmia elhge stis 30 Noembrioy toy1996). Oi ofeiles aytes qa
apodoqoyn se eji mhniaies doseis, xwris prosayjhseis .
<P>     Antistoixa, gia ta xreh twn epixeirhsewn pros thn eforia, poy
einai dedhlwmena mexri thn 30h Noembrioy 1996, problepetai h
anastolh  mexri tis 30 Martioy kai qa plhrwqoyn se 24 mhniaies
doseis, epishs xwris prosayjhseis.
<P>     Gia thn apokatastash twn katestrammenwn agrotikwn
kalliergeiwn kai toy apwlesqentos zwikoy kefalaioy,problepetai h
paratash ths ypobolhs twn ypeyqynwn dhlwsewn, h apozhmiwsh apo ton
ELGA olwn twn kalliergeiwn kai toy zwikoy kefalaioy,opws kai h
enisxysh gia thn episkeyh twn agrotikwn mhxanhmatwn.
<P>     Se o,ti afora, telos, sta xreh kai ta daneia twn agrotwn poy
exoyn plhgei, qa yparjoyn eynoikes ryqmiseis kai dieykolynseis.Gia
ta apoqhkeymena agrotika proionta poy exoyn katastrafei qa
xorhghqoyn daneia me dwrean epixorhghsh meroys toy kefalaioy kai
shmantikes epidothseis toy epitokioy. Symfwna me to YPEXWDE, to
kostos twn zhmiwn poy proklhqhkan sta agrotika ktismata
(symperilambanomenwn twn kthnotrofikwn kai twn ktismatwn twn
ixqyokallierghtwn)anerxetai sta 350 ekatommyria drx.,enw oi zhmies
stis gewrgikes kalliergeies (kalampoki kai bambaki) anerxontai sta
500 ekatommyria drx.kai sto zwiko kefalaio sta 100 ekatommyria
drx.
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</a> SYLLALHTHRIO QA PRAGMATOPOIHSOYN AYRIO STHN AQHNA OI AGROTES THS QESSALIAS</H3>
<P>     Syllalhthrio qa pragmatopoihsoyn ayrio sthn Aqhna oi agrotes
ths Qessalias mazi me tis oikogeneies toys.
<P>     Sto metajy, oi odhgoi forthgwn apeiloyn toys agrotes me
antimetra kai endexetai na mplokaroyn ayrio thn kaqodo toys sthn
Aqhna, me aformh ta epeisodia poy dhmioyrghqhkan xqes sto Aigio.
<P>     O proedros ths omospondias aytokinhtistwn dieqnwn metaforwn
Panagiwths Nikolaras, dhlwse oti stis 5 to apogeyma qa synedriasei
to syndikalistiko toys organo gia na apofasisei ean oi odhgoi qa
apokleisoyn tis eqnikes odoys Aqhnwn -Korinqoy kai Aqhnwn -Lamias,
elpod_fomtar etsi toys agrotes na pragmatopoihsoyn syllalhthrio
sthn prwteyoysa.
<P>     Sth Qessalonikh apofasizei shmera h pammakedonikh
syntonistikh epitroph twn agrotwn ean qa aposyrqoyn apo ta mploka.
<P>     Eidh anoixtoi einai oi eqnikoi dromoi Qessalonikhs -Edessas,
Aqhnwn -Larisas mexri to ycos toy Almyroy kai h palia eqnikh odos
Aqhnwn -Lamias sth qesh Eryqres.
<P>     Apo ta odofragmata toy Almyroy kai toy Belestinoy epitrepetai
h dieleysh oswn tajideyoyn me epibatika aytokinhta meta apo
symfwnia metajy twn jenodoxwn Magnhsias kai twn agrotwn.
<H3><A NAME="03">[03]</a> ANOIJE O DROMOS STA ''PRASINA FANARIA''  ME APOFASH TWN AGROTWN</H3>
<P>     Eleyqerh einai apo tis 4.30 to apogeyma h dieleysh twn
oxhmatwn apo th diastayrwsh ''Prasina Fanaria'' sto dromo pros to
aerodromio &quot;Makedonia&quot; ths Qessalonikhs. Thn apofash gia
termatismo toy apokleismoy ths diastayrwshs phre
 h Syntonistikh Epitroph Agwna Makedonias-Qrakhs,twn agrotwn kata
th synedriash ths poy pragmatopoihqhke to meshmeri sto ktirio ths
PASEGES, ws &quot;deigma kalhs qelhshs, enocei twn Xristoygennwn,
prokeimenoy na metakinhqei to koino aeroporikws xwris problhmata&quot;.
<P>     Symfwna me thn apofash ths Epitrophs oi agrotes prokeitai na
apomakrynoyn apo thn perioxh ta trakter toys kai na enisxysoyn to
mploko ths Qermhs, sthn prajh, omws, arketa apo ta trakter mexri
tis 5 to apogeyma paremenan paratetagmena kata mhkos toy dromoy.
<P>     Oi agrotes ths Makedonias kai ths Qrakhs apofasisan epishs th
diathrhsh olwn twn mplokwn se kyrioys odikoys komboys ths Boreias
Elladas, opws sta diodia twn Malgarwn, to Loydia, to aerodromio
ths Xrysoypolhs sthn Kabala, to Aiginio kai to Litoxwro Pierias
kai to Kleidi Hmaqias.
<P>     Se o,ti afora sto ayriano panelladiko agrotiko syllalhthrio,
h Epitroph den phre epishmh apofash yper h kata ths symmetoxhs kai
to qema epafietai sthn proswpikh boylhsh twn agrotwn.
<H3><A NAME="04">[04]</a> S.TZOYMAKAS: WS TON IANOYARIO OI APOZHMIWSEIS TWN AGROTWN GIA TIS KALLIERGEIES POY EPLHGHSAN APO QEOMHNIES</H3>
<P>     Ta apotelesmata toy Symboylioy twn ypoyrgwn Gewrgias ths
Koinothtas stis Bryjelles paroysiase shmera o Ypoyrgos Gewrgias
Stefanos Tzoymakas o opoios xarakthrise qetikes tis epafes poy
eixe me Eyrwpaioys epitropoys.
<P>     Anakoinwse oti h Eyrwpaikh Enwsh protiqetai na bohqhsei toys
Ellhnes kallierghtes anagnwrizontas pws oi zhmies poy exoyn
ypostei einai arketa megales. Prosqese oti h ellhnikh kybernhsh qa
ypoballei ypomnhma me ektimhseis toy kostoys twn apozhmiwsewn, to
opoio h Koinothta qa egkrinei kai sth synexeia qa probei se
anakatanomh kondyliwn apo to koinotiko plaisio sthrijhs gia thn
kalych twn anagkwn.      Anaferomenos sto xrono ths diadikasias
ayths, o k. Tzoymakas shmeiwse oti ton Ianoyario qa arxisoyn na
kataballontai oi apozhmiwseis, synolikoy ycoys deka
disekatommyriwn draxmwn. Anaferomenos sta genikotera problhmata
twn agrotwn, ypogrammise oti &quot;h hgesia toy ypoyrgeioy Gewrgias
]wei proteinei programma tetraetias me metarryqmiseis, kostologhsh
aytoy toy programmatos, sxedia nomwn, gia na diamorfwqei to neo
qesmiko plaisio, opws kai alles politikes gia na oloklhrwqei mia
nea antilhch kai mia nea ejelijh ston tomea ths gewrgias&quot;.
O kybernhtikos ekproswpos
<P>     H kybernhsh einai diateqeimenh na syzhthsei me toys agrotes
dia toy ypoyrgoy Gewrgias Stefanoy Tzoymaka, epanelabe to meshmeri
o kybernhtikos ekproswpos Dhmhtrhs Reppas o opoios, omws,
dieykrinise oti ena tetoio aithma mexri ayth th stigmh den exei
diatypwqei.
<P>     Erwthqeis an o prwqypoyrgos protiqetai na dextei th
syntonistikh epitroph twn agrotwn o ypoyrgos Typoy eipe oti einai
telikh apofash toy k. Shmith na mhn dextei toys agrotes efoson den
apodesmeyoyn to eqniko odiko diktyo.
<H3><A NAME="05">[05]</a> PROBLHMATA KAI STHN AGORA THS QESSALONIKHS, EFOSON SYNEXISQEI H APERGIA TWN NAYTERGATWN</H3>
<P>     Dyo oxhmatagwga kai ena epibathgo ploio einai aragmena sto
limani ths Qessalonikhs kai perimenoyn th lhjh ths apergias twn
naytergatwn gia na apopleysoyn.
<P>     Ta problhmata poy prokyptoyn apo tis kinhtopoihseis twn
ergazomenwn emfanizontai entonotera, apo xqes, kaqws logw
synwstismoy sto limani den pragmatopoioyntai oyte ta ektakta
dromologia twn oxhmatagwgwn poy metaferoyn proionta sthn agora ths
Qessalonikhs. Etsi, de qa pragmatopoihqei kanena apo ta 15 ektakta
dromologia oxhmatagwgwn poy htan programmatismena gia thn trexoysa
ebdomada, alla oyte kai -ta periorismena, parola ayta, kata th
xeimerinh periodo- dromologia twn epibathgwn.
<P>     Shmeiwnetai oti ta en logw oxhmatagwga eixan dromologhqei
prokeimenoy na kalyfqei to keno poy dhmioyrghse sthn trofodosia
ths agoras ths Qessalonikhs o apokleismos twn dromwn apo toys
agrotes. H apergia twn naytergatwn, poy eixe arxika khryxqei ws
48wrh (Deytera kai Trith), epektaqhke xqes me nea 48wrh poy lhgei
ayrio to brady.
<P>     Mexri stigmhs, den einai gnwsto kata poson oi naytergates qa
apofasisoyn kai nea paratash twn kinhtopoihsewn. Efoson de,
shmeiwqei -ontws- ejelijh pros thn kateyqynsh ayth -kai se
syndyasmo me to endexomeno synexishs toy apokleismoy toy eqnikoy
odikoy diktyoy- einai idiaitera piqano na dhmioyrghqei problhma
eparkeias sthn agora.
<H3><A NAME="06">[06]</a> ANHSYXIES KAI PROBLHMATISMOYS GIA THN PROOPTIKH TOY SAE EJEFRASAN MELH TOY PROEDREIOY TOY</H3>
<P>     Anhsyxies kai problhmatismoys gia thn prooptikh toy SAE
ejefrasan o Proedros toy Symboylioy Apodhmoy Ellhnismoy kai
tessera melh toy Proedreioy toy  se dhlwseis toys sto Makedoniko
Praktoreio Eidhsewn, amesws meta th lhjh ths triths synedriashs
toys, poy oloklhrwqhke to meshmeri sth Qessalonikh.
<P>     Se apokleistikes toy dhlwseis sto MPE o Proedros toy SAE,
Antrioy Aqens, xarakthrise tis syzhthseis poy eixe to Proedreio,
stg diarkeia ths synedriashs toy, me thn politikh hgesia, ws
ejairetika ygieis, ekane, omws, logo kai gia &quot;anhsyxies&quot;.
<P>     &quot;Den qa elega oti exoyme parapona. Exoyme anhsyxies. Akoma
kai h Kybernhsh exei anhsyxies, poy basizontai sto gegonos oti
qeloyme na kanoyme perissotera mesa apo to Symboylio Apodhmoy
Ellhnismoy. Alla htan ygieis oi syzhthseis, perissotero apo pote
allote. Ejairetika ygieis. Pisteyw oti einai kalo to oti twra
jeroyme akribws tis qeseis ths Kybernhshs, kai ayth tis dikes
mas&quot;, dhlwse o k.Aqens kai prosqese:
<P>     &quot;Epishs eixame thn eykairia na exoyme mia ek baqewn syzhthsh
me ta melh ths Diakommatikhs Epitrophs. Mhn jexnate oti einai oloi
neoi sta kaqhkonta toys,opote eprepe na arxisoyme kai pali apo to
mhden. Alla feygoyme me mia poly kalh antilhch gia to poy
phgainoyme sto ejhs. Syzhthsame gia sygkekrimena pragmata poy qa
kanoyme sto ameso mellon.Prokeitai epishs na epanejetasoyme ta
symperasmata olwn twn Perifereiakwn Synedriwn, tis anagkes kai ta
aithmata twn Perifereiwn, kai qa erqoyme ton Aprilio
proetoimasmenoi. Proteinoyme h tetarth synedriash na ginei stis 10-
13 Aprilioy, me poly sygkekrimenes protaseis kai ypodeijeis kai qa
proskalesoyme toys armodioys ypoyrgoys gia ta problhmata twn
Apodhmwn Ellhnwn&quot;.
<P>     Se erwthsh gia to an einai aisiodojos gia thn epiteyjh ths
aytoxrhmatodothshs toy SAE o Proedros toy apanthse qetika, enw
anaforika me thn oikonomikh sthrijh toy qesmoy apo thn politeia
eipe: &quot;Nai, exoyn yparjei kaqysterhseis kai egw proswpika kalyca
olo ayto to tajidi toy Proedreioy  me dika moy ejoda. Pisteyw,
omws, oti mas edwsan logo na pisteyoyme oti qa eisprajoyme poroys
mexri to telos aytoy toy xronoy&quot;.
<P>      &quot;Kaqe arxh kai dyskolh, alla to qema einai oti para oles tis
dyskolies xrhmatikes, k.a., san Proedreio exoyme kataferei na
dwsoyme ena orama sto SAE, exoyme dhmioyrghsei ta Perifereiaka
SAE,doyleyoyme san Proedreio kai oses dyskolies exoyme ayth th
stigmh fantazomai oti qa mporesoyme na tis jeperasoyme sto
mellon&quot;, dhlwse apo thn pleyra toy o Antiproedros toy SAE kai
Proedros toy Perifereiakoy SAE Wkeanias, Hlias Rallhs, enw o
Proedros toy Perifereiakoy SAE Eyrwphs, (Antiproedros epishs toy
pagkosmioy SAE) Agaqaggelos Aslanidhs, dhlwse:
<P>     &quot;Htan h kalyterh apo oles tis prohgoymenes synedriaseis.
Pisteyoyme oti to politiko elleimma poy yphrxe oson afora sto SAE,
ystera apo ayth th synedriash qa kalyfqei etsi, wste na mporoyme
na petyxainoyme toys stoxoys poy qetoyme pros ofelos toy
Ellhnismoy. H stash toso ths Kybernhshs, oso kai ths Diakommatikhs
Epitrophs ths Boylhs apenanti mas htan ikanopoihtikh. Dhlwsan oti
mas sthrizoyn kai oti emeinan poly ikanopoihmenoi apo to ergo poy
exoyme epitelesei me ta mesa poy diaqetame&quot;.
<P>     Pio aysthrh kritikh askhsan oi dyo apo toys treis grammateis
toy SAE, Dhmhtrhs Kwnstantinidhs kai Pasxalhs Papaxristopoylos.
<P>     &quot;Meta thn teleytaia synedriash, kapoia stigmh h Ellada prepei
na apofasisei an qelei Apodhmo Ellhnismo kai pws ton qelei.
Kat'arxhn den prepei na doyme ton Apodhmo Ellhnismo
synaisqhmatika, alla kaqara texnokratika. An pragmati qeloyme
Apodhmo Ellhnismo, o opoios qa sthrizei thn Ellada kai se penhnta
h ekato xronia apo shmera, se opoiodhpote qema, qa prepei na
epemd}sei h Ellada twra ston Apodhmo Ellhnismo xwris logistikes
praktikes&quot;, epeshmane o k.Kwnstantinidhs.
<P>     Gia &quot;apogohteysh twn Apodhmwn ws pros th stash ths ellhnikhs
politeias&quot;, ekane logo o k.Papaxristopoylos, symfwna me ton opoio,
&quot;h syxnh metabolh proswpwn se syndyasmo me thn emfanizomenh
metabolh sthn politikh gia ton Apodhmo Ellhnismo, dhmioyrgei
amfibolies kai problhmatismoys gia to kata poso h ellhnikh
politeia epiqymei ayton ton qesmo. Isws exei arxisei na fobatai th
dynamikh toy kai akoma perissotero th mellontikh toy dynamikh&quot;.
<H3><A NAME="07">[07]</a> TA DEKA SHMEIA - PROTASEIS THS M.BRETANIAS GIA TO KYPRIAKO SYZHTHSAN OI Q.PAGKALOS KAI M.RIFKINT</H3>
<P>     Me ton Bretano omologo toy Malkom Rifkint synanthqhke shmera
sto Londino o ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn Qeodwros Pagkalos o opoios ton
enhmerwse gia ta eqnika mas qemata, ta ellhnotoyrkika kai to
Kypriako.
<P>     O k.Pagkalos zhthse dieykriniseis gia ta deka shmeia -
protaseis toy ypoyrgeioy ejwterikwn ths M. Bretanias gia proodo
sthn epilysh toy Kypriakoy. Problhmatismo dhmioyrgei to dekato
shmeio, h diatypwsh toy opoioy yponoei oti prepei prwta na yparjei
lysh toy Kypriakoy kai katopin na arxisoyn oi entajiakes
diapragmateyseis ths Megalonhsoy.
<H3><A NAME="08">[08]</a> SYNANTHSH MOYMPARAK -STEFANOPOYLOY THN PARASKEYH STO KAIRO</H3>
<P>     O Proedros ths Dhmokratias Kwnstantinos Stefanopoylos
anaxwrei, thn Paraskeyh, gia epishmh episkech sthn Aigypto, opoy
qa synanthqei me ton proedro ths Aigyptoy Xosni Moymparak.
<P>     H episkech toy k.Stefanopoyloy paroysiazei endiaferon epeidh
h katastash sth Mesh Anatolh exei periplakei, afoy me thn eklogh
ws Prwqypoyrgoy toy Israhl toy Mpentzamin Netaniaxoy oi
israhlopalaistiniakes sxeseis pernoyn ojytath krish. Proxqes o
proedros twn HPA Mpil Klinton xarakthrise ws katastrofikoys gia
thn eirhnh toys ebraikoys oikismoys sta katexomena arabika edafh.
<P>     H aigyptiakh efhmerida &quot;Al Gkoym Xoyrigia&quot; dhmosieyse qetiko
arqro gia tis ellhnoaigyptiakes sxeseis kai tonise oti oi
synomilies twn dyo proedrwn qa peristrafoyn stis dimereis sxeseis
poy briskontai se synexh beltiwsh se oloys toys tomeis.
<P>     O Proedros ths Dhmokratias qa epistrecei sthn Aqhna stis 23
Dekembrioy.
<H3><A NAME="09">[09]</a> TIMIO KAI ANTIPROSWPEYTIKO SYNEDRIO THS N.D. ZHTA O K.MHTSOTAKHS</H3>
