<P>     Shmeiwnei de oti an gia to epikeimeno synedrio ths
ajiwmatikhs antipoliteyshs den chfisei h bash toy kommatos gia thn
eklogh synedrwn, o idios den prokeitai na symmetasxei se ayto. &quot;An
to synedrio den ginei ton Febroyario me chfoforia apo th bash, h
N.D. qa odhghqei se aytoktonia&quot; tonizei o k. Mhtsotakhs.
<H3><A NAME="10">[10]</a> PROS ADIEJODO ODEYEI TO PORTO KARRAS-GIA KINDYNO KLEISIMATOS MILOYN OI ERGAZOMENOI</H3>
<P>     Se adynamia plhrwmhs twn misqwn toy proswpikoy einai sfodra
endexomeno na odhghqei h &quot;Toyristikh Gewrgikh Ejagwgikh&quot; -sthn
opoia anhkei to jenodoxeiako sygkrothma Porto Karras- apo 1hs
Ianoyarioy. Se ayth thn prooptikh sygklinoyn kai oi ektimhseis twn
ergazomenwn sto sygkrothma, meta thn apofash ths Grecotel na mh
leitoyrghsei kata th fetinh saizon to &quot;Melitwn&quot; (to ena apo ta dyo
jenodoxeia toy sygkrothmatos, to opoio kai diaxeirizetai).
<P>     Symfwna me plhrofories, h Grecotel odhghqhke sthn apofash
ayth -para to gegonos oti h prohgoymenh xrhsh htan idiaitera
kerdofora (270 ekat.)- afoy h &quot;tyxh&quot; toy sygkrothmatos ekkremei.
&quot;Ypo endexomeno, to Porto Karras na teqei se eidikh ekkaqarish -
opws exoyn zhthsei oi treis pistwtries trapezes ths &quot;Toyristikhs
Gewrgikhs&quot;- h Grecotel de diakindyneyei na breqoyn ston &quot;aera&quot; oi
krathseis, kaqws qa anagkastei na plhrwsei megales apozhmiwseis
sta toyristika praktoreia me ta opoia synergazetai&quot;, tonise sto
Makedoniko Praktoreio Eidhsewn anqrwpos poy parakoloyqei to qema
apo konta. Einai endeiktiko oti perysi to &quot;Melitwn&quot; filojenhse
18.000 atoma, poy pragmatopoihsan -synolika- 120.000
dianyktereyseis.
<P>     Sto Efeteio Qessalonikhs ekkremei apo to Dekembrio toy 1995
aithsh ypagwghs ths &quot;Toyristikhs Gewrgikhs&quot; se kaqestws eidikhs
ekkaqarishs. Oi pistwtries trapezes yposthrizoyn, sthn aithsh
toys, oti katexoyn anw toy 50% twn ofeilwn ths epixeirhshs kai -ws
ek toytoy- stoixeioqetoyn dikaiwma na zhthsoyn mia tetoia ejelijh.
Wstoso, oi adelfoi Karra exoyn antiqeth apoch ws pros to synoliko
ycos twn xrewn, thn opoia kai gnwstopoihsan sth Dikaiosynh.
Katopin toytoy, apofasisqhke h dienergeia pragmatognwmosynhs,
prokeimenoy na diapistwqei to akribes ycos twn ofeilwn kai kata
poson oi aitoyntes sygkentrwnoyn to 51% aytwn.
<P>     &quot;Wstoso, kai paroti orisqhkan pragmatognwmones, kaqysterei h
orkwmosia toys. Apo eggrafo -de- toy Efeteioy pros to swmateio
ergazomenwn sto sygkrothma, prokyptei safws oti h diadikasia
pragmatognwmosynhs de qa exei oloklhrwqei entos toy etoys&quot;,
ypogrammise o proedros toy swmateioy, D.Rebenikiwths. &quot;Synepws,
kindyneyei na oristikopoihqei h apofash ths Grecotel, me
apotelesma olo to sygkrothma -poy synthreitai mexri shmera apo ta
kerdh toy &quot;Melitwn&quot;, kaqws ta esoda ths ypoloiphs leitoyrgias
aporrofwntai gia thn ikanopoihsh twn xrewn- na perielqei se
adiejodo&quot;.
<P>     &quot;Kaqws exoyme labei th diabebaiwsh ths Grecotel oti efoson
lhjei to qema ews to telos Febroyarioy, to &quot;Melitwn&quot; qa
janaleitoyrghsei, zhtame na yparjei symfwnia metajy twn pistwtriwn
trapezwn -me thn eggyhsh ths Politeias- oti de qa dhmioyrghqei
sthn etaireia kanena problhma se periptwsh ekkaqarishs&quot;, synexise
o idios. &quot;Se periptwsh, de, poy to sygkrothma kleisei -estw kai
gia mikro xroniko diasthma- eimaste apofasismenoi na mhn
epitrecoyme thn eisodo se kanena neo ependyth, an den katabalei
toys misqoys akomh kai gia to diasthma mh leitoyrgias&quot;.
<P>     Symfwna me toys ergazomenoys, thn olh katastash epiteinei kai
h apo koinoy prospaqeia toy IKA kai ths Eqnikhs na katasxesoyn ta
pos\ -ycoys peri ta 25 ekat. mhniaiws- poy aforoyn sto enoikio toy
kazino Xalkidikhs, kaqws kai ta kondylia poy katabalei to kazino
gia toys epimerismoys (xrhsh twn ypodomwn toy sygkrothmatos).
-Mexri shmera to &quot;Melitwn&quot; apasxoloyse 254 atoma. Epipleon, 200
monimoi ypallhloi ergazontai sta kentrika grafeia ths etaireias
kai 607 sto kazino. Synolika, sto sygkrothma apasxoloyntai kai 700
epoxiakoi ergazomenoi, enw ektimatai oti se epixeirhseis poy
parexoyn symplhrwmatikes ergasies -&quot;zwntas&quot;, oysiastika, apo to
sygkrothma- ergazontai alla 250 atoma.
<P>     &quot;Shmera, blepoyme thn etaireia na dialyetai mprosta sta matia
mas. Yparxei adynamia plhrwmhs twn promhqeytwn, den emfialwnontai
krasia epeidh den einai dynath h agora mpoykaliwn kai de ginetai
kamia krathsh en ocei Xristoygennwn. Epipleon, jepoylioyntai ta
mhxanhmata toy elaioyrgeioy&quot;, katelhje o k.Rebenikiwths.
<H3><A NAME="11">[11]</a> ENA LABARO STAYROFORIWN, AGIOGRAFIES TOY 17oy AIWNA KAI XEIROGRAFA BIBLIA TOY 1811 ANAZHTOYN STEGH STO XWRIO PANAGIA THS QASOY</H3>
<P>     Ena asprokokkino labaro stayroforiwn, poy h paradosh
yposthrizei oti anhkei ston Rixardo ton Leontokardo, xeirografa
biblia poy xronologoyntai  apo to 1811 kai agiografies toy 17oy,
toy 18oy kai toy 19oy aiwna, kindyneyoyn apo th fqora, alla kai
toys arxaiokaphloys, sthn koinothta Panagias ths Qasoy.
<P>     Ta shmantikotata ayta keimhlia, mazi me palia ekklhsiastika
skeyh kai mpakirenia nomismata filojenoyntai ston nao ths
Koimhsews ths Qeotokoy, h anegersh toy opoioy egine to 1831, panw
sta ereipia dyo palaioterwn ekklhsiwn. H akribhs xronologhsh ths
anegershs twn dyo prohgoymenwn ktismatwn den einai dynath, logw
ths oloklhrwtikhs katastrofhs twn sxetikwn arxeiwn. Pantws, apo
dihghseis perihghtwn kai eggrafa ths epoxhs, prokyptei oti h
deyterh ekklhsia xtisthke gyrw sto 1700, se antikatastash mias
poly palaioterhs byzantinhs.
<P>     Idiaitero endiaferon paroysiazei kai to jyloglypto templo toy
naoy, poy xronologeitai apo tis arxes toy prohgoymenoy aiwna, enw
diaswzetai kai tmhma toy temploy ths palaioterhs ekklhsias, poy
xrhsimeyei shmera ws eikonostasi kai apeikonizei dyo neara agoria
me omfalioys lwroys. H paradosh toy nhsioy leei oti to ypoloipo
tmhma toy jyloglyptoy dwristhke sth monh Ibhrwn toy Agioy Oroys,
otan ayth katastrafhke apo pyrkagia.
<P>        Thn arxaiologikh kai istorikh ajia toy mnhmeioy enisxyei
to gegonos oti ena megalo tmhma toy, xtisthke me marmara poy
apospasthkan apo arxaioys naoys ths perioxhs, me apotelesma na
diathroyntai mexri shmera sto ktisma epigrafes mh qrhskeytikoy
periexomenoy.
<P>     Sth biblioqhkh malista ths Benetias yparxei tajidiwtiko
xeirografo enos germanoy perihghth poy episkefthke  thn ekklhsia
ths Panagias, o opoios anaferetai sthn yparjh mias arxaias
epigrafhs sto dapedo toy naoy. H epigrafh den yparxei pia.
<P>     Shmera oi katoikoi ths perioxhs prospaqoyn na periswsoyn
monoi toys ta keimhlia toy xwrioy. H koinothta, se synergasia me
thn ekklhsia, epixeirei thn anegersh enos mikroy moyseioy opoy qa
stegastoyn, topoqethmena se proqhkes, to labaro, oi eikones, ta
sje}g kai ta nomismata.
<P>     &quot;Prepei opwsdhpote na ginoyn kapoies prospaqeies toylaxiston
gia na xronologhqoyn kata proseggisin ayta ta keimhlia kai fysika
gia na stegastoyn&quot;, eipe sto Makedoniko Praktoreio o daskalos toy
xwrioy, Gewrgios Kabazhs, poy prospaqei se synergasia kai me alles
arxes ths Panagias, na eyaisqhtopoihsei thn Politeia kai thn koinh
gnwmh, pros thn kateyqynsh ths prostasias toy naoy. Pros thn
kateyqynsh ayth o k.Kabazhs, kata th diarkeia synedrioy sth
Qessalonikh ton prohgoymeno Septembrio, paroysiase stoixeia
sxetika me ton nao, prokeimenoy na egeirei to endiaferon twn
parebriskomenwn episthmonwn.
<P>     O k.Kabazhs anaferqhke kai sthn yparjh mias anaglyfhs sthlhs,
poy ferei epigrafh, h opoia brisketai shmera &quot;parathmenh&quot;, opws
xarakthristika eipe, anamesa se mia stoiba apo tsimenta sto
jwkklhsi toy Agioy Gewrgioy sthn Panagia ths Qasoy.
<H3><A NAME="12">[12]</a> LOGOTEXNIKES &quot;EISBOLES&quot; SE TRAPEZES KAI DHMOSIES YPHRESIES STH QESSALONIKH PROGRAMMATIZEI GIA TO 1997 O ORGANISMOS POLITISTIKHS PRWTEYOYSAS</H3>
<P>     Apospasmata neoellhnikhs logotexnias kai stixoi erwtikwn,
dhmotikwn kai rempetikwn tragoydiwn qa &quot;eisballoyn&quot; -dia stomatos
tetrameloys qeatrikhs omadas- kaqolh th diarkeia toy 1997 se
trapezes, dhmosies yphresies kai ergasiakoys xwroys, prokeimenoy
na cyxagwghsoyn, alla kai na afypnisoyn to koino ths polhs, sto
plaisio mias prwtoboylias toy Organismoy Politistikhs Prwteyoysas
ths Eyrwphs.
<P>     Oi asynhqistes aytes trileptes episkeceis, poy qa ginontai se
wres aixmhs sto kentro ths polhs, qa oloklhrwnontai me thn
prosfora sto koino fylladiwn me erga klasikwn kai sygxronwn
poihtwn.
<P>     Hdh, h tetramelhs omada twn apofoitwn ths dramatikhs sxolhs
toy KQBE, poy exei analabei th diorganwsh twn logotexnikwn
trileptwn, exei episkeftei to nomarxiako symboylio ths
Qessalonikhs, alla kai ta grafeia  gnwsths efhmeridas ths polhs,
prosferontas stoys ergazomenoys ena eyxaristo kai epoikodomhtiko
dialeimma.
