<H3><A NAME="B1">[B]</A> EJWTERIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
<H3><A NAME="13">[13]</a> 200 OMHROI APO TO&quot;FWTEINO MONOPATI&quot; STH LIMA - METAJY TOYS O PRESBEYTHS THS ELLADAS</H3>
<P>     O presbeyths ths Elladas sto Peroy, Alkibiadhs Karokhs,
sygkatalegetai metajy twn diakosiwn  omhrwn poy kratoyn 30
akroaristeroi antartes, oi opoioi to brady katelaban thn katoikia
toy Iapwna presbeyth sthn prwteyoysa ths xwras, Lima.
<P>     H epiqesh twn antartwn egine kata th diarkeia dejiwshs pros
timhn toy Iapwna Aytokratora kai sthn opoia parabriskontan
ekatontades politikoi kai diplwmates.
<P>     Thn eidhsh ths omhrias toy Alkibiadh Karokh, epibebaiwse o
A'Grammateas ths ellhnikhs presbeias toy Peroy Nikos Mpazos kaqws
kai o epikefalhs twn tmhmatos twn  presbewn Latinikhs Amerikhs,
pq]sbgr k.Ladopoylos.
<P>     Metajy twn omhrwn einai kai o ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn toy Peroy
kai oi presbeytes ths Koybas, ths Bolibias kai ths Brazilias.
<P>     Plhrofories anaferoyn oti oi enoploi antartes einai melh toy
epanastatikoy kinhmatos &quot;Fwteino Monopati&quot;  kai apeiloyn na
skotwsoyn toys omhroys ean oi arxes den apeleyqerwsoyn syntrofoys
toys poy briskontai stis fylakes.
<P>     Oi antartes apeleyqerwsan toys hlikiwmenoys kai tis gynaikes
anamesa stis opoies htan kai h mhtera toy Proedroy toy Peroy
Almperto Foytsimori.
<H3><A NAME="14">[14]</a> PRWTH EIDHSH STA SKOPIA H PROSKLHSH E.BENIZELOY STON OMOLOGO TOY GIA THN TELETH ENARJHS THS POLITISTIKHS PRWTEYOYSAS</H3>
<P>     Shmantikh probolh apo ta mesa enhmerwshs ths PGDM gnwrise h
prwtoboylia toy Ellhna ypoyrgoy Politismoy, Eyaggeloy Benizeloy na
apeyqynei prosklhsh pros ton skopiano omologo toy, Slompontan
Oynkofski na symmetexei sthn epishmh teleth enarjhs twn ekdhlwsewn
gia thn Politistikh Prwteyoysa ths Eyrwphs 1997.
<P>     H kratikh thleorash ths geitonikhs xwras metedwse ws prwth
ejwterikh eidhsh thn &quot;proqesh ths Elladas na symperilabei kai ta
Skopia sthn epishmh teleth khryjhs ths Qessalonikhs ws
Politistikhs Prwteyoysas ths Eyrwphs gia to erxomeno etos&quot;.
<P>     Anafora sthn prosklhsh poy aphyqyne pros ta Skopia o Ellhnas
ypoyrgos Politismoy ekane kai o kratikos radiofwnikos staqmos twn
Skopiwn.
<H3><A NAME="15">[15]</a> ME TON G. KLHRIDH QA SYNANTHQOYN ELLHNOKYPRIOI KAI TOYRKOKYPRIOI FOITHTES</H3>
<P>     Me ton Proedro ths Dhmokratias Glayko Klhridh, qa synanthqoyn
ayrio, Ellhnokyprioi kai Toyrkokyprioi foithtes, sto plaisio ths
enqarrynshs ameswn epafwn twn dyo pleyrwn. Hdh, oi foithtes
synanthqhkan me ton Toyrkokyprio hgeth Raoyf Ntenktas.
<P>     H synanthsh ayth, apofasisthke meta apo paraklhsh ths
presbeias twn HPA sth Leykwsia kai entassetai sto plaisio omadwn
ergasias ths Epitrophs Ypotrofiwn ``Foylmprait''.
<P>     ``Skopos twn synanthsewn einai  na bohqhqei h neoterh genia
twn mellontikwn hgetwn twn dyo koinothtwn, na maqoyn perissotera h
mia gia thn allh, akoygontas amesa tis apoceis ths paroysas genias
hgetwn'', dhlwse  sto KYPE  ekproswpos ths Presbeias twn HPA.
<P>     Parallhla, xarakthrise tis synanthseis aytes ws xrhsimes, enw
shmeiwse oti `` oi HPA qa enqarrynoyn kaqe eykairia gia atoma twn
dyo koinothtwn na maqoyn perissotera stoixeia h mia gia thn allh''.
<H3><A NAME="16">[16]</a> TO DIKASTHRIO ANQRWPINWN DIKAIWMATWN DIKAIWNEI ELLHNOKYPRIA GIA THN PARANOMH KATOXH THS PERIOYSIAS THS APO TA KATOXIKA STRATEYMATA</H3>
<P>     Me 11 chfoys yper kai eji kata, to Dikasthrio Anqrwpinwn
Dikaiwmatwn toy Symboylioy ths Eyrwphs dikaiwse prosfygh
Ellhnokyprias gia thn paranomh katoxh ths perioysias ths apo ta
toyrkika katoxika strateymata kai  apofasise oti yparxei
sumewif|lemg parabiash twn anqrwpinwn dikaiwmatwn
<P>     Sthn apofash toy to Dikasthrio anaferei xarakthristika oti
&quot;synexizetai h parabiash twn anqrwpinwn dikaiwmatwn ths Titinas
Loizidoy se sxesh me thn akinhth perioysias ths sthn Keryneia h
opoia apo to 1974 brisketai katw apo ton elegxo toy toyrkikoy
stratoy&quot;.
<P>     H shmasia ths apofashs toy Symboylioy ths Eyrwphs egkeitai
sto gegonos oti gia prwth fora h Toyrkia paroysiazetai ypologh
dieqnws gia tis parabiaseis twn anqrwpinwn dikaiwmatwn logw ths
synexizomenhs paranomhs katoxhs meroys ths Kyproy, dhlwse o
dikhgoros ths k.Loizidoy.
<H3><A NAME="17">[17]</a> KYMA ATOMIKWN PROSFYGWN ELLHNOKYPRIWN KATA THS TOYRKIAS ANAMENETAI STO EYRWPAIKO DIKASTHRIO</H3>
<P>     Kyma atomikwn prosfygwn Ellhnokypriwn kata ths Toyrkias
anamenetai na akoloyqhsei meta thn apofash toy Eyrwpaikoy
Dikasthrioy Anqrwpinwn Dikaiwmatwn poy katadikazei thn Toyrkia gia
parabiash twn idiokthsiakwn dikaiwmatwn ths Ellhnokyprias Titinas
Loizidoy, h opoia parempodisthke na metabei sthn ejoxikh ths
katoikia sta Katexomena.
<P>     Me erwthsh toy sto Symboylio Ypoyrgwn ths EE, o Eyrwboyleyths
toy SYN, Alekos Alabanos zhta na efarmosqei h apofash toy
Dikasthrioy gia th Loizidoy, alla kai gia kaqe omoia periptwsh
parabiashs twn perioysiakwn dikaiwmatwn, apo tis dynameis katoxhs.
<P>     Epishs, na epitrapei sthn Elenh Fwka poy didaskei sta
Katexomena, h eleyqerh prosbash sthn eleyqerh perioxh ths Kyproy,
poy shmera empodizetai, prokeimenoy na kamfqei to eleyqero ths
fronhma, kata parabash ths Synqhkhs, kaqws kai  h antikatastash
enos alloy Ellhna daskaloy poy didaske mexri protinos sthn
Karpasia, alla syntajiodothqhke.
<P>     Telos, o k.Alabanos zhta  na epitrapei sta paidia ths
Karpasias na didaskontai anempodista apo ta biblia kai alla efodia
poy h Kypriakh Dhmokratia toys stelnei, shmeiwnontas oti biblia
istorias h qrhskeytikwn pote den fqanoyn ston proorismo toys.
<H3><A NAME="18">[18]</a> ANAPTYSSONTAI OI BOYLGAROTOYRKIKES EMPORIKES SXESEIS</H3>
<P>     H Toyrkia einai basikos emporikos etairos ths Boylgarias
metajy twn balkanikwn xwrwn, dhlwse o proedros  toy Boylgarikoy
Emporikoy Biomhxanikoy Epimelhthrioy, Mpozintar Mpozinof, shmera
sth Sofia, sto periqwrio toy seminarioy Boylgarwn kai Toyrkwn
epixeirhmatiwn me qema tis boylgarotoyrkikes oikonomikes sxeseis
kai tis dynatothtes gia ependyseis sth Boylgaria.
<P>      Symfwna me ton k.Mpozinof, sth Boylgaria drasthriopoioyntai
1600 toyrkikes etairies, enw h Boylgaria ekproswpeitai mono me dyo
etairies sthn toyrkikh agora.
Basiko empodio sth dieyrynsh ths boylgarikhs emporikhs paroysias sthn
Toyrkia, kata ton k. Mpozinof, einai oi periorismoi poy qetei h
toyrkikh nomoqesia.
<P>     Mexri stigmhs to Boylgariko Emporiko kai Biomhxaniko
Epimelhthrio exei ypogracei symfwnies synergasias me tria toyrkika
emporika Epimelhthria. Ths Agkyras, ths Adrianoypolhs kai ths
Sl}qmgr.
<P>     Ejalloy, skopos toy seminarioy ths Sofias htan h dieyrynsh
twn dimerwn epafwn ston emporiko tomea, h ejetash twn dynatothtwn
gia toyrkikh symmetoxh stis idiwtikopoihseis sth Boylgaria, h
dhmioyrgia miktwn epixeirhsewn kai h egkairh kai egkyrh antallagh
plhroforiwn metajy twn Emporikwn Epimelhthriwn ths Boylgarias kai
ths Toyrkias.
<H3><A NAME="19">[19]</a> KRISH STHN TOYRKIKH AYTOKINHTOBIOMHXANIA EJAITIAS AQROWN EISAGWGWN METAXEIRISMENWN</H3>
<P>     Enw Germania kai Hnwmenes Politeies prospaqoyn na
dialeykanoyn to skandalo &quot;biomhxanikhs kataskopias&quot; metajy ths
&quot;Opel&quot; kai ths &quot;Folgks Bagken&quot;, sthn Toyrkia h egxwria
aytokinhtobiomhxania einai sta proqyra ths katarreyshs.
<P>     Aitia h almatwdhs ayjhsh ths eisagwghs aytokinhtwn, kyriws
metaxeirismenwn, meta thn apofash ths toyrkikhs kybernhshs na
katarghsei polloys dasmoys stis eisagwges oxhmatwn -metro poy
eynoei amesa thn Germania.
<P>     Deixnontas fanera oti epiqymia ths einai na tonwsei tis
sxeseis ths me th Germania, basiko symmaxo ths stis prospaqeies
gia thn eisodo ths sthn Eyrwpaikh Enwsh, h Toyrkia, eqese se
efarmogh mia nea nomoqesia, h opoia orizei oti oi Toyrkoi
metanastes, poy qa kataqetoyn gia ena oloklhro etos to poso twn
50.000 markwn sthn toyrkikh Kentrikh Trapeza, qa exoyn to dikaiwma
na eisagoyn metaxeirismena aytokinhta, ews tessarwn xronwn, xwris
na katabaloyn dasmoys.
<P>     Me ton tropo ayto, h toyrkikh kybernhsh ypologizei oti qa
proselkysei stis kratikes trapezes poso toylaxiston 5
disekatommyriwn markwn, paragnwrizontas oti ki an akomh petyxei
ton stoxo ths, aytos qa pollaplasiasei ta yparxonta problhmata
sthn egxwria aytokinhtobiomhxania.
<P>     Symfwna me ta yparxonta stoixeia, ton Ianoyario toy 1995 to
pososto twn eisagomenwn aytokinhtwn kymainontan sto 5% epi toy
synoloy twn agorwn, enw to antistoixo mhna toy 1996 eftase to 17%
kai me to neo etos ena sta tessera aytokinhta qa eisagetai.
<P>     H toyrkikh aytokinhtobiomhxania sthrizetai se treis
koinoprajies egxwriwn etaireiwn me th Fiat, th Reno kai thn
Togiota antistoixa, oi opoies odhgoyntai me maqhmatikh akribeia se
xreokopia.
<P>     Hdh o megalyteros omilos ths xwras h TOFAS, exei katarghsei
xiliades qeseis ergasias gia na mporesei na antapejelqei sthn
piesh ths agoras, enw oi apolyseis ergazomenwn ston xwro ths
aytokinhtobiomhxanias anamenetai me thn parodo toy xronoy na
diogkwqoyn.
<H3><A NAME="20">[20]</a> MEGALH EKQESH BYZANTINWN EIKONWN STH GENEYH</H3>
<P>     Megalh ekqesh me titlo &quot;Byzantines eikones- to fws ths
Xristianikhs Anatolhs&quot; anoije hdh tis pyles ths sto Moyseio Texnhs
kai Istorias ths Geneyhs. Oi eikones anhkoyn sth syllogh toy
Libanezoy polyekatommyrioyxoy Ampoy Antal kai h ekqesh qa
diarkesei ws tis 4 Maioy 1997.
<P>     Ektiqentai ellhnikes eikones byzantinoy kai metabyzantinoy
yfoys, toy Damaskhnoy, Krhta zwgrafoy sygxronoy toy Domhnikoy
Qeotokopoyloy, kaqws kai dyo allwn Krhtwn, twn Tzanh kai Poylakh.
<P>     &quot;Melxitikes&quot; eikones poy dhmioyrghqhkan apo Ellhnes
agiografoys gia &quot;Melxites&quot; pistoys, oi opoioi apoteloysan meros
twn Orqodojwn h Kaqolikwn Arabwn.
<P>     Akomh, ektiqentai rwsikes eikones twn Sxolwn Nobgkoront kai
Mosxas.
<P>     Ton epishmo katalogo ths Ekqeshs prologizei o Mhtropoliths
Elbetias k.Damaskhnos.
<H3><A NAME="21">[21]</a> KEKLEISMENWN TWN QYRWN H SYNANTHSH BAN NTER STOYL ME EKPROSWPOYS TWN POLITIKWN KOMMATWN THS PGDM</H3>
<P>     Kekleismenwn twn qyrwn synexizetai se kentriko jenodoxeio twn
Skopiwn, h syzhthsh stroggylhs trapezas me qema thn oikodomhsh
armonikwn sxesewn metajy twn meionothtwn sthn PGDM, poy diorganwse
o epitropos toy OASE, armodios  gia qemata meionothtwn, Maj Ban
Nter Stoyl o opoios episkeptetai thn PGDM.
<P>     Sth syzhthsh metexoyn o politikos dieyqynths toy Symboylioy
ths Eyrwphs, o antikatastaths toy ypatoy armosth gia thn prwhn
Gioygkoslabia Gkernt Arens,  oi ypoyrgoi  Ejwterikwn kai
Dikaiosynhs, Lioympomir Frtskofski kai Blanto Popofski kai
ekproswpoi twn politikwn kommatwn ths PGDM. To albanofwno Komma
Dhmokratikhs Eyhmerias (PDP) ekproswpeitai apo ton proedro toy
kommatos Ampoyraxman Aliti
<P>     Sth syzhthsh arnhqhkan na metasxoyn, an kai prosklhqhkan, ta
rizospastika albanofwna kommata &quot;Dhmokratikhs Eyhmerias-Albanwn&quot;
(PDP-A) kai &quot;Laiko Dhmokratiko&quot; (NDP).
<P>     O dhmosiografikos kosmos ths PGDM ejefrase th dysareskeia toy
gia to gegonos oti den epetraph h eisodos sta mesa enhmerwshs. O
Nter Stoyl dikaiologhse thn apagoreysh legontas oti h episkech toy
sta Skopia einai idiwtikh kai diabebaiwse oti sth syzhthsh den
prokeitai na ginoyn diapragmateyseis metajy kybernhshs kai
meionothtwn. Wstoso toso h hmiepishmh efhmerida &quot;Noba Makentonia&quot;
oso  kai h &quot;Ntnebnik&quot; se sxetika dhmosieymata diatypwnoyn
amfibolies gia to poso einai &quot;idiwtikh&quot; h synanthsh, kai
dierwtwntai giati h kybernhsh metexei me dyo ypoyrgoys enw
antiqeta ta kommata esteilan ekproswpoys toys.
<H3><A NAME="22">[22]</a> GIA KRISH STO MEGALYTERO KOMMA THS ANTIPOLITEYSHS THS PGDM KANEI LOGO SKOPIANH EFHMERIDA</H3>
<P>     Gia krish sto Fileleyqero Komma ths PGDM kanei logo h
efhmerida twn Skopiwn &quot;Betser&quot;, yposthrizontas pws ta qemelia toy
megalyteroy kommatos ths antipoliteyshs diabrwnontai apo tis
eswkommatikes sygkroyseis poy jespasan meta th diejagwgh twn
dhmotikwn eklogwn.
<P>     Symfwna me thn efhmerida, h eklogikh htta twn fileleyqerwn
apodoqhke sthn arnhtikh propaganda orismenwn stelexwn toy kata twn
ypochfiwn toy kommatos. H propaganda ayth htan idiaitera aisqhth
sto dhmo Axridas, opoy stelexh toy Fileleyqeroy Kommatos
yposthrijan dhmosia ton ypochfio dhmarxo ths kybernwsas
Sosiakdglojqatij^r Enwshs, me apotelesma na odhghsoyn se paraithsh
ton proedro toy topikoy pararthmatos ths Axridas.
<P>     Ejaitias ths yposthrijhs poy edwsan oi opadoi kai ta stelexh
toy Fileleyqeroy Kommatos ston sosialdhmokrath ypochfio, to komma
exase kai to dhmo toy Stip, ston opoio epikratoyse epi xronia.
<P>     Para ta apta deigmata gia tis eswkommatikes sygkroyseis sto
Fileleyqero Komma, katalhgei h efhmerida, to proedreio toy
kommatos eqelotyflei, yposthrizontas pws oi 60.000 chfoi poy
sygkentrwse stis dhmotikes ekloges apoteloyn &quot;megalh hqikh nikh&quot;.
Oson afora thn paraithsh toy proedroy toy topikoy pararthmatos ths
Axridas, anaferei pws ayth apotelei fysiologikh synexeia ths
leitoyrgias kai ths yparjhs toy kommatos.
<H3><A NAME="23">[23]</a> NEA MYSTIKH BASH TOY RKK STHN KRHTH BRHKE O TOYRKIKOS TYPOS</H3>
<P>     Nea epiqesh kata ths Elladas gia paroxh yposthrijhs sto
Koyrdiko Ergatiko Komma (RKK) kanei shmera h toyrkikh efhmerida
Tsoymxroyriet.
<P>     Sygkekrimena h efhmerida anaferei oti se mystikh epixeirhsh
poy egine prosfata,  metaferqhkan apo to stratopedo twn prosfygwn
toy Layrioy se &quot;nea bash sthn Krhth&quot;, opws grafei, 220 Koyrdoi
antartes toy RKK.
<P>     H Tsoymxroyriet prosqetei oti h epixeirhsh thn opoia
xarakthrizei mazikh, egine ypo to prosxhma bohqeias toy Eryqroy
Stayroy kai prokalese &quot;megalh anhsyxia stoys ellhnikoys
kybernhtikoys kykloys&quot;.
<P>     Symfwna me to dhmosieyma, sthn Agkyra ektimatai oti h kinhsh
einai mia prospaqeia ths ellhnikhs kybernhshs na krycei to gegonos
oti h Aqhna bohqa to RKK.
<P>     Parallhla anaferetai oti h Toyrkia exei epaneillhmena
apokalycei to syndesmo anamesa sto stratopedo toy Layrioy kai to
RKK.
<P>     Ajizei na shmeiwqei oti h efhmerida den katonomazei thn
topoqesia ths bashs sthn Krhth opws allwste den eixan katonomastei
kai oi topoqesies allwn tetoiwn &quot;basewn&quot; stis kata kairoys
paromoies &quot;apokalyceis&quot;, oi opoies exoyn diaceystei kathgorhmatika
apo tis ellhnikes arxes.
<P>     To Layrio filojenei megalo ariqmo prosfygwn apo thn Toyrkia
oi opoioi exoyn zhthsei asylo sthn Elada gia na diafygoyn apo tis
diwjeis poy yfistanto apo tis toyrkikes arxes.
