<H2>Macedonian Press Agency: News in Greek, 96-12-20</H2>
<H4>From: Macedonian Press Agency &lt;mpa@philippos.mpa.gr&gt;</H4>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/mpe">Macedonian Press Agency: News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory</H5>
<H4>ENHMERWTIKO DELTIO EIDHSEWN TOY MAKEDONIKOY PRAKTOREIOY</H4>
<H4>Qessalonikh 20 Dekembrioy 1996</H4>
<HR>
<H3>EIDHSEIS STA ELLHNIKA</H3>
<H4><A HREF="#A0">[A]</a> ESWTERIKES EIDHSEIS</H4>
<H4><A HREF="#B0">[B]</a> EJWTERIKES EIDHSEIS</H4>
<HR>
<H3>TITLOI EIDHSEWN</H3>
<H4><A NAME="A0"></A><A HREF="#A1">[A]</a> ESWTERIKES EIDHSEIS</H4>
<DIR>
<LI><H4><A HREF="#01">[01]</a> D.REPPAS: H KYBERNHSH METAKINHQHKE APO TIS ARXIKES THS QESEIS ENW OI AGROTES PARAMENOYN AMETAKINHTOI</H4>
<LI><H4><A HREF="#02">[02]</a> SYNEXIZETAI KAI SHMERA H APERGIA TWN NAYTIKWN - AKINHTOPOIHMENA TA PLOIA STA LIMANIA</H4>
<LI><H4><A HREF="#03">[03]</a> ANESTEILAN TIS KINHTOPOIHSEIS TOYS OI AGROTES THS MAKEDONIAS KAI THS QRAKHS</H4>
<LI><H4><A HREF="#04">[04]</a> OYRA ENOS XILIOMETROY STON PROMAXWNA META THN APOXWRHSH TWN AGROTWN APO TA PERISSOTERA MPLOKA THS BOREIAS ELLADAS</H4>
<LI><H4><A HREF="#05">[05]</a> PAGKOSMIA SYGKINHSH PROKALESE O QANATOS TOY DIASHMOY ITALOY HQOPOIOY MARTSELLO MASTROGIANNI</H4>
