<H3>OI EIDHSEIS ANALYTIKA</H3>
<H3><A NAME="A1">[A]</A> ESWTERIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</a> D.REPPAS: H KYBERNHSH METAKINHQHKE APO TIS ARXIKES THS QESEIS ENW OI AGROTES PARAMENOYN AMETAKINHTOI</H3>
<P>     H kybernhsh metakinhqhke apo tis arxikes ths qeseis enw oi
agrotes paramenoyn ametakinhtoi kai kratoyn toys dromoys kleistoys
tonise shmera o o kybernhtikos ekproswpos Dhmhtrhs Reppas.
<P>     Afhse de aixmes kata twn arxhgwn twn kommatwn ths
antipoliteyshs sto qema twn agrotikwn kinhtopoihsewn. &quot;Oi
politikoi arxhgoi miloyn me thn eyglwtth siwph toys kai apofeygoyn
na kataggeiloyn thn prajh twn apokleismwn twn dromwn&quot; shmeiwse o
Ypoyrgos Typoy kai prosqese oti prepei epiteloys aytos o
proklhtikos tropos apokleismoy twn dromwn na parei telos.
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</a> SYNEXIZETAI KAI SHMERA H APERGIA TWN NAYTIKWN - AKINHTOPOIHMENA TA PLOIA STA LIMANIA</H3>
<P>     Akinhtopoihmena sta limania paramenoyn ta ploia, kaqws oi
naytikoi synexizoyn thn apergia toys, ews ayrio to prwi.
<P>     Sto limani ths Qessalonikhs, paramenoyn egklwbismena ta ploia
&quot;Kink Minos&quot;, &quot;Kazantzakhs&quot; kai &quot;El Greco&quot;, enw akyrwqhkan 15
dromologia oxhmatagwgwn apo Peiraia kai Hrakleio Krhths.
<P>     Efoson synexistei o apokleismos toy limanioy kai tis
prosexeis hmeres anamenetai na dhmioyrghqoyn sobara problhmata
sthn trofodosia ths agoras ths Qessalonikhs.
<P>     O ypoyrgos Emporikhs Naytilias Stayros Soymakhs, xarakthrise
ta problhmata twn naytikwn pragmatika kai ojymena, tonise wstoso
oti den mporoyn na epilyqoyn ypo to kaqestws apeilwn.
<H3><A NAME="03">[03]</a> ANESTEILAN TIS KINHTOPOIHSEIS TOYS OI AGROTES THS MAKEDONIAS KAI THS QRAKHS</H3>
<P>     Thn anastolh twn agrotikwn kinhtopoihsewn sth Boreia Ellada
apofasise h Syntonistikh Epitroph Agwna Makedonias-Qrakhs, sth
shmerinh synedriash ths, poy pragmatopoihqhke sto ktirio ths
PASEGES.
<P>     Sthn anakoinwsh ths h Epitroph tonizei oti h apofash ayth
elhfqh enocei twn Xristoygennwn kai prokeimenoy na dwsei xrono
ston prwqypoyrgo na ylopoihsei thn yposxesh-desmeysh toy gia
synanthsh me tis Syntonistikes Epitropes gia dialogo kai epilysh
tym problhmatwn. Anaferetai, epishs, oti an oi desmeyseis aytes de
ginoyn prajh se eylogo xroniko diasthma &quot;o agrotikos kosmos einai
etoimos na diekdikhsei kai pali ta aithmata toy,klimakwnontas tis
kinhtopoihseis toy me dynamikotero tropo&quot;.
<P>     H Epitroph de qa aytodialyqei kai qa synedriasei ek neoy meta
tis giortes, gia na ektimhsei ti qa exei kanei h Kybernhsh sto
diasthma poy qa mesolabhsei kai na apanthsei analoga.
<H3><A NAME="04">[04]</a> OYRA ENOS XILIOMETROY STON PROMAXWNA META THN APOXWRHSH TWN AGROTWN APO TA PERISSOTERA MPLOKA THS BOREIAS ELLADAS</H3>
<P>     Oyra forthgwn dieqnwn metaforwn, mhkoys enos xiliometroy,
exei sxhmatisqei sto telwneio toy Promaxwna apo xqes to apogeyma,
meta thn apoxwrhsh twn agrotwn apo ta kyriotera mploka ths
Makedonias kai ths Qrakhs, poy eixe ws apotelesma thn
&quot;apeleyqerwsh&quot; dekadwn forthgwn poy briskontan akinhtopoihmena sth
Boreia Ellada.
<P>     Ta perissotera apo ta forthga einai boylgarika, poy
epistrefoyn sth geitonikh xwra, kaqws kai apo xwres-melh ths E.E.
<H3><A NAME="05">[05]</a> PAGKOSMIA SYGKINHSH PROKALESE O QANATOS TOY DIASHMOY ITALOY HQOPOIOY MARTSELLO MASTROGIANNI</H3>
<P>     Pagkosmia sygkinhsh prokalese o qanatos toy diashmoy italoy
hqopoioy Martselo Mastrogianni, poy afhse xtes, se hlikia 72
xronwn, thn teleytaia toy pnoh sto Parisi.
<P>     Se endeijh penqoys kai qlichs gia thn apwleia toy megaloy
hqopoioy, to syntribani ths Fontana nti Trebi sth Rwmh, opoy o
Mastrogianni eixe gyrisei thn perifhmh skhnh toy enagkalismoy me
thn Anita Ekmpergk sthn tainia &quot;Ntoltse Bita&quot; toy Fellini,
skepasthke me mayro pani.  Stis 4 to apogeyma shmera qa telestei
epimnhmosynh dehsh sthn ekklhsia toy Agioy Soypikioy sto Parisi,
enw sth synexeia h soros toy hqopoioy qa metaferqei sth Rwmh gia
thn tafh.
<P>     O diashmos hqopoios epasxe edw kai kairo apo karkino sto
pagkreas kai xtes exase thn anish maxh me ton qanato. Konta toy
mexri th stigmh poy ejepneyse, paremeinan h korh toy Kiara, h
prwhn syntrofos toy, Katrin Nteneb kai o stenos filos toy, Misel
Pikoli.
<P>     O Martsello Mastrogianni prwtagwnisthse se dekades tainies,
poy perasan sthn istoria toy pagkosmioy kinhmatografoy, alla
apotelese  kai ton hrwa toy atmosfairikoy komij &quot;Tajidi sthn
Toyloym&quot; toy diashmoy skitsografoy Milo Manara, poy basizetai se
ena senario toy Fellini, poy den egine pote tainia.
<P>     Prosfata emfanisthke sthn tainia &quot;Pret-a-porte&quot;, poy afora
ton kosmo ths modas, safws ghrasmenos, alla panta gohteytikos, se
enan rolo me plhqos kwmikwn stoixeiwn, poy o Mastrogianni
ajiopoihse sto epakro, synergazomenos me th synaderfo toy, Sofia
Lwren.
<P>     Ws shmantikh eixe xarakthrisei o italos hqopoios th
synergasia toy me ton Qeodwro Aggelopoylo,  stis tainies
&quot;Melissokomos&quot; kai &quot;To metewro bhma toy pelargoy&quot;.
<P>     &quot;O qanatos toy Martsello Mastrogianni apotelei apwleia zwhs
jai oxi mnhmhs&quot;, dhlwse o Ypoyrgos Politismoy, Eyaggelos
Benizelos, sxoliazontas ton xamo toy megaloy hqopoioy, poy &quot;efyge&quot;
xwris na afhsei pisw toy kapoion antajio toy diadoxo.
<H3><A NAME="06">[06]</a> APOSTOLH ALLHLEGGYHS  30 EKATOMMYRIWN STOYS PLHMMYROPAQEIS THS JANQHS APO THN ERT-3</H3>
<P>     Apostolh allhleggyhs jekina ayrio apo to G' Swma Stratoy gia
toys plhmmyropaqeis ths Janqhs. H apostolh organwqhke apo ton 102
FM ths ERT-3 mesa apo radiofwniko maraqwnio me skopo thn
oikonomikh kai ylikh bohqeia pros toys katoikoys ths Janqhs. Oi
prosfores se eidh jepernoyn se ajia ta 30.000.000 draxmes kai
sygkentrwqhkan apo synergeio ths Nomarxias, toy dhmoy Eleyqerioy-
Kordelioy kai toy Stratoy. To fortio qa paradoqei sto Nomarxh
Janqhs gia na prowqhqei stoys plhmmyropaqeis.
<H3><A NAME="07">[07]</a> KENTRO PROSTASIAS KATANALWTWN: &quot;PROSOXH STHN EPILOGH BENZINADIKOY&quot;</H3>
<P>     Mexri kai 560 drx. ofelos mporei na exei o odhgos se kaqe
&quot;foylarisma&quot; toy rezerboyar toy aytokinhtoy toy, analoga me to
benzinadiko poy epilegei.
<P>     Se deigmatolhptikh ereyna poy pragmatopoihse to Kentro
Prostasias Katanalwtwn (KEPKA) sta benzinadika toy nomoy
Qessalonikhs, diapistwse &quot;anoigma&quot; timwn poy anerxetai ews kai tis
14 drx. toso gia th super, oso kai gia thn amolybdh. Sygkekrimena,
gia th super kategrace katwtath timh 209 drx. kai anwtath 223
drx., enw gia thn amolybdh 193 drx. kai 207 drx., antistoixa. Ws
ek toytoy, ena &quot;foylarisma&quot; twn 40 litrwn benzinhs mporei na
kostisei mexri kai 560 drx. akribotera h fqhnotera, analoga me thn
periptwsh.
<P>     To KEPKA shmeiwnei oti se arketa prathria oi times ths
benzinhs diamorfwnontai arketa xamhlotera apo ekeines tis opoies
endeiktika anaferei to deltio poy ekdidei to ypoyrgeio Anaptyjhs.
Epishmainei de, oti &quot;meta thn apodesmeysh toy irakinoy petrelaioy,
oi times twn kaysimwn anamenetai na akoloyqhsoyn ptwtikh poreia
dieqnws&quot;.
<H3><A NAME="08">[08]</a> OLOKLHRWMENH PROSEGGISH TSEXIAS, SLOBAKIAS, OYGGARIAS, ROYMANIAS, MOLDABIAS, OYKRANIAS GIA TA ELLHNIKA AGROTIKA PROIONTA</H3>
<P>     Nwpa kai metapoihmena agrotika proionta ths xwras mas prowqei
mesw oloklhrwmenoy programmatos o Syndesmos Ejagwgewn Boreioy
Ellados (SEBE), stis agores ths Tsexias, ths Slobakias, ths
Oyggarias, ths Roymanias, ths Moldabias kai ths Oykranias.
<P>     Sto programma -poy ylopoieitai se synergasia me to ypoyrgeio
Gewrgias kai me th xrhmatodotikh sthrijh ths Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs-
symmetexoyn 24 epixeirhseis kai agrotikoi synetairismoi apo olh
thn Ellada. Prokeitai gia tis: EAS Paggaioy, Elaioyrgikh, GEOK,
ASEPOP Belbendoy, EAS Trikalwn, Paylidhs, EGS Giannitswn, AS
Zagoras Phlioy, INTERCOM, AS &quot;H Dhmhtra&quot;, EAS Phlioy, EAS
Alejandreias, AS Tympakioy, KON BERI AE, Synergatikh AE, EAS
Pierias, ZEYS, EAS Korinqias, EAS Almwpias, EGS Maleme, EAS
Pq]befar, EGS Mesologgioy, EAS Beroias kai EAS Qessalonikhs.
<P>     Apwteros stoxos ths drashs einai h organwmenh paroysia stis
eji anatolikoeyrwpaikes agores. Shmera, stis en logw xwres
pragmatopoioyntai men ejagwges ellhnikwn agrotikwn proiontwn,
wstoso krinontai mallon ws apospasmatikes kai sigoyra mh
antiproswpeytikes ths eyrytaths gkamas ths ellhnikhs paragwghs.
<P>     Kata to teleytaio dimhno, diorganwqhkan sto plaisio toy
programmatos dyo ebdomades prowqhshs ellhnikwn proiontwn se super
market twn xwrwn aytwn, kaqws kai ekdhlwseis geysignwsias se
kentrika jenodoxeia twn prwteyoyswn toys. Stis ekdhlwseis
ekteqhkan deigmata ths paragwghs twn symmetexoyswn epixeirhsewn,
enw prosklhqhkan ntopioi eisagwgeis kai xondremporoi, poy
enhmerwqhkan gia to programma apo stelexh toy ypoyrgeioy Gewrgias
kai toy SEBE.
<P>     Parallhla, dhmioyrghqhke katalogos me ta profil twn 24
epixeirhsewn-forewn, o opoios ektypwqhke se 4.000 antitypa.
Apestalh de, sta Epimelhthria kai toys ypoloipoys synergazomenoys
foreis twn eji xwrwn.
<P>     Ews to Dekembrio toy 1997 -opote kai qa oloklhrwqei to
programma- programmatizontai epixeirhmatikes apostoles se kaqe mia
apo tis agores-stoxoys.
<H3><A NAME="09">[09]</a> E.BENIZELOS: H EQNIKH TRAPEZA PREPEI NA LEITOYRGEI  WS IQYNOYSA DYNAMH STON XWRO TWN XORHGIWN</H3>
<P>     Tipote den mporei na ginei ston xwro toy politismoy, xwris na
yparxei mia stoixeiwdhs oikonomikh anesh, tonise o ypoyrgos
Politismoy, Eyaggelos Benizelos, se xairetismo poy aphyqyne kata
th diarkeia ths ekdhlwshs gia ta 30 xronia drasthriothtas toy
morfwtikoy idrymatos ths Eqnikhs Trapezas.
<P>     Paraklhsh pros toys dioikoyntes ths Eqnikhs Trapezas, wste
ayth na leitoyrghsei ws iqynoysa dynamh ston xwro twn xorhgiwn,
sto plaisio ths oikonomikhs kai politistikhs ths politikhs,
aphyqyne o k.Benizelos, poy synexarh toys epikefalhs  toy
idrymatos gia thn terastia symbolh toy oxi mono sthn paragwgh
biblioy, alla kai se oloklhro to fasma toy endiaferontos toy
Ypoyrgeioy Politismoy.
<H3><A NAME="10">[10]</a> PROTASH ANEGERSHS MNHMEIOY GIA TOYS EBRAIOYS THS QESSALONIKHS POY EJONTWQHKAN APO TOYS NAZI</H3>
<P>     Thn anegersh enos mnhmeioy, pros timhn twn dolofonhqentwn apo
toys Nazi Ebraiwn ths Qessalonikhs, proteine me epistolh toy pros
ton Organismo Politistikhs Prwteyoysas o Basileios Dolmas, prwhn
proedros ths DEQ.
<P>     &quot;Me thn anatolh toy 1997 h Qessalonikh kaleitai na dwsei fws
se olh thn Eyrwph. Gia na ginei ayto prepei prwta na fwtisoyme th
mia skoteinh selida sthn istoria ths polhs mas. Hrqe elpizw wra na
timhsoyme toys nekroys ths polhs mas poy jerizwse o nazismos sthn
teleytaia lailapa ths Eyrwphs kai toy kosmoy&quot;, shmeiwse o
k.Dolmas.
<P>     Ws idiaitera ajiologh xarakthrise thn idea toy k.Dolma o
proedros ths israhlitikhs koinothtas, Andreas Sefixa, poy tonise
|ti einai poly shmantiko na eyforoyntai apo  tetoia synaisqhmata
oloi oi polites, gia na diathrhqei h mnhmh ths dolofonias twn
Ebraiwn ths Qessalonikhs.
<P>     &quot;Den mas parexwrhqh gia to mnhmeio h plateia Eleyqerias, poy
eixe proteinei kai o k.Dolmas, alla ena alsylio sth symbolh twn
odwn Neas Egnatias kai Papanastasioy. To Ypoyrgeio Politismoy qa
diaqesei 20 ekatommyria draxmes gia thn anegersh toy mnhmeioy .
Hdh exei prokhryxqei panellhnios diagwnismos kai exei systaqei
epitroph poy qa krinei to ergo&quot;, shmeiwse o k.Sefixa.
<P>     Protash me paromoio periexomeno eixe ypoballei sthn ellhnikh
kybernhsh kai ta kommata, symfwna me plhrofories toy MPE, o
proedros ths Pagkosmias Diakoinoboyleytikhs Enwshs toy Ellhnismoy,
Dhmhtrhs Dollhs, boyleyths toy Ergatikoy Kommatos sth Biktoria
ths Aystralias.
<P>     Pros thn kateyqynsh ths diathrhshs ths mnhmhs kai ths
genikoterhs afypnishs twn Qessalonikewn, h Israhlitikh Koinothta
exei dromologhsei plhqos ekdhlwsewn se synergasia me ton Organismo
Politistikhs Prwteyoysas ths Eyrwphs.
<P>     H idrysh moyseioy, h diorganwsh enos festibal paradosiakwn
tragoydiwn kai kyriws h sygkentrwsh sth Qessalonikh twn
israhlitikwn koinothtwn oloklhrhs ths Eyrwphs, stoxeyoyn sth
diathrhsh ths mnhmhs, alla taytoxrona qa feroyn sthn polh
proswpikothtes dieqnoys kyroys, poy malista diakeintai qetika
apenanti sta eqnika mas  qemata.
<H3><A NAME="11">[11]</a> AYJHMENA METRA ASTYNOMEYSHS ENOCEI TWN EORTWN</H3>
<P>     Th lhch ayjhmenwn astynomikwn metrwn enocei twn eortwn twn
Xristoygennwn kai ths Prwtoxronias, gia thn apotelesmatikh
antimetwpish twn eidikwn problhmatwn poy parathroyntai thn periodo
ayth apofasise to Ypoyrgeio Dhmosias Tajhs.
<P>     Eidikotera, qa ayjhqoyn oi pezes peripolies astynomikwn, qa
lhfqoyn idiaitera metra asfaleias se xwroys xrhmatikwn synallagwn,
enw ystera apo synnenohsh me toys Organismoys Topikhs
Aytodioikhshs qa epidiwxqei h sygkrothsh miktwn synergeiwn
elegxwn, anaforika me to qema twn paranomwn mikropwlhtwn kai ths
epaiteias.
<H3><A NAME="12">[12]</a> STH QESSALONIKH APO 6 MEXRI 16 MARTIOY H 24h DIEQNHS SYNODOS TOY EYRWPAIKOY KOINOBOYLIOY NEWN</H3>
<P>     Sth Qessalonikh qa pragmatopoihqei apo 6 mexri 16 Martioy h
24h Dieqnhs Synodos toy Eyrwpaikoy Koinoboylioy Newn, sthn opoia
qa symmetasxoyn 250 maqhtes apo 22 toylaxiston xwres ths
Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs kai ths Kentrikhs kai Anatolikhs Eyrwphs. H
synqesh ths ellhnikhs apostolhs, poy qa symmetasxei sthn Synodo,
qa kaqoristei meqayrio, Kyriakh, sth diarkeia ths Genikhs
Syneleyshs toy Eyrwpaikoy Koinoboylioy Newn Ellados. Antikeimena
ths Genikhs Syneleyshs qa einai oi sxeseis metajy Eyrwpaikhs
Enwshs kai Toyrkias meta tis teleytaies apofaseis ths Eyrwpaikhs
Epitrophs kai toy Eyrwkoinoboylioy, h perifereiakh sygkrothsh ths
E.E. kai h arxh ths epikoyrikothtas, h enarmonish ths eisagwghs
twn maqhtwn twn xwrwn - melwn ths Enwshs sta Panepisthmia kai h
amtitqolojqatij^ politikh kai ta Syntagmatika Dikaiwmata se eqniko
kai atomiko epipedo.
<P>     To Eyrwpaiko Koinoboylio Newn exei systaqei basei koinotikwn
programmatwn kai apotelei mikrografia toy Eyrwkoinoboylioy.
Apoteleitai apo 15 epitropes sto protypo twn Epitropwn ths
Eyrwboylhs (Epitropes Periballontos, Ygeias, Ejwterikwn Ypoqesewn,
Oikonomikwn Qematwn, Anaptyjhs, Koinwnikwn Ypoqesewn,
Paideias,Neolaias kai Politismoy k.o.k.).
<P>     Oi apostoles poy ekproswpoyn kaqe xwra kaqorizontai apo tis
Genikes Syneleyseis twn eqnikwn pararthmatwn toy programmatos,
afoy prohghqei diagwnismos anamesa sta sxoleia ths xwras se
sygkekrimena qemata. Sthn Ellada to programma efarmozetai mexri
shmera mono sthn Qessalonikh kai thn Aqhna, oi opoies analambanoyn
ek peritrophs th diorganwsh twn dyo Eqnikwn Syndiaskecewn poy
pragmatopoioyntai kaqe anoijh kai fqinopwro antistoixa.
<P>     H Genikh Syneleysh ths Kyriakhs, poy qa kaqorisei thn
ellhnikh symmetoxh, qa pragmatopoihqei sto plaisio ths 3hs Eqnikhs
Syndiaskechs toy ellhnikoy swmateioy, poy arxise shmera me
kleistes synedriaseis twn epimeroys Epitropwn
<H3><A NAME="13">[13]</a> MHNYMA TOY G.PAPANDREOY PROS TON APODHMO ELLHNISMO ME THN EYKAIRIA TWN EORTWN</H3>
<P>     Mhnyma pros toys apodhmoys 'Ellhnes apesteile, me thn
eykairia twn eortwn twn Xristoygennwn kai toy Neoy 'Etoys, o
anaplhrwths ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn, Giwrgos Papandreoy.
<P>     Sto mhnyma toy o k. Papandreoy ekfrazei tis eyxes toy stoys
apodhmoys kai shmeiwnei, metajy allwn, oti tis giortines aytes
hmeres h skech olwn &quot;strefetai entonotera  pros ton Ellhnismo poy
diabiei sthn Oikoymenh kai poy, stis epaljeis toy Ellhnismoy kai
ths Orqodojias, ths paradoshs kai ths pisths, dinei kaqhmerina to
fwteino toy parwn&quot;.
<H3><A NAME="14">[14]</a> DIORISQHKAN WS ANWTERA STELEXH TOY LEYKOY OIKOY TREIS AMERIKANOI ELLHNIKHS KATAGWGHS</H3>
<P>     Sto diorismo epta anwterwn stelexwn toy Leykoy Oikoy, metajy
twn opoiwn kai triwn ellhnikhs katagwghs, anaferontai dhmosieymata
twn amerikanikwn efhmeridwn. Ton Tzwrtz Stefanopoylo poy apoxwrei
gia na didajei sto Koloympia, na synergasqei me to ABC kai na
gracei biblio, qa antikatasthsei o Ram Emanoyel.
<P>     Oi dyo apo toys treis ellhnikhs katagwghs neoproslhfqentes, o
Tzwn Pontesta kai h Sylbia Maqioys, diorisqhkan anaplhrwtes toy
neoy Proswparxh toy Leykoy Oikoy E.Mpooyls. H trith Biktoria Rant,
diorisqhke dieyqyntria toy Grafeioy toy k.Mpooyls.
<P>     H Oyasigkton Post grafei oti h epilogh twn stelexwn antanakla
thn protimhsh toy neoy Proswparxh se nea atoma, ejypna kai
synergasima metajy toys. Idiaiterh mneia ginetai gia th Sylbia
Maqioys, 31 etwn, gia thn opoia o k.Mpooyls anefere oti einai apo
tis lamproteres nees sthn Amerikh, enw ektimatai oti me thn
proswpikothta ths kai thn thlegeneia poy diaqetei, qa anadeixqei
se enan neo -qhlyko aythn th fora- Tzwrtz Stefanopoylo.
<H3><A NAME="15">[15]</a> O PROGRAMMATISMOS GIA TON AQLHTISMO MESA STO 1997 APASXOLHSE TOYS K. SHMITH KAI A. FOYRA STH  SHMERINH SYNANTHSH TOYS</H3>
<P>     O programmatismos gia ton aqlhtismo kaqws kai to qema twn
paranomwn stoixhmatwn, htan ta kyria shmeia anaforas, kata th
diarkeia ths synanthshs toy Yfypoyrgoy Aqlhtismoy Andrea Foyra me
ton Prwqypoyrgo Kwsta Shmith.
<P>      &quot;Enhmerwsa ton Prwqypoyrgo gia ton sxediasmo toy 1997, gia
tis aqlhtikes diorganwseis kai gia thn poreia diekdikhshs twn
Olympiakwn Agwnwn toy 2004&quot;, ypogrammise o k. Foyras, stoys
dhmosiografoys.
<P>     Anaferomenos sta paranoma stoixhmata, o Yfypoyrgos
Aqlhtismoy, xarakthrise thn katastash poy epikratei ws &quot;aqlia&quot;,
enw  epeshmane oti &quot;o OPAP anabaqmizei to logismiko toy kai
syndeetai me on line  syndesh me ola ta praktoreia toy. Kai mesa
sto 1997 ektos apo to oti qa yparjoyn ejelijeis, o OPAP qa
organwsei kainoyria paixnidia giati qa exei ayth th dynatothta&quot;.
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="B1">[B]</A> EJWTERIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
<H3><A NAME="16">[16]</a> T.TSILLER: TON TELEYTAIO KAIRO YPARXEI MIA PROSEGGISH STIS APOCEIS TOYRKIAS-RWSIAS WS PROS TO KYPRIAKO</H3>
<P>     Sobarh anhsyxia prokalei sthn Agkyra h prooptikh agoras
rwsikwn pyraylwn apo thn Kypro, symfwna me dhmosieyma ths
efhmeridas &quot;Sibontnia&quot;, poy sxoliazei th synanthsh sth Mosxa ths
Ypoyrgoy Ejwterikwn ths Toyrkias, Tansoy Tsiller, me ton rwso
omologo ths, Gebgkeni Primakwf.
<P>     Pantws, o rwsos Ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn, se erwthsh toyrkwn
dhmosiografwn sxetika me thn pwlhsh twn pyraylwn, apanthse oti h
xwra toy den qewrei toys pyrayloys &quot;edafoys- aeros&quot; ws epiqetika
opla.
<P>     Meta to telos twn synomiliwn, h Tansoy Tsiller dhlwse oti
&quot;ton teleytaio kairo yparxei mia proseggish stis apoceis Toyrkias-
Rwsias  ws pros to kypriako&quot;, xwris wstoso na epektaqei se
leptomereies sxetika me to periexomeno ayths ths proseggishs.
<H3><A NAME="17">[17]</a> DIACEYDEI O I.TOSEFSKI DHMOSIEYMATA POY EFERAN THN KYBERNHSH TWN SKOPIWN NA EXEI THN POLITIKH BOYLHSH GIA ALLAGH TOY ARQROY TOY SYNTAGMATOS POY AFORA STHN ONOMASIA</H3>
<P>     O presbhs Iban Tosefski poy ekproswpei thn PGDM stis
ellhnoskopianes synomilies ths Neas Yorkhs, dieceyse dhmosieymata
toy ellhnikoy typoy poy ton eferan na dhlwnei oti h kybernhsh toy
exei thn politikh boylhsh na proxwrhsei se allagh toy sxetikoy
arqroy toy Syntagmatos poy afora thn onomasia ths xwras toy.
<P>     O Tosefski se thlefwnikh synenteyjh toy ston kratiko
radiofwniko staqmo,  isxyristhke oti h dhlwsh toy parermhneyqhke
apo ta ellhnika mesa enhmerwshs. &quot;Ayto poy eipa egw, einai oti
yparxei politikh boylhsh ejeyreshs amoibaias, epwfeloys kai gia
tis dyo xwres lysh&quot;, ypogrammise.
<H3><A NAME="18">[18]</a> APEILES AKRODEJIWN TOYRKWN ANAGKASAN TON SYGGRAFEA GIASAR JELAK NA KATAFYGEI STHN ELBETIA</H3>
<P>     Apeiles kata ths zwhs toy dexetai apo akrodejies omades o
Toyrkos syggrafeas Giasar Kemal symfwna me dhmosieyma ths megalhs
kykloforias danezikhs efhmeridas &quot;Politiken&quot;. O Giasar Kemal, toy
opoioy to Efeteio epikyrwse thn poinh fylakishs poy eixe epiblhqei
prwtodika me pentaeth anastolh, katefyge sthn Elbetia. Opws
anaferei h efhmerida h syggrafeas den zhthse politiko asylo, alla
aplws katefyge sthn Elbetia  gia na mporesei na doylecei xwris na
apeileitai, alla kai se endeijh diamartyrias  gia tis pieseis  poy
qelei na askhsei to toyrkiko kratos.
<P>     Filos toy Kemal apantwntas se erwthseis toy dhmosiografoy
Niels Barfoed ths &quot;Politiken&quot; dhlwse ta ejhs: &quot;O Giasar Kemal den
zhthse asylo apo thn Elbetia. Emeis toy zhthsame na erqei sth xwra
ayth giati fobomastan oti qa paqei kako. Palaiotera eixan
epixeirhsei na kacoyn ton Aziz Nesin. O Kemal dexotan apeiles apo
akrodejioys. Ton teleytaio kairo eidikes dynameis  mesa sto kratos
estrecan tis drasthriothtes toys enantion twn dianooymenwn kai
skotwsan Koyrdoys dhmosiografoys&quot;.
<P>     O idios o syggrafeas epishmane oti to Eqniko Symboylio
Asfaleias kai oi stratiwtikoi  sthn Toyrkia deixnoyn eyaisqhsia
otan prokeitai gia epikriseis poy dexetai to nomiko systhma ths
xwras kai den anagnwrizoyn stoys syggrafeis to dikaiwma na askoyn
kritikh .&quot;To na askei kaneis kritikh einai ena fysiko dikaiwma.
Omws sthn Toyrkia einai adikhma. To kratos twra mas apeilei me
qanato kai me poines fylakishs. H Toyrkikh Dhmokratia ktisthke
panw se egklhmata eis baros lawn. Sthn Anatolikh Toyrkia oi
Koyrdoi kai oi syggeneis moy jerizwnontai dia ths bias apo toys
topoys toys&quot; ypogrammise.
<H3><A NAME="19">[19]</a> GIA DIAFQORA KATHGOREITAI O PRWQYPOYRGOS THS BOYLGARIAS, Z.BINTENOF, APO BOYLEYTH THS ANTIPOLITEYSHS</H3>
<P>     Salo exei prokalesei sth Boylgaria h anoixth epistolh toy
boyleyth  ths &quot;Enwshs Dhmokratikwn Dynamewn&quot;, Entbin Soygkaref,
sthn opoia kathgoroyntai gia diafqora o prwqypoyrgos Zan Bintenof
kai alloi epta anwtatoi ajiwmatoyxoi, metajy twn opoiwn o
dioikhths ths Kentrikhs Trapezas, Lioympomir Filipof, o proedros
ths Epitrophs Taxydromeiwn kai Thlepikoinwniwn, Lioympomir Kolarof
kai o proedros ths Boylgarikhs Etairias Thlepikoinwniwn, Mixahl
Ntanof.
<P>     Meta apo th dhmosiopoihsh ths epistolhs, shmera o k.Soygkaref
thn apedwse ston Geniko Eisaggelea, Iban Tatartsef, mazi me alla,
apokalyptika, opws isxyrizetai, eggrafa, poy apodeiknyoyn tis
diastaseis poy feretai na exei parei h diafqora sthn anwtath
klimaka ths ejoysias sth Boylgaria.
<P>     Se prwtoselida dhmosieymata toys oi efhmerides &quot;24 Wres&quot; kai
&quot;Kontinent&quot; ths Sofias tonizoyn oti o k.Soygkaref kathgorei ton
prwqypoyrgo, Z.Bintenof, oti afhse na idryqei o &quot;egklhmatikos
oikonomikos sxhmatismos Orion&quot;, ston opoio drasthriopoioyntai
atoma toy stenoy periballontos toy, opws o  prwhn dieyqynths toy
grafeioy Typoy toy Ypoyrgikoy Symboylioy, Krasimir Raintofski, o
proedros ths Boylgarikhs Etairias Thlepikoinwniwn, M.Ntanof kai o
pq|edqor ths Epitrophs Taxydromeiwn kai Thlepikoinwniwn,
L.Kolarof.
<P>     Symfwna me tis kataggelies toy k.Soygkaref, poy einai kai
antiproedros ths koinoboyleytikhs Epitrophs gia thn patajh ths
diafqoras, o oikonomikos sxhmatismos &quot;Orion&quot; eyqynetai gia
paranomoys oikonomikoys xeirismoys, metajy twn opoiwn katatassei
kai thn idrysh &quot;me klemmeno kefalaio&quot; ths Boylgarikhs Agrotikhs
kai Biomhxanikhs Trapezas.
<H3><A NAME="20">[20]</a> ANOIXTO AFHSE O OLLANDOS YPOYRGOS EJWTERIKWN  TO ENDEXOMENO EKTAKTHS SYGKLHSHS SYMBOYLIOY KORYFHS THS EE, THN PROSEXH ANOIJH</H3>
<P>     Anoixto afhse to endexomeno na sygklhqei thn prosexh anoijh,
ektakto Symboylio Koryfhs ths Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs gia thn anaqewrhsh
ths synqhkhs toy Maastrixt,  o Ollandos ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn Xans
Ban Mirlo, h xwra toy opoioy analambanei thn Proedria ths EE apo
1hs Ianoyarioy 1997.
<P>     Opws anefere to BBC, epikaloymeno dhlwseis toy Ollandoy
ypoyrgoy,
h sygklish toy symboylioy qa ejarthqei apo to apotelesma twn
bretanikwn boyleytikwn eklogwn poy anamenetai na diejaxqoyn to
argotero mexri ton Maio.
<P>     Symfwna me ton Ban Mirlo, h kybernhsh toy antimetwpizei
sobara th syglish enos ektaktoy symboylioy. O logos einai ta
apotelesmata twn bretanikwn eklogwn, an dhladh qa tis
janakerdisoyn oi synthrhtikoi poy den qeloyn megales allages sth
synqhkh toy Maastrixt kai frenaroyn me kaqe tropo tis ergasies ths
Diakybernhtikhs h an qa tis kerdisoyn oi Ergatikoi poy einai poly
pio anoixtoi stis proteinomenes metarryqmiseis ths koinotikhs
synqhkhs.
<P>     Meta tis bretanikes ekloges oi &quot;15&quot; hgetes ths Eyrwpaikhs
Enwshs qa prepei na paroyn  mia taktikhs fyshs apofash gia na
etoimasoyn me ton kalytero dynato tropo to programmatismeno
symboylio sto Amsterntam poy qa ginei stis 16 Ioynioy to opoio qa
prepei na epikyrwsei qewrhtika toylaxiston ta osa exoyn symfwnhqei
gia thn anaqewrhsh ths synqhkhs toy Maastrixt apo th
Diakybernhtikh Diaskech, sxoliase to BBC.
<H3><A NAME="21">[21]</a> O N.ERMPAKAN AFAIREI ARMODIOTHTES APO THN TANSOY TSILLER</H3>
<P>     Ws prospaqeia ypobaqmishs toy roloy ths Tansoy Tsiller,
ejelabe o toyrkikos typos thn apofash toy prwqypoyrgoy Netsmentin
Ermpakan na periorisei orismenes armodiothtes toy ypoyrgeioy
Ejwterikwn.
<P>     O Ermpakan, me egkyklio-ekplhjh, opws th xarakthrizei h
efhmerida &quot;Xoyrriet&quot;, afairei apo to ypoyrgeio Ejwterikwn thn
armodiothta syntonismoy olwn twn oikonomikwn kai politistikwn
sxesewn me toys Toyrkoys toy ejwterikoy kai tis islamikes xwres,
tis opoies metabibase ston ypoyrgo Epikrateias Ampntoylax Gkioyl.
<P>     H efhmerida tonizei oti me thn energeia ayth oi armodiothtes
toy ypoyrgeioy Ejwterikwn periorizontai mono sthn prowqhsh twn
politikwn sxesewn enw  anabaqmizetai o &quot;skiwdhs&quot; ypoyrgos
Ampntoylax Gkioyl poy anhkei stis tajeis toy &quot;Kommatos Eyhmerias&quot;.
<P>     Kata thn efhmerida, ypobaqmizetai epishs kai o ypoyrgos
Epikrateias Namik Kemal Zeympek poy anhkei sto komma ths
k.Tsiller, o opoios proedreyei twn miktwn oikonomikwn epitropwn
Toyrkias-Kazakstan kai Toyrkias- Azermpaitzan.
<H3><A NAME="22">[22]</a> GIA TRITO MHNA APEXOYN APO TA MAQHMATA OI ALBANOI FOITHTES TOY PANEPISTHMIOY TWN SKOPIWN</H3>
<P>     Gia trito synexh mhna apexoyn apo ta maqhmata toys oi albanoi
foithtes toy Paidagwgikoy Tmhmatos toy panepisthmioy twn Skopiwn,
kaqws to aithma toys, poy afora sth diejagwgh twn maqhmatwn
apokleistika sthn Albanikh glwssa, paramenei alyto.
<P>     Oi ekproswpoi twn albanwn foithtwn, oi opoioi ejeqesan
epaneilhmmena to aithma toys sto Ypoyrgeio Paideias ths PGDM,
dhlwnoyn apofasismenoi na synexisoyn thn apoxh mexri th dikaiwsh
toys.
<P>     Opws metedwse h kratikh thleorash twn Skopiwn, oi foithtes
zhtoyn twra thn paraithsh toy proedroy kai toy genikoy grammatea
toy tmhmatos, yposthrizontas pws arnoyntai na akoysoyn ta aithmata
toys.
<P>     Se dhlwsh toy sto kratiko thleoptiko kanali, o proedros toy
Paidagwgikoy Tmhmatos aperrice tis kathgories twn albanwn
foithtwn, yposthrizontas pws to tmhma akoloyqei rhta tis diatajeis
toy nomoy peri tritobaqmias ekpaideyshs, o opoios gia toys
albanoys foithtes toy Paidagwgikoy Tmhmatos problepei thn paradosh
meroys kai oxi olwn twn maqhmatwn sthn albanikh glwssa.
<H3><A NAME="23">[23]</a> NEA KATADIKH THS AGKYRAS APO TO EYRWPAIKO DIKASTHRIO ANQRWPINWN DIKAIWMATWN</H3>
<P>     To Eyrwpaiko Dikasthrio Anqrwpinwn Dikaiwmatwn katadikase,
symfwna me syntomo thlegrafhma toy praktoreioy Reuter, thn Agkyra
na plhrwsei apozhmiwseis kai ta dikastika ejoda se ypoqesh Koyrdoy
poy to 1992 synelhfqh kai basanisqhke ws tromokraths apo tis
toyrkikes arxes.
<P>     Ypenqymizetai oti prin liges meres katadikasqhke pali h
Toyrkia gia thn ypoqesh ths ellhnokyprias Titinas Loizidoy,
apofash poy xarakthrizetai staqmos me eyryteres epiptwseis, afoy
afora sto dikaiwma epikoinwnias kai perioysias sthn katexomenh
Kypro.
<H3><A NAME="24">[24]</a> BOMBARDISTHKAN STRATOPEDA TOY RKK STO BOREIO IRAK</H3>
<P>     Syntonismenes epixeirhseis me th symmetoxh bombardistikwn
aeroskafwn enantion stratopedwn toy RKK sto Boreio Irak, alla kai
th Notioanatolikh Toyrkia, pragmatopoioyn oi toyrkikes dynameis
asfaleias.
<P>     Symfwna me thn efhmerida &quot;Xoyrriet&quot;, eji polemika aeroskafh F-
16 poy apogeiwqhkan apo thn aeroporikh bash toy Ntigiarmpakir,
pragmatopoihsan ejodoys stoys &quot;tromokratikoys stoxoys&quot; Metina kai
Xakoyr, stoys opoioys parathrhqhke kinhtikothta. (Prokeitai gia ta
dyo stratopeda opoy prospaqoyn na stegastoyn ta melh toy RKK sto
Boreio Irak).
<P>     Stratiwtikes phges tonisan pws sta toyrkika aeriwqoymena,
pareixan yposthrijh kai elikoptera typoy Cobra, enw armodioi eipan
oti kai sta dyo stratopeda kataferqhke xtyphma sto RKK kai pws den
einai gnwsth akomh h zhmia poy epeferan oi epixeirhseis.
<P>     H efhmerida &quot;Toyrkie&quot;, afoy anaferetai stis idies plhrofories
gia to bombardismo twn stratopedwn toy RKK sto Boreio Irak,
prosqetei oti synexizontai oi epixeirhseis enantion toy RKK kai
entos ths xwras, enw armodioi eipan oti oi epixeirhseis twn
dynamewn asfaleias entaqhkan stis perioxes Sirnak, Xakiari kai
Ban.
<H3><A NAME="25">[25]</a> SYNANTHSH MPERISA - ROYGKOBA STA TIRANA</H3>
<P>     Tis eyxaristies toys pros tis Hnwmenes Politeies gia &quot;to
endiaferon poy deixnoyn gia thn epilysh toy problhmatos toy
Kossyfopedioy&quot;, ejefrasan amesws meta th synanthsh toys sta
Tirana, o Albanos proedros, Sali Mperisa kai o hgeths twn
Albanofwnwn toy Kossyfopedioy, Impraxim Roygkoba.
<P>     Opws metedwse h Albanikh Thleorash, oi dyo politikoi
xarakthrisan ws &quot;aparaithth&quot; thn energopoihsh ths Eyrwpaikhs
Enwshs kai ths Gallias gia thn epilysh toy problhmatos aytoy kai
xairetisan tis diamartyries twn foithtwn toy Beligradioy, oi
opoies, opws tonisan, &quot;ajizei na yposthrixtoyn&quot;.
