<H2>European Business News (EBN), 96-12-20</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/europe/ebn">European Business News (EBN)</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-19.ebn.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="97-01-02.ebn.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The European Business News Server at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.ebn.co.uk/">http://www.ebn.co.uk/</A>&gt;</H4>
<H4>Page last updatedDecember 20 1000 CET</H4>
<HR>
<H3>CONTENTS</H3>
<H4>
<DIR>
  <LI><A HREF="#01">[01]</A> EU ministers agree to compromise on easing cuts in fishing quotas
  <LI><A HREF="#02">[02]</A> German economic data suggest long-term price stability
  <LI><A HREF="#03">[03]</A> CS Holding establishes new credit-risk system
