<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/ant1">Antenna Radio News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-16.ant1.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-19.ant1.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: Antenna Radio &lt;<A HREF="http://www.antenna.gr">http://www.antenna.gr</A>&gt; - email: <A HREF="mailto:antenna@antenna.ath.forthnet.gr">antenna@antenna.ath.forthnet.gr</A></H4>
<H3>News in Greek, of 18/12/1996</H3>
<HR>
<H3>TITLOI</H3>
<H4>
<UL>
<LI>KYPRIAKO
<LI>AGROTIKO
<LI>NAYTERGATIKO
</UL>
</H4>
<HR>
<H4>KYPRIAKO</H4>
Entonh kinhtikothta gia to Kypriako,se Aqhna, Leykwsia kai Londino opoy
shmera o ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn Qeodwros Pagkalos synantatai me ton bretano
omologo toy Malkom Rifkint.
<H4>NAYTERGATIKO</H4>
Epeisodia ginontai ayth thn wra sto limani toy Peiraia.Odhgoi forthgwn
aytokinhtwn prospaqhsan na spasoyn to mploko twn apergwn naytergatwn , wste
na fortwqei mia ntalika sto DAIDALOS .
<H4>ASFALISTRA</H4>
Diaceydei to ypoyrgeio Anaptyjhs plhrofories oti prokeitai na epiblhqei
ektakth eisfora apo tis asfalistikes etairies gia thn kalych toy elleimatos
toy epikoyrikoy toys tameioy.
<H4>JANQH</H4>
Ta metra poy prokeitai na parei h kybernhsh gia thn enisxysh twn
plhmmyropaqwn ths Janqhs qa anakoinwsei shmera o ypoyrgos PEXWDE Kwstas
Laliwths poy episkeptetai shmera thn perioxh.
<H4>Kaysima</H4>
Drastikh meiwsh twn timwn diylisthrioy twn kaysimwn, anamenetai na
anakoinwsei to meshmeri, to Ypoyrgeio Anaptyjhs.
<H4>MHTSOTAKHS</H4>
Sth Nea Dhmokratia,o Kwnstantinos Mhtsotakhs se synenteyjh toy sto
periodiko KRAS dhlwnei oti den prokeitai na paei se synedrio-maimoy, poy
den qa einai timio kai antiproswpeytiko.
<H4>STAH</H4>
Ayrio qa apofasisei o proistamenos ths eisaggeleias Prwtodikwn Aqhnwn
Anastasios Kanellopoylos an stoixeioqeteitai poiniko adikhma meta thn
arnhsh ths dhmosiografoy Ellhs Stah na kataqesei xqes sthn ejetastikh
epitroph ths boylhs poy diereyna thn ypoqesh toy kazinoy sto Floisbo.
<H4>PEROY</H4>
Se ejelijh briskontai oi diapragmateyseis twn peroybianwn antartwn toy
kinhmatos Toypak Amaroy, poy exoyn syllabei 200 omhroys sthn katoikia toy
iapwna presbeyth sth Lima me ton ypoyrgo Eswterikwn toy Peroy,Xoyan
Mpriones Ntabila. Metajy twn omhrwn einai oi ypoyrgoi Ejwterikwn kai
Gewrgias toy Peroy.
<H4>XWMATERH</H4>
Kleisth shmera h xwmaterh Anw Liosiwn kai den apokleietai to dhmotiko
Symboylio na apofasisei apoce kleisimo ths xwmaterhs ep aoriston.
<H4>GERAKAS MARAQWNOS</H4>
Thn anagkh na ginoyn epeigontws erga sth lewforo Maraqwnos wste na mhn
qrhnhsoyme kai alla qymata tonise, milwntas ston ANT1, o dhmarxos Geraka
Giannhs Papadogiwrgakhs.
<H4>AQLHTIKO</H4>
Thn epanalhch toy agwna mpasket Arh- Mpesiktas poy eixe diakopei logw
epeisodiwn apofasise h FIMPA.
<P>O agwnas qa ginei sthn Aqhna stis 7 Ianoyarioy kekleismenwn twn qyrwn.
<P>Oi dyo omades timwrhqhkan me prostimo 45 xiliadwn markwn h kaqe mia enw oi
prwtagwnistes twn epeisodiwn Aggelidhs kai Alejanter timwrhqhkan me 3 kai 4
agwnistikes antistoixa.
<H4>DIEQNH</H4>
Dyo stratiwtikoi skotwqhkan kai enas traymatisthke kata thn ptwsh toy
elikopteroy toy opoioy epebainan konta sthn aeroporikh bash Malino sta
perixwra ths Mosxas, symfwna me thlegrafhma toy praktoreioy Interfaj.
<P>O proedros toy Iran Akmpar Xasemi Rafsanzani anamenetai ayrio sthn Toyrkia
gia epishmh episkech poy apoblepei sthn peraiterw sysfijh twn sxesewn
metajy twn dyo xwrwn, para tis synexizomenes prospaqeies twn HPA na
apomonwsoyn to kaqestws ths Texeranhs.
<P>H Genikh Syneleysh toy Organismoy Hnwmenwn Eqnwn epikyrwse xqes dia bohs th
``systash-protash`` toy Symboylioy Asfaleias gia thn eklogh toy Kofi Annan
sto ajiwma toy Genikoy Grammatea gia mia pentaetia,dhladh apo thn 1-h
Ianoyarioy 1997 ws kai thn 31-h Dekembrioy 2001.
<P>Ekrhjh bombas sygklonise to kentro toy Lagos-ths megalyterhs polhs ths
Nighrias -me apotelesma na traymatistoyn sobara 12 stratiwtes,metedwsan
topikoi radiostaqmoi.
<P> H ekrhjh shmeiwqhke sthn synoikia Alaoysa me apotelesma na katastrafei
olosxerws ena lewforeio poy metefere toys stratiwtes.
<P>Ton arxitromokrath Karlos anekrinan ayth thn ebdomada sto Parisi dyo
praktores ths bretanikhs Skotlant Giarnt, sxetika me tis ypoqeseis ths
apopeiras dolofonias enos epixeirhmatia kai ths ekrhjhs bombas se mia
Trapeza toy Londinoy, anaferei sth shmerinh ths ekdosh h efhmerida Taims.
