<H2>Antenna: News in Greek, 96-12-19</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/ant1">Antenna Radio News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-18.ant1.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-30.ant1.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: Antenna Radio &lt;<A HREF="http://www.antenna.gr">http://www.antenna.gr</A>&gt; - email: <A HREF="mailto:antenna@antenna.ath.forthnet.gr">antenna@antenna.ath.forthnet.gr</A></H4>
<H3>News in Greek, of 19/12/1996</H3>
<HR>
<H3>TITLOI</H3>
<H4>
<UL>
<LI>AGROTIKO
<LI>NAYTERGATIKO
<LI>KYPRIAKO
</UL>
</H4>
<HR>
<H4>AGROTIKO</H4>
Apo ta mploka twn eqnikwn odwn sthn Aqhna shmera oi agrotes poy katebhkan
me perissotera apo 100 lewforeia. Apo thn plateia Baqh opoy briskontai
sygkentrwmenoi aytthn thn wra oi agrotes qa poreytoyn pros to ypoyrgeio
Gewrgias kai sth synexeia pros th Boylh.
<H4>APERGIES</H4>
Me ton ypoyrgo Emporikhs Naytilias Stayro Soymakh synantwntai oi
naytergates poy nwritera pragmatopoihsan syllallhthrio sthn plateia
Karaiskakh kai poreia pros to ypoyrgeio.
<H4>BOMBA</H4>
H tromokratikh Organwsh 17 Noembrh h o ELA brisketai pisw apo thn
bombistikh epiqesh xqes brady sthn SITIMPANGK sto Xalandri ektima h
antitromokratikh yphresia.Wstoso kamia organwsh den exei analabei thn
eyqynh gia thn epiqesh.
<H4>KYPROS</H4>
To Eyrwpaiko Dikasthrio gia ta anqrwpina dikaiwmata katadikase thn Toyrkia
meta apo prosfygh ellhnokyprias daskalas poy sterhqhke th dynatothta
prosbashs sthn perioysia ths , sthn katexomenh Kypro meta thn toyrkikh
eisbolh to 74 .
<H4>PEROY</H4>
Sto Peroy, stasimh paramenei h katastash sth Lima opoy antartes toy
kinhmatos Toypak Amaroy kratoyn ekatontades omhroys sthn presbeia ths
Iapwnias.
<H4>STAH</H4>
Diwjh gia ceydh anwmoti kataqesh askhse enantion ths dhmosiografoy Ellhs
Stah o proistamenos ths eisaggelias prwtodikwn Anastasios Kanellopoylos gia
thn arnhsh ths na kataqesei sthn ejetastikh epitroph ths Boylhs gia to
kazino toy Floisboy.
<H4>MASTROGIANNI</H4>
Ena apo ta iera terata ths 7hs texnhs,o Italos hqopoios Martsello
Mastrogianni peqane shmera sto spiti toy sto Parisi se hlikia 72 xronwn kai
meta apo polymhnh maxh me ton karkino poy ton prosebale sto pagkreas.H
anakoinwsh toy qanatoy toy egine gnwsth apo to oikogeneiako periballon toy
hqopoioy.
<H4>LAQROMETANASTES</H4>
18 Irakinoi laqrometanastes, metajy twn opiown kai pente paidia, kratoyntai
sto Astynomiko Tmhma ths Samoy. Entopisqhkan kai synelhfqhsan to prwi apo
andres toy Limenikoy sthn perioxh Kampoy Boyrliwtwn toy nhsioy.
<H4>PAPAPA EQELONTES</H4>
Kampania gia to pneyma toy eqelontismoy jekinhse o ANTENNA ep eykairia twn
hmerwn twn Xristoygennwn. Hdh h antapokrish toy koinoy einai terastia kai
idiaitera sygkinhtikh.
<H4>JANQH</H4>
Ayrio jekina to karabani me ta forthga poy qa metaferoyn stoys
plhmmyropaqeis ths Janqhs th bohqeia h opoia sygkentrwqhke me prwtoboylia
toy ANTENNA,ths Arxiepiskophs,toy Dhmoy Aqhnaiwn kai ths KEDKE.
<P>Entypwsiakh paramenei en tw metajy h antapokrish politwn kai epixeirhsewn
sthn prwtoboylia.
<P>H epixeirhsh Foyrlhs prosefere 50 hlektrikes koyzines enw h farmakobiomhxania
Mpitsam 5 dwdekades embolia Hpatitidas A.
<P>O ariqmos logariasmoy sthn Eqnikh Trapeza gia thn kataqesh xrhmatwn einai
669/470192- 54.
<H4>AQLHTIKO</H4>
Tesseris mhnes qa parameinei ektos ghpedwn o paikths toy Olympiakoy
Pentragk Tzortzebits.
<H4>ANALYTIKA</H4>
Analytika oi eidhseis toy Antenna sth nea mas dieyqynsh http://www.antenna.gr
<H4>&copy; ANT1-Radio 1996</H4>
