<TITLE>Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in Greek (AM), 96-12-20</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<center><a href="/info"><IMG SRC="/gifs/hrnet.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="[HR-Net Banner]"></a><BR></center>

<H2>Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in Greek (AM), 96-12-20</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/mpeb">Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-19_1.mpeb.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-20_1.mpeb.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Macedonian Press Agency at <A HREF="http://www.mpa.gr">http://www.mpa.gr</A> and <A HREF="http://www.hri.org/MPA">http://www.hri.org/MPA</A>.</H4>
<HR>
<H4>Web Posted: 09:22 GMT+2</H4>
<H3>SYNTOMO PRWINO DELTIO THS 20.12.96</H3>
Entash dhmioyrghqhke sth boylh, kata th syzhthsh toy proypologismoy toy
1997, me aformh ta agrotika qemata. O arxhgos ths ajiwmatikhs
antipoliteyshs ejapelyse frastikh epiqesh kata ths kybernhshs. Apokalese
ton prwqypoyrgo &quot;ceyth&quot;, epiteqhke kata toy ypoyrgoy Gewrgias legontas oti
exei &quot;qrasos&quot; enw ligo nwritera kathgorhse ton yfypoyrgo Eqnikhs Oikonomias
gia &quot;aneyqynothta&quot;. Amesh htan h antidrash toy prwqypoyrgoy o opoios
kathgorhse ton Miltiadh Ebert gia gia dhmagwgia, sxoliazontas to yfos, ton
tropo kai toys xarakthrismoys poy xrhsimopoihse. &quot;Oi ybristes den exoyn
prooptikh kai ayto to apedeije o ellhnikos laos me th chfo toy,
katachfizontas th N.D. stis ekloges&quot;, tonise o k.Shmiths. Sth syzhthsh
parenebhsan oi proedroi toy SYN, toy DHKKI oi opoioi afoy tonisan oti h
kybernhsh den efarmozei agrotikh politikh se eqniko epipedo, zhthsan na
epanejetasei th stash ths kai na arxisei dialogo me toys agrotes.
<P>Synedriazei to meshmeri h Panqessalonikh Syntonistikh Epitroph prokeimenoy
na kaqorisei thn peraiterw stash ths meta thn akarph xqesinh synanthsh sthn
Aqhna 16meloys antiproswpeias me ton ypoyrgo Gewrgias, Stefano Tzoymaka,
kai ton yfypoyrgo ston prwqypoyrgo, Giwrgo Pasxalidh. Oi dyo ypoyrgoi
epanelaban th qesh toy k. Shmith oti o prwqypoyrgos qa dextei ayqhmeron
toys ekproswpoys twn agrotwn, gia dialogo panw sta problhmata toys, ypo thn
proypoqesh oti qa dwsoyn sthn kykloforia toys odikoys komboys poy exoyn
mplokarei. Apo thn pleyra toys oi ekproswpoi twn agrotwn dhlwsan oti
epistrefoyn sta mploka kai qa synexisoyn tis kinhtopoihseis toys.
<P>Tria oxhmatagwga paremeinan kai xqes &quot;egklwbismena&quot; sto limani ths
Qessalonikhs, ejaitias ths panelladikhs apergias twn naytergatwn. Prokeitai
gia ta KING MINOS, KAZANTZAKHS kai EL GRECO. To &quot;mplokarisma&quot; toy limanioy
eixe synepeia to synwstismo 110 forthgwn -ta opoia perimenan ta oxhmatagwga-
alla kai ton analogo ekneyrismo twn odhgwn toys. Epipleon, akyrwqhkan ta
programmatismena, 15 dromologia oxhmatagwgwn apo Peiraia kai Hrakleio
Krhths. Kata synepeia den fqanoyn sth Qessalonikh ta emporeymata kyriws apo
thn Krhth, kaqws -stadiaka- forthga me emporeymata apo thn Aqhna
katafernoyn na erxontai kai odikws. Efoson synexisqei o apokleismos toy
limanioy kai kata tis prosexeis hmeres, anamenetai na dhmioyrghqoyn sobara
problhmata sthn trofodosia ths agoras ths Qessalonikhs.
<P>Thn symparastash toy, sta dikaia, opws ta onomazei, aithmata twn agrotwn,
ejefrase to Dhmotiko Symboylio toy Dhmoy Qessalonikhs, me chfisma toy kai
kalese ton Prwqypoyrgo na dexqei na syzhthsei me antiproswpeia twn agrotwn
gia thn enarjh enos oysiastikoy kai kalopistoy dialogoy.
<P>Epiqesh enantion ths kybernhshs, gia ton tropo me ton opoio antimetwpizei
toys agrotes kai toys naytergates ejapelyse, me anakoinwsh toy, to Grafeio
Typoy ths Kentrikhs Epitrophs toy KKE. &quot;H qatserikh adiallajia kai
epiqetikothta enantion twn agrotwn kai twn allwn ergazomenwn einai to
basiko xarakthristiko ths kybernhshs toy PASOK, opws apodeixthke kai apo
thn ek neoy aporrich twn agrotikwn aithmatwn&quot;, tonizei sthn anakoinwsh toy
to KKE.
<P>O 62xronos Manwlhs Rodiths apo to Hrakleio Krhths peqane apo kardia enw
parakoloyqoyse ta epeisodia metajy naytergatwn kai odhgwn forthgwn sto
limani toy Peiraia. Tetamenh htan h katastash kai se alla limania ths xwras.
Oi naytergates apofasisan paratash ths apergias toys kai oi ploiokthtes
apeiloyn me apolyseis twn apergwn.
<P>Gia thn Aigypto anaxwrei shmera o Proedros ths Dhmokratias Kwsths
Stefanopoylos, opoy qa pragmatopoihsei tetrahmerh epishmh episkech,
synodeyomenos apo ton ypoyrgo Ejwterikwn Q.Pagkalo.
<P>Sth Qessalonikh qa erxetai thn Kyriakh o Proedros toy DHKKI, Dhmhtrhs
Tsobolas, prokeimenoy na parastei se ekdhlwsh toy kommatos toy gia thn
prwth epeteio ths Idrytikhs toy Diakhryjhs. O k.Tsobolas qa exei to prwi
ths Kyriakhs epafes me stelexh toy kommatos kai foreis ths Qessalonikhs,
sta grafeia toy DHKKI, to apogeyma qa paraxwrhsei synenteyjh Typoy, enw
stis 9 to brady qa parastei se synestiash gia th symplhrwsh enos etoys apo
thn idrysh toy kommatos toy.
<P>Poinikh diwjh gia ceydh kataqesh kata ths dhmosiografoy Ellhs Stah askhse o
Proistamenos ths Eisaggelias Aqhnwn Anastasios Kanellopoylos. H diwjh
askeitai epeita apo arnhsh ths k. Stah na dwsei dieykriniseis sthn armodia
Ejetastikh Epitroph ths Boylhs gia to ypomnhma poy kateqese anaforika me
thn agora dyo akinhtwn.
<P>Th Qessalonikh kai th Xalkidikh qa episkefqoyn entos twn hmerwn trianta
ychlobaqma stelexh toy megaloy rwsikoy tajidiwtikoy organismoy VAO
INTOURIST, poy prosfata ypegrace symfwnia me thn ellhnikh etaireia Kinissi
Tour Operator. Oi Rwsoi toyristikoi praktores, oi opoioi qa episkefqoyn thn
Ellada sto plaisio toy ethsioy &quot;tajidioy kinhtroy&quot; poy diorganwnei h rwsikh
etaireia, qa syndyasoyn thn episkech toys sth Qessalonikh me ton eortasmo
ths Politistikhs Prwteyoysas ths Eyrwphs 1997 kai twn 850 xronwn ths Mosxas
kai qa exoyn epafes prokeimenoy na syzhthsoyn tis prooptikes beltiwshs ths
poiothtas twn yphresiwn sth Rwsia.
<P>Mexri thn Kyriakh qa exei paradoqei sth Genikh Grammateia Palinnostoyntwn
Omogenwn toy Ypoyrgeioy Makedonias-Qrakhs, to sxedio nomoy gia thn
apokatastash twn omogenwn apo tis xwres ths prwhn Sobietikhs Enwshs, to
opoio epejergazetai o Dikhgorikos Syllogos Qessalonikhs kai to opoio qa
prowqhqei sth Boylh. Ayto anakoinwse o Genikos Grammateas Palinnostoyntwn
Omogenwn, Xrhstos Kamenidhs, milwntas sthn hmerida me qema ''Katapolemhsh
Koinwnikoy Apokleismoy Palinnostoyntwn Ellhnopontiwn'', poy organwsan h
Panellhnia Omospondia Pontiakwn Swmateiwn kai h Genikh Grammateia Laikhs
Epimorfwshs sth Qessalonikh.
<P>O prwqypoyrgos, Kwstas Shmiths, qa egkainiasei to apogeyma thn ekqesh poy
diorganwnei h Boylh twn Ellhnwn eis mnhmh toy Xarilaoy Trikoyph, sto
plaisio ths seiras ekdhlwsewn poy diorganwnei me aformh th symplhrwsh 100
xronwn apo to qanato toy megaloy Ellhna politikoy.
<P>Peqane sto Parisi se hlikia 72 etwn apo karkino toy pagkreatos o diashmos
Italos hqopoios Martselo Mastrogiani. Th stigmh toy qanatoy toy sto pleyro
toy briskotan h prwhn syntrofos toy Katrin Nteneb, h korh toys Kiara
Mastrogiani kai o filos toy hqopoios Misel Pikoli. H prwth toy dieqnhs
kinhmatografikh epityxia htan h tainia &quot;Ntoltse Bita&quot; toy Frenteriko Felini
kai mia apo tis teleytaies htan h &quot;Tzintzer kai Frent&quot; epishs toy Felini.
<P>''Prokeitai gia mia apwleia zwhs kai oxi apwleia mnhmhs'', dhlwse o
Ypoyrgos Politismoy, Eyaggelos Benizelos, plhroforoymenos to qanato toy
Italoy hqopoioy. ''Ws hqopoios metetrepe to proswpeio toy roloy se proswpo
ths pragmatikhs zwhs apo tis tainies toy neoitalikoy realismoy ws tis
ellhnikes kai pagkosmies tainies toy Qeodwroy Aggelopoyloy, stis opoies
exei prwtagwnisthsei'', shmeiwse o k.Benizelos.
<P>Th bebaiothta toy oti h Kypros qa einai melos ths EE to 2000, ''anejarthta
apo tis antirrhseis ths Toyrkias kai tis epifylajeis tritwn'', ejefrase o
Kyprios Ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn, Alekos Mixahlidhs, ektimwntas oti oi
entajiakes diapragmateyseis ths Kyproy me thn EE qa arxisoyn stis arxes toy
1998, me pio piqanh periodo to Martio. ''To gegonos oti h Ellada einai hdh
isotimo melos, einai to megalo xarti gia thn Kypro'', tonise o k.Mixahlidhs.
<P>Ws shmantikh nomikh epityxia, xarakthrise o kybernhtikos ekproswpos
Giannakhs Kasoylidhs, thn apofash toy Dikasthrioy Anqrwpinwn Dikaiwmatwn
toy Symboylioy ths Eyrwphs, sthn ypoqesh ths Titinas Loizidoy, enantion ths
Toyrkias. Symfwna me thn apofash ayth, eidikoi prokeitai na melethsoyn thn
ypoqesh, etsi wste na symboyleysoyn thn kybernhsh gia tis nomikes kai
politikes proektaseis ths. O k. Kasoylidhs katesthse safes oti proketai gia
atomikh prosfygh polith ths Kypriakhs Dhmokratias, ta apotelesmata ths
opoias, &quot;ikanopoioyn plhrws thn kypriakh kybernhsh&quot;.
<H4>BALKANIKES EIDHSEIS</H4>
Me mia akomh poreia diamartyrias, poy diorganwse gia 30h mera xqes o
synaspismos ''Zagientno'' giortase symbolika h antipoliteysh sto Beligradi
ton Agio Nikolao (oi qrhskeytikes eortes sth Serbia eortazontai me to
palaio hmerologio), th megalyterh giorth ths xwras. Nwritera, 30.000
foithtes diadhlwsan stoys dromoys toy Beligradioy. Sthn poreia symmeteixan
kai 23 foithtes toy panepisthmioy toy Kragkoygiebats, oi opoioi diesxisan
apostash 120 xiliometrwn me ta podia gia na symparastaqoyn stoys
synadelfoys toys. Gia shmera oi foithtes exoyn programmatisei na kleisoyn
gia mish wra tis kentrikes odoys ths gioygkoslabikhs prwteyoysas, ws akomh
mia endeijh diamartyrias. Shmera omws pragmatopoihqhkan kai sygkentrwseis
yposthrijhs pros to Serbo proedro Slompontan Milosebits. Se 4 poleis ths
Serbias, yposthriktes toy Serboy Proedroy ejefrasan thn antiqesh toys me
tis kinhtopoihseis ths antipoliteyshs.
<P>Episkech sthn Agkyra pragmatopoei o proedros toy Iran Xasemi Rafsantzani,
synodeyomenos apo polymelh antiproswpeia Se dhlwseis poy ekane o Toyrkos
proedros Soyleiman Ntemirel, amesws meta thn epishmh ypodoxh poy
epifylaxthke ston k. Rafsantzani, tonise oti kata th diarkeia twn epafwn qa
ejetastoyn qemata katapolemhshs ths tromokratias. O Toyrkos proedros
epishmane oti h beltiwsh twn sxesewn qa einai wfelimh kai gia tis dyo xwres.
O k. Rafsantzani apo thn pleyra toy ejefrase thn ikanopoihsh toy gia tis
prospaqeies poy kataballontai pros thn kateyqynsh ths beltiwshs twn sxesewn.
<P>Shmantikotato paragonta gia tis sxeseis twn orqodojwn ekklhsiwn apotelei h
apoklimakwsh twn entasewn metajy ths Serbikhs ekklhsias kai ths ekklhsias
ths PGDM, opws tonise o Oikoymenikos Patriarxhs Barqolomaios, kata th
synanthsh poy eixe me ton presbh ths PGDM sthn Agkyra k. Tragian Petkofski.
Symfwna me thn anakoinwsh toy Ypoyrgeioy Ejwterikwn twn Skopiwn, o
Oikoymenikos Patriarxhs edeije megalo endiaferon gia thn katastash sthn
PGDM.
<P>Egkainiasthke to neo chfiako thlefwniko diktyo, to opoio syndeei tis poleis
Kriba Palanka-ths PGDM- kai Kioystintil-ths Boylgarias. 'Opws metedwse o
radiofwnikos staqmos twn Skopiwn, to chfiako ayto diktyo apotelei meros toy
diabalkanikoy diktyoy, me to opoio anamenetai na syndeqoyn chfiaka h
Toyrkia, h Boylgaria, h Albania kai h PGDM.
<P>Paraithsh ths kybernhshs Bintenof kai prowres koinoboyleytikes ekloges
zhthsan diadhlwtes, sth Sofia, se poreia diamartyrias poy organwsan h
&quot;Enwsh Dhmokratikwn Dynamewn&quot; kai h Enwsh &quot;Allagh&quot;, sthn opoia ypagontai 24
syndikalistikes kai mh kybernhtikes organwseis. &quot;Mexri edw me thn ypomonh !
H Boylgaria den sas qelei!&quot; htan to basiko synqhma ths diadhlwtwn poy
ekanan stash mprosta sto ktirio ths kratikhs radiothleorashs,
diamartyromenoi gia thn &quot;epilektikh plhroforhsh&quot; poy yposthrizoyn oti
prosferoyn ta kratika MME sth xwra.
