<BODY>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<center><a href="/info"><IMG SRC="/gifs/hrnet.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="[HR-Net Banner]"></a><BR></center>

<H2>Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in Greek (PM), 96-12-19</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/mpeb">Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-19.mpeb.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-20.mpeb.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Macedonian Press Agency at <A HREF="http://www.mpa.gr">http://www.mpa.gr</A> and <A HREF="http://www.hri.org/MPA">http://www.hri.org/MPA</A>.</H4>
<HR>
<H4>Web Posted: 18:13 GMT+2</H4>
<H3>SYNTOMO BRADINO DELTIO EIDHSEWN - 19.12.1996</H3>
Xiliades agrotes poy eftasan me poylman, me tis oikogeneies toys, apo th
Qessalia kai thn Peloponnhso sthn Aqhna, elaban meros sth sygkentrwsh ejw
apo to Ypoyrgeio Gewrgias. Sth synexeia pragmatopoihsan poreia pros th
Boylh, zhtwntas synanthsh me ton prwqypoyrgo. Sthn poreia meteixan
oikodomoi kai syntajioyxoi, oi opoioi diorganwsan sygkentrwsh symparastashs
to meshmeri sthn plateia Kaniggos. Dekaejamelhs antiproswpeia twn agrotwn
synanthqhke, sth Boylh, me ton yfypoyrgo para tw prwqypoyrgw Giwrgo
Pasxalidh kai ton Ypoyrgo Gewrgias Stefano Tzoymaka. Sth Makedonia kai th
Qrakh oi kinhtopoihseis twn agrotwn odhgoyntai pros ektonwsh. Sth
Qessalonikh oi agrotes apesyran ta mploka apo ta &quot;Prasina Fanaria&quot; kai apo
thn aerogefyra ths Qermhs, wstoso paramenoyn sth gefyra toy Loydia kai ta
diodia Malgarwn. O nomarxhs Qessalonikhs Kwstas Papadopoylos ejefrase thn
ikanopoihsh toy gia thn antapokrish twn agrotwn sto aithma twn paragwgikwn
tajewn kai koinwnikwn omadwn na anasteiloyn tis kinhtopoihseis toys. Kalese
de thn kybernhsh se enarjh gonimoy kai oysiastikoy dialogoy.
<P>&quot;H kybernhsh den mporei na ekbiazetai gia toys apokleismoys toy eqnikoy
odikoy diktyoy&quot; ypogrammise shmera o kybernhtikos ekproswpos Dhmhtrhs
Reppas o opoios epanelabe oti o prwqypoyrgos den qa synanthqei me toys
agrotes an den lyqoyn prwta ta odofragmata. Erwthqeis de gia to rolo toy
Kommoynistikoy Kommatos o k. Reppas tonise oti to KKE edwse thn epikoyria
toy kai th syntonistikh kalych sthn telikh morfh twn kinhtopoihsewn.
<P>Thn pagia qesh ths Elladas oti h Toyrkia prepei na apodextei tis arxes toy
dieqnoys dikaioy kai na sebastei tis dieqneis synqhkes kai symbaseis poy
prosdiorizoyn ola ayta ta qemata twn diaforwn, poy epikaleitai oti exei sto
Aigaio, epanelabe o ypoyrgos Eqnikhs Amynas Akhs Tsoxatzopoylos,
sxoliazontas thn ektimhsh poy ejefrase o Ollandos ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn Xans
Ban Mirlo symfwna me thn opoia &quot;Ellada kai Toyrkia einai etoimes na
jekinhsoyn dialogo gia thn epilysh twn opoiwn diaforwn toys&quot;. O Ban Mirlo,
kata th diarkeia ths paroysiashs twn proteraiothtwn ths Ollandikhs
Proedrias, poy arxizei apo 1hs Ianoyarioy 1997, poy stis Bryjelles kai
apantwntas se erwthseis dhmosiografwn ejefrase thn ektimhsh oti &quot;h Ellada
kai h Toyrkia einai etoimes na jekinhsoyn dialogo gia thn epilysh twn
metajy toys diaforwn&quot;.
<P>O 62xronos Manwlhs Rodiths apo to Hrakleio Krhths peqane apo kardia enw
parakoloyqoyse ta epeisodia metajy naytergatwn kai odhgwn forthgwn sto
limani toy Peiraia. Tetamenh htan h katastash kai se alla limania ths xwras.
Oi naytergates apofasisan paratash ths apergias toys kai oi ploiokthtes
apeiloyn me apolyseis twn apergwn.
<P>Tetrahmerh epishmh episkech sthn Aigypto pragmatopoiei apo ayrio o Proedros
ths Dhmokratias Kwsths Stefanopoylos. H prwth hmera ths episkechs toy,
einai afierwmenh sthn omogeneia. Ayrio to prwi qa brisketai synodeyomenos
apo ton ypoyrgo Ejwterikwn Qeodwro Pagkalo sthn Alejandreia, opoy qa
episkeftei to Moyseio Ellhno-Rwmaikwn Arxaiothtwn. H epomenh episkech toy
qa einai sto Ellhniko Patriarxeio kai meta sto Moyseio Kabafh. Argotera, o
Proedros ths Dhmokratias qa synanthqei me ton sebasmiotato mhtropolith k.
Dionysio kai alloys arxiereis.
<P>Peqane shmera sto spiti toy sto Parisi se hlikia 72 etwn apo karkino toy
pagkreatos o diashmos Italos hqopoios Martselo Mastrogiani. Th stigmh toy
qanatoy toy sto pleyro toy briskotan h prwhn syntrofos toy Katrin Nteneb, h
korh toys Kiara Mastrogiani kai o filos toy hqopoios Misel Pikoli. H prwth
toy dieqnhs kinhmatografikh epityxia htan h tainia &quot;Ntoltse Bita&quot; toy
Frenteriko Felini kai mia apo tis teleytaies htan h &quot;Tzintzer kai Frent&quot;
epishs toy Felini.
<P>Oi presbeis ths Elladas, toy Kanada, ths Ispanias kai ths Germanias, o
politistikos akoloyqos ths Gallias kai enas Peroybianos diplwmaths
meteferan sthn kybernhsh toy Peroy ta aithmata twn antartwn poy synexizoyn
na kratoyn ekatontades omhroys sthn katoikia toy Iapwna presbh. Jenes
kybernhseis exoyn episthsei thn prosoxh sthn kybernhsh toy Peroy na mhn
proxwrhsei se spasmwdikes kinhseis, qetontas, etsi, se kindyno th zwh twn
omhrwn.
<P>Poinikh diwjh gia ceydh kataqesh kata ths dhmosiografoy Ellhs Stah askhse
shmera o Proistamenos ths Eisaggelias Aqhnwn Anastasios Kanellopoylos. H
diwjh askeitai epeita apo arnhsh ths k. Stah na dwsei dieykriniseis sthn
armodia Ejetastikh Epitroph ths Boylhs gia to ypomnhma poy kateqese
anaforika me thn agora dyo akinhtwn.
<P>Thn anagkh yposthrijhs twn diapragmateysewn toso apo thn Ellada oso kai apo
thn Toyrkia ypogrammizei, sthn nea ekqesh toy gia to Kypriako, o
aperxomenos Genikos Grammateas toy OHE Mpoytros Mpoytros Gkali. Kanei de
logo gia epideinwsh ths katastashs sthn Kypro to teleytaio ejamhno toso apo
dhmografikhs apocews oso kai se oti afora stis sxeseis twn dyo koinothtwn
metajy toys kai me ton ejw kosmo.
<P>Idiaitero endiaferon edeije o Mpoytros Gkali gia to kypriako kata th qhteia
toy ws G.G. toy OHE. Thn ektimhsh ayth diatypwse o kybernhtikos ekproswpos
Giannakhs Kasoylidhs. O k.Kasoylidhs, tonise oti o k.Gkali &quot;asxolhqhke
energa me to kypriako kai yphrjan fores poy de distase na milhsei me
aysthrh glwssa gia th stash ths toyrkokypriakhs pleyras&quot; enw epishmane oti
lypatai poy den eytyxhse na dei to ergo toy na oloklhrwnetai me mia lysh
sto problhma. Ejefrase epishs thn apoch oti kai o diadoxos toy Gkali, Kofi
Anan gnwrizei gia to kypriako kai poly syntoma qa to ferei se aisio telos.
<P>Dyomisi xiliades anqrwpoi stis xwres ths prwhn Sobietikhs Enwshs
epwfeloyntai apo to ereynhtiko kai ekpaideytiko programma &quot;Iaswn&quot;,
prokeimenoy na maqoyn ellhnika. Mono sto panepisthmio toy Ntoyniesk sthn
Oykrania, 600 atoma parakoloyqoyn me megalo endiaferon kai enqoysiasmo ta
maqhmata ekmaqhshs ths arxaias, neas ellhnikhs kai byzantinhs glwssas kai
istorias, enw oi ariqmoi ayjanontai diarkws, dhmioyrgwntas elpides gia thn
apokatastash twn ellhnikwn spoydwn stis xwres ths prwhn Sobietikhs Enwshs.
<P>Sthn enisxysh kai dieyrynsh ths synergasias metajy ths Aqhnas kai twn
Tiranwn stoxeyei h episkech toy dhmarxoy Aqhnaiwn, Dhmhtrh Abramopoyloy,
sthn albanikh prwteyoysa. Ayto tonisthke kata tis epafes poy eixe xqes o k.
Abramopoylos sthn albanikh prwteyoysa me ton prwqypoyrgo ths xwras,
Alejanter Meji, ton ypoyrgo Ejwterikwn, Tritan Siexoy, kai ton dhmarxo
Tiranwn, k. Mproika. Idiaitero endiaferon paroysiazei h prwtoboylia toy k.
Abramopoyloy, gia thn epilysh basikwn problhmatwn twn Albanwn poy
ergazontai sthn Aqhna. O dhmarxos Aqhnaiwn anaferqhke sthn epektash toy
diktyoy koinwnikhs pronoias kai basikhs iatrikhs periqalchs gia aytoys,
kaqws kai sthn ejasfalish egkyrhs kai egkairhs plhroforhshs pros tis
albanikes arxes gia ta problhmata anqrwpistikhs fyshs twn Albanwn politwn
poy ergazontai se olh thn Ellada, ajiopoiwntas kalytera tis yparxoyses
dynatothtes.
<P>Oi topikes prwines omixles kai broxes sta Dytika kai argotera stis
perissoteres perioxes ths xwras qa einai to kyrio xarakthristiko toy
ayrianoy kairoy. Eidikotera sth Dytikh Ellada qa shmeiwqoyn liges nefwseis
poy grhgora qa pyknwsoyn kai qa brejei enw meta to meshmeri qa ekdhlwqoyn
kai kataigides. Sthn ypoloiph xwra qa ekdhlwqoyn nefwseis kai topikes
broxes. Th nyxta sta boreiodytika o kairos qa beltiwqei enw to prwi sta
hpeirwtika qa shmeiwqoyn topikes omixles. H qermokrasia qa kymanqei sta
Boreia hpeirwtika apo 5 ews 14 baqmoys, sta ypoloipa Hpeirwtika apo 8 ews
18 kai sta nhsia toy Aigaioy apo 13 ews 19 baqmoys Kelsioy. Sth Qessalonikh
ayrio o kairos qa einai nefelwdhs enw pros to brady qa brejei. H
qermokrasia sthn polh qa kymanqei apo 6 ews 13 baqmoys Kelsioy.
<HR>
