<H2>Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in Greek (PM), 96-12-20</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/mpeb">Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-20.mpeb.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-21.mpeb.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Macedonian Press Agency at <A HREF="http://www.mpa.gr">http://www.mpa.gr</A> and <A HREF="http://www.hri.org/MPA">http://www.hri.org/MPA</A>.</H4>
<HR>
<H4>Web Posted: 18:17 GMT+2</H4>
<H3>SYNTOMO BRADINO DELTIO EIDHSEWN - 20.12.1996</H3>
Thn anastolh twn agrotikwn kinhtopoihsewn sth Boreia Ellada apofasise h
Syntonistikh Epitroph Agwna Makedonias-Qrakhs, sth shmerinh synedriash ths.
Sthn anakoinwsh ths h Epitroph tonizei oti h apofash ayth elhfqh enocei twn
Xristoygennwn, enw o prwqypoyrgos toys kalese se dialogo. To apogeyma
synedriase sth Larisa h Panqessalikh Epitroph twn agrotwn kai apofasise
synexish twn kinhtopoihsewn kai enisxysh twn yparxontwn odofragmatwn.
<P>Oi apanthseis ths kybernhshs sta aithmata twn agrotwn einai gnwstes, wstoso
oi dromoi paramenoyn apokleismenoi, dhlwse shmera o kybernhtikos ekproswpos
Dhmhtrhs Reppas o opoios tonise oti exoyn ikanopoihqei ta tria apo ta eji
aithmata twn agrotwn. Eidikotera apofasisthke h ryqmish twn agrotikwn xrewn,
h enisxysh twn agrotwn twn opoiwn oi kalliergeies eplhghsan apo qeomhnies
kai h prowqhsh toy mhtrwoy agrotwn to prwto ejamhno toy 1997 gia th
xorhghsh fthnoy petrelaioy. Sto metajy qetikh einai h gnwmodothsh ths
oikonomikhs kai koinwnikhs Epitrophs poy ejetase shmera to nomosxedio toy
ypoyrgeioy Ergasias kai Koinwnikwn Asfalisewn gia th metatroph toy OGA se
kyrio forea asfalishs.
<P>Tetrahmerh epishmh episkech sthn Aigypto pragmatopoiei apo shmera o
Proedros ths Dhmokratias Kwsths Stefanopoylos, synodeyomenos apo ton
ypoyrgo Ejwterikwn Qeodwro Pagkalo. O k. Stefanopoylos episkefqhke to
Moyseio Ellhnorwmaikwn Arxaiothtwn sthn Alejandreia, to Ellhniko
Patriarxeio kai to Moyseio Kabafh. Argotera, synanthqhke me ton
sebasmiotato mhtropolith k.Dionysio kai alloys arxiereis. O Proedros ths
Dhmokratias eixe epafes me stelexh ths omogeneias kai ypogrammise to rolo
toys sthn epilysh twn eqnikwn mas zhthmatwn. To apogeyma metebh sto Kairo
opoy ayrio to meshmeri qa synanthqei me ton Aigyptio proedro Xosni
Moymparak. Oi kyrioi Stefanopoylos kai Moymparak qa syzhthsoyn epi mia wra
gia tis sxeseis twn dyo xwrwn.
<P>Apostolh allhleggyhs jekina ayrio apo to G' Swma Stratoy gia toys
plhmmyropaqeis ths Janqhs. H apostolh organwqhke apo ton 102 FM ths ERT-3
mesa apo radiofwniko maraqwnio me skopo thn oikonomikh kai ylikh bohqeia
pros toys katoikoys ths Janqhs. Oi prosfores se eidh jepernoyn se ajia ta
30.000.000 draxmes kai sygkentrwqhkan apo synergeio ths Nomarxias, toy
dhmoy Eleyqerioy-Kordelioy kai toy Stratoy. To fortio qa paradoqei sto
Nomarxh Janqhs gia na prowqhqei stoys plhmmyropaqeis.
<P>To Eyrwpaiko Dikasthrio Anqrwpinwn Dikaiwmatwn katadikase, symfwna me
syntomo thlegrafhma toy praktoreioy Reuters, thn Agkyra na plhrwsei
apozhmiwseis kai ta dikastika ejoda se ypoqesh Koyrdoy poy to 1992
synelhfqh kai basanisthke ws tromokraths apo tis toyrkikes arxes.
Ypenqymizetai oti prin liges meres katadikasthke pali h Toyrkia gia thn
ypoqesh ths Ellhnokyprias Titinas Loizidoy, apofash poy xarakthrizetai
staqmos me eyryteres epiptwseis, afoy afora sto dikaiwma epikoinwnias kai
perioysias sthn katexomenh Kypro.
<P>Oi jenes kybernhseis arxizoyn na antilambanontai oti h katastash sthn Kypro
einai opws ena hfaisteio poy einai etoimo na ekragei, tonise o proedros
Glaykos Klhridhs amesws meta th synanthsh poy eixe me ton presbh twn HPA
sth Leykwsia Keneq Mpril. Stoxos twn Amerikanwn einai h prowqhsh ameswn
diapragmateysewn gia epilysh toy kypriakoy mesa sto prwto ejamhno toy 1997,
ypogrammise o k.Mpril apo thn pleyra toy, anaferomenos stis prosfates
dhlwseis toy k.Klinton, o opoios desmeythke oti qa ergastei sklhra gia th
Megalonhso kai tis ellhnotoyrkikes sxeseis.
<P>Ypanaxwrei o prwqypoyrgos ths Toyrkias Netsmentin Ermpakan stoys oroys ths
neoterhs symfwnias poy ypegrace me to Israhl gia ton eksygxronismo 54
aeroskafwn F-4, sthn prospaqeia toy na elaxistopoihsei tis antidraseis poy
ekdhlwqhkan apo to Komma Eyhmerias alla kai orismenes islamikes xwres. Opws
anaferei h efhmerida &quot;Zaman&quot; o Ermpakan meta thn epikyrwsh ths symfwnias me
to Israhl kataballei twra entones prospaqeies prokeimenoy na meiwsei to
kostos twn 632 ekatommyriwn dolariwn poy qa katablhqoyn sto Israhl gia ton
eksygxronismo toyrkikwn aeroskafwn.
<P>H ejasqenish twn anemwn kai oi topikes proskaires broxes qa einai ta kyria
xarakthristika toy ayrianoy kairoy. Arxika se olh th xwra qa ekdhlwqoyn
nefwseis kai sto Aigaio sporadikes kataigides. Grhgora o kairos qa
beltiwqei. H qermokrasia qa kymanqei sta boreia hpeirwtika apo 6 ews 14
baqmoys Kelsioy, sto Ionio kai ta ypoloipa Hpeirwtika apo 8 ews 18 baqmoys
kai sta nhsia toy Aigaioy apo 13 ews 19 baqmoys Kelsioy. Sth Qessalonikh
ayrio qa ekdhlwqoyn topikes nefwseis me broxh, omws apo to meshmeri o
kairos qa beltiwqei. Oi anemoi qa pneoyn asqeneis enw h qermokrasia sthn
polh qa kymanqei apo 6 ews 13 baqmoys Kelsioy.
<HR>
