<HEAD>
<TITLE>Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in Greek (AM), 96-12-19</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<center><a href="/info"><IMG SRC="/gifs/hrnet.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="[HR-Net Banner]"></a><BR></center>

<H2>Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in Greek (AM), 96-12-19</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/mpeb">Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-18_1.mpeb.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-19_1.mpeb.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Macedonian Press Agency at <A HREF="http://www.mpa.gr">http://www.mpa.gr</A> and <A HREF="http://www.hri.org/MPA">http://www.hri.org/MPA</A>.</H4>
<HR>
<H4>Web Posted: 09:34 GMT+2</H4>
<H3>SYNTOMO PRWINO DELTIO THS 19.12.96</H3>
Syllalhthrio sthn plateia Baqhs sthn Aqhna pragmatopoioyn to meshmeri oi
agrotes ths Qessalias mazi me tis oikogeneies toys. Oi agrotes sth synexeia
qa pragmatopoihsoyn poreia sth boylh apo koinoy me toys oikodomoys kai toys
syntajioyxoys se endeijh symparastashs. H Omospondia Idiokthtwn Forthgwn
Aytokinhtwn apofasise na mhn empodisei thn kaqodo twn agrotwn sthn Aqhna.
Sygkentrwsh
<P>Pros ektonwsh odhgoyntai oi kinhtopoihseis twn agrotwn sth Makedonia kai th
Qrakh. Sth Qessalonikh oi agrotes aposyrqhkan kai apo ton odiko kombo sthn
aerogefyra ths Qermhs se endeijh kalhs qelhshs prokeimenoy na ejyphrethqoyn
oi tajidiwtes.
<P>H kybernhsh einai diateqeimenh na syzhthsei me toys agrotes dia toy
ypoyrgoy Gewrgias, dhlwse o kybernhtikos ekproswpos Dhmhtrhs Reppas, o
opoios dieykrinise oti den exei diatypwqei tetoio aithma ek meroys twn
agrotwn. Epanelabe oti o prwqypoyrgos Kwstas Shmiths protiqetai na dexqei
th syntonistikh epitroph twn agrotwn efoson apodesmeysoyn to eqniko diktyo.
<P>Synexizetai kai shmera sthn olomeleia ths boylhs h syzhthsh toy
proypologismoy gia to 1997, h opoia qa oloklhrwqei me onomastikh chfoforia
ta mesanyxta toy Sabbatoy. Xqes o ypoyrgos Eqnikhs Oikonomias Giannos
Papantwnioy aneptyje apo toy bhmatos ths boylhs toys stoxoys ths
oikonomikhs politikhs poy basizontai sto triptyxo, anaptyjh, erywpaikh
sygklish, synoxh.
<P>Wrologiakh bomba ejerragh ligo meta ta mesanyxta sto ypokatasthma ths
trapeza City Bank, se polysyxnasto dromo toy Xalandrioy. O ekrhktikos
mhxanismos poy apoteleito apo epitrapezio roloi kai toylaxiston 3 kila
dynamitidas eixe topoqethqei sto mhxanhma aytomaths analhchs xrhmatwn. Apo
thn ekrhjh katastrafhke sxedon oloklhrwtika h trapeza enw proklhqhkan
sobares ylikes zhmies sta gyrw katasthmata kai sta staqmeymena oxhmata.
Mexri stigmhs kamia organwsh den exei analabei thn eyqynh gia thn
topoqethsh toy ekrhktikoy mhxanismoy.
<P>Eleyqeroys afhsan tis prwtes prwines wres oi enoploi antartes ths organwshs
&quot;Toypak-amaro&quot; poy katelaban to ktirio ths iapwnikhs presbeias sth Lima,
toys presbeis ths Elladas, Kanada kai ths Germanias kai dyo alloys
diplwmates, prokeimenoy na mesolabhsoyn sthn peroybianh kybernhsh gia ta
aithmata toys. Oi antartes kratoyn 250 peripoy omhroys toys opoioys
apeiloyn na skotwsoyn ean oi arxes den apeleyqerwsoyn toys syntrofoys toys
poy briskontai stis fylakes.
<P>Me ton Bretano omologo toy Malkom Rifkint synanthqhke sto Londino o
ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn Qeodwros Pagkalos o opoios ton enhmerwse gia ta eqnika
mas qemata, ta ellhnotoyrkika kai to Kypriako. O k.Pagkalos zhthse
dieykriniseis gia ta deka shmeia - protaseis toy ypoyrgeioy ejwterikwn ths
M. Bretanias gia proodo sthn epilysh toy Kypriakoy. Problhmatismo
dhmioyrgei to dekato shmeio, h diatypwsh toy opoioy yponoei oti prepei
prwta na yparjei lysh toy Kypriakoy kai katopin na arxisoyn oi entajiakes
diapragmateyseis ths Megalonhsoy.
<P>Ton Ianoyario toy 1997 qa epanalhfqoyn oi synomilies metajy Elladas kai
PGDM sthn edra toy OHE, sth Nea Yorkh, opws anakoinwse o ekproswpos toy
Genikoy Grammatea toy OHE, Sairoys Bans, meta th diwrh synanthsh poy eixan
oi presbeis Xrhstos Zaxarakis kai Iban Tosefski. Apantwntas se erwthseis
twn dhmosiografwn o k. Bans tonise oti h hmeromhnia synanthshs Zaxaraki-
Tosefski qa kaqoristei argotera, enw sxetika me thn eklogh neoy Genikoy
Grammatea toy OHE kai thn entolh poy afora sto diko toy diamesolabhtiko
rolo, ypogrammise oti o idios qa synexisei mexri thn oloklhrwsh twn
synomiliwn kai gia thn wra den exei na pei tipote perissotero. Apanthse,
epishs, arnhtika sthn erwthsh an exoyn katateqei apo tis dyo pleyres
sygkekrimena onomata gia th geitonikh xwra. O ekproswpos ths PGDM
ypogrammie pws h xwr toy exei th boylhsh na lysei to problhma.
<P>Eleyqerh einai apo xqes to apogeyma h dieleysh twn oxhmatwn apo th
diastayrwsh ''Prasina Fanaria'' sto dromo pros to aerodromio &quot;Makedonia&quot;
ths Qessalonikhs. Thn apofash gia termatismo toy apokleismoy ths
diastayrwshs phre h Syntonistikh Epitroph Agwna Makedonias-Qrakhs,twn
agrotwn kata th synedriash ths poy pragmatopoihqhke to meshmeri sto ktirio
ths PASEGES, ws &quot;deigma kalhs qelhshs, enocei twn Xristoygennwn,
prokeimenoy na metakinhqei to koino aeroporikws xwris problhmata&quot;.
<P>Meiwsh toy kostoys paragwghs kata penhnta eji disekatommyria draxmes, ths
apasxolhshs kata 208.000 hmeromisqia, poy antistoixoyn se dyo
disekatommyria draxmes, twn paradosewn kata 134 disekatommyria kai toy
kefalaioy kinhsews ths biomhxanias kata 20%, einai oi synepeies twn
agrotikwn kinhtopoihsewn, opws prokyptei apo ereyna toy Syndesmoy Ellhnikwn
Biomhxaniwn poy pragmatopoihqhke se 530 epixeirhseis. Ta apotelesmata ths
ereynas edwse sth dhmosiothta o Proedros toy Syndesmoy Ellhnikwn
Biomhxaniwn Iaswn Stratos.
<P>Dyo oxhmatagwga kai ena epibathgo ploio einai aragmena sto limani ths
Qessalonikhs kai perimenoyn th lhjh ths apergias twn naytergatwn gia na
apopleysoyn. Ta problhmata poy prokyptoyn apo tis kinhtopoihseis twn
ergazomenwn emfanizontai entonotera, apo proxqes, kaqws logw synwstismoy
sto limani den pragmatopoioyntai oyte ta ektakta dromologia twn
oxhmatagwgwn poy metaferoyn proionta sthn agora ths Qessalonikhs. Etsi, de
qa pragmatopoihqei kanena apo ta 15 ektakta dromologia oxhmatagwgwn poy
htan programmatismena gia thn trexoysa ebdomada, alla oyte kai -ta
periorismena, parola ayta, kata th xeimerinh periodo- dromologia twn
epibathgwn.
<P>Timio kai antiproswpeytiko synedrio ths Neas Dhmokratias zhta o epitimos
Proedros toy kommatos Kwnstantinos Mhtsotakhs se synenteyjh toy se
ebdomadiaio periodiko. Shmeiwnei de oti an gia to epikeimeno synedrio ths
ajiwmatikhs antipoliteyshs den chfisei h bash toy kommatos gia thn eklogh
synedrwn, o idios den prokeitai na symmetasxei se ayto. &quot;An to synedrio den
ginei ton Febroyario me chfoforia apo th bash, h N.D. qa odhghqei se
aytoktonia&quot; tonizei o k. Mhtsotakhs.
<P>Synexizontai shmera stis Bryjelles oi ergasies toy Symboylioy Ypoyrgwn
Alieias ths Eyrwpaikhs 'Enwshs me th symmetoxh toy yfypoyrgoy Gewrgias,
Basilh Geranidh. Metajy twn qematwn poy syzhtoyntai sto Symboylio einai to
&quot;Polyetes Programma Prosanatolismoy&quot; gia thn periodo apo 1 Ianoyarioy 1997
ews 31 Dekembrioy 2002, poy afora sth meiwsh toy Koinotikoy alieytikoy
stoloy, gia thn prostasia twn ixqyapoqematwn. Ejalloy to Symboylio qa
apasxolhsei kai to &quot;Doryforiko Systhma Parakoloyqhshs twn Koinotikwn
Alieytikwn Stolwn&quot; kai sygkekrimena h protash gia tropopoihsh toy
kanonismoy peri efarmoghs elegxoy twn Koinotikwn Alieytikwn Stolwn.
<P>Erga anaptyjhs systhmatwn hlektronikhs antallaghs dedomenwn (EDI) se
sygkekrimenoys kladoys paragwghs, yposthrizei to ypoyrgeio Anaptyjhs. Mesw
toy ypoprogrammatos 1, metro 2 toy Epixeirhsiakoy Programmatos ths
Biomhxanias xrhmatodotoyntai se pososto 60% draseis proypologismoy 130 ekat.
drx., kata anwtato orio. To programma sthrizei draseis poy analambanoyn
syspeirwseis etaireiwn kai organismwn, stis opoies mporoyn na symmetexoyn
mikromesaies metapoihtikes epixeirhseis toy sygkekrimenoy kladoy,
syllogikoi foreis, kaqws kai promhqeytes proiontwn logismikoy EDI kai
thlepikoinwniakwn yphresiwn. Symfwna me thn prokhryjh toy ergoy,
mikromesaia noeitai kaqe epixeirhsh poy paroysiazei kyklo ergasiwn
mikrotero twn 300 ekat.drx. h apasxolei ligoteroys apo 30 ergazomenoys.
<P>Mexri thn 31h Aygoystoy 1997 parateinetai me diatajh poy chfisqhke thn
prohgoymenh ebdomada sth Boylh, h proqesmia dhlwshs stis Astynomikes Arxes
twn kynhgetikwn oplwn gia thn ekdosh adeias katoxhs toys. H apofash ayth
elhfqh, prokeimenoy na dhlwqoyn stis armodies Astynomikes Arxes ola ta
kynhgetika opla poy katexontai kai na ekdoqoyn oi sxeyikes adeies katoxhs.
<P>Staqmo sthn istoria ths nomologias gia ta anqrwpina dikaiwmata kai thn
ejelijh toy dhmosioy dieqnoys dikaioy, xarakthrise o Genikos Eisaggeleas
ths Kypriakhs Dhmokratias, Alekos Markidhs, thn apofash toy Eyrwpaikoy
Dikasthrioy Anqrwpinwn Dikaiwmatwn, anaforika me thn ypoqesh ths Titinas
Loizidoy. ''Basikh nomikh qesh ths Toyrkias htan oti den exei opoiadhpote
dikaiodosia sto ceydokratos'', eipe o k.Markidhs, shmeiwnontas oti h qesh
ayth aporrifqhke, enw ypogrammise oti ''H apofash leei kaqara oti ekeinos o
opoios katexei mia sygkekrimenh perioxh, anejarthta an thn katexei nomima h
paranoma, eyqynetai gia opoiadhpote parabiash anqrwpinwn dikaiwmatwn entos
ayths ths perioxhs''.
<P>Me ton Proedro Glayko Klhridh, qa synanthqoyn ayrio, Ellhnokyprioi kai
Toyrkokyprioi foithtes, sto plaisio ths enqarrynshs ameswn epafwn twn dyo
pleyrwn. Hdh, oi foithtes synanthqhkan me ton Toyrkokyprio hgeth Raoyf
Ntenktas. H synanthsh ayth, apofasisthke meta apo paraklhsh ths presbeias
twn HPA sth Leykwsia kai entassetai sto plaisio omadwn ergasias ths
Epitrophs Ypotrofiwn ``Foylmprait''.
<H4>BALKANIKES EIDHSEIS</H4>
Synexizontai kai shmera oi sygkentrwseis diamartyrias ths antipoliteyshs
kai twn foithtwn sto Beligradi kai se alles poleis ths Serbias. Pera omws
apo tis sygkentrwseis toy antipoliteyomenoy synaspismoy &quot;Zagientno&quot;, o
kybernhtikos sxhmatismos toy Slompontan Milosebits, se mia prospaqeia na
apodeijei oti yparxoyn kai para polloi, oi opoioi den symfwnoyn me ton en
logw tropo diamartyrias, apofasise na proxwrhsei se &quot;antidiadhlwseis&quot;.
'Etsi xqes sygkentrwsh yposthrijhs pros th serbikh kybernhsh
pragmatopoihqhke sthn polh Sremska Mitrobitsa, enw analoges kinhtopoihseis
kai se alles poleis programmatizontai kai gia tis epomenes hmeres.
<P>Trianta mia xiliades andres apo toys opoioys oi 8500 qa einai Amerikanoi qa
apoteloyn thn dynamh asfaleias h opoia qa antikatasthsei apo thn 1h
Ianoyarioy 1997 thn dieqnh Dynamh Efarmoghs poy egkatastaqhke sth xwra gia
thn epibolh ths synqhkhs toy Ntehton. H telikh egkrish toy NATO sth sxetikh
apofash toy Symboylioy Asfaleias hdh edoqh kai sygxronws egine gnwsto oti
sth dynamh asfaleias qa paroyn meros 5000 Bretanoi, 3000 Germanoi kai 2500
Galloi.
<P>To poso twn 600.000 germanikwn markwn enekrine h kybernhsh ths Germanias
gia thn enarjh toy programmatos gia thn oikonomikh anaptyjh kai prostasia
toy anqrwpinoy periballontos stis parakties zwnes ths limnhs Oxridas kai
ths Prespas, metedwse o radiostaqmos twn Tiranwn. Opws metedwse o
radiofwnikos staqmos twn Tiranwn, to programma ayto, gia thn ylopoihsh toy
opoioy qa symmetasxoyn me xrhmatika posa kai h Eyrwpaikh Organwsh gia thn
prostasia toy anqrwpinoy periballontos, kaqws kai alla idrymata, einai
idiaiterhs shmasias, dioti ylopoieitai kai me th symmetoxh ths PGDM.
<P>Episkech ergasias sthn Italia pragmatopoiei o neoeklegeis Proedros ths
Boylgarias, Petar Stogianof, meta apo prosklhsh toy Italoy Proedroy, Oskar
Loyitzi Skalfaro. Sth Rwmh, o k.Stogianof qa synanthqei me to Italo
prwqypoyrgo, Romano Pronti, ton ypoyrgo Ejwterikwn, Lamperto Ntini kai qa
ginei dektos apo ton Papa Iwannh Paylo ton B'.
<H4>KAIROS</H4>
Nefwseis me asqeneis anemoys problepei gia shmera h EMY gia thn polh ths
Qessalonikhs. H qermokrasia sthn polh qa kymanqei apo 6 ews 13 baqmoys
Kelsioy.
