<H2>Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in Greek (AM), 96-12-21</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/mpeb">Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-20_1.mpeb.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-21_1.mpeb.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Macedonian Press Agency at <A HREF="http://www.mpa.gr">http://www.mpa.gr</A> and <A HREF="http://www.hri.org/MPA">http://www.hri.org/MPA</A>.</H4>
<HR>
<H4>Web Posted: 10:11 GMT+2</H4>
<H3>SYNTOMO DELTIO EIDHSEWN THS 21.12.96</H3>
Thn anastolh twn agrotikwn kinhtopoihsewn sth Boreia Ellada apofasise h
Syntonistikh Epitroph Agwna Makedonias-Qrakhs, sth xqesinh synedriash ths.
Sthn anakoinwsh ths h Epitroph tonizei oti h apofash ayth elhfqh enocei twn
Xristoygennwn, enw o prwqypoyrgos toys kalese se dialogo. Xqes to apogeyma
synedriase sth Larisa h Panqessalikh Epitroph twn agrotwn kai apofasise
synexish twn kinhtopoihsewn kai enisxysh twn yparxontwn odofragmatwn. Xqes
brady anesteile tis kinhtopoihseis ths kai h Panellhnia Omospondia Naytikwn
meta thn yposxesh ths kybernhshs oti qa epanejetasei thn katarghsh twn
foroapallagwn twn naytikwn, prin kataqesei to forologiko nomosxedio stis 7
Ianoyarioy. Oi naytikoi proeidopoioyn me nees apergies ean h kybernhsh
epimeinei sthn katarghsh twn foroapallagwn toys. Ta dromologia twn ploiwn
se ola ta limania ths xwras diejagontai kanonika.
<P>&quot;Shmantikh epitaxynsh sthn aporrofhsh twn koinotikwn kondyliwn exei h
Ellada ton teleytaio xrono, kalyptontas gia prwth fora to 100%&quot;. Ayto
dhlwse sth Boylh o ypoyrgos Eqnikhs Oikonomias kai Oikonomikwn, Giannos
Papantwnioy, apantwntas ston arxhgo ths Ajiwmatikhs Antipoliteyshs,
Miltiadh 'Ebert, o opoios, me parembash toy, kathgorhse thn kybernhsh gia
megalh kaqysterhsh stis eisprajeis gia ta erga poy xrhmatodotoyntai apo thn
Koinothta. 'Opws ypogrammise o k. Papantwnioy, symfwna me thn telikh
ektimhsh toy Genikoy Logisthrioy, to 1996 oi eisroes apo ta koinotika
kondylia qa anelqoyn sto 1 tris 817 dis draxmes enanti 1 tris 881 dis, poy
htan o stoxos. 'Opws ejhghse o ypoyrgos Eqnikhs Oikonomias, qa yparjei
sterhsh mono gia 60 dis kai h kalych qa ftasei to 97%. Malista, o k.
Papantwnioy kateqese kai sxetiko eggrafo toy Genikoy Logisthrioy toy
Kratoys, me proxqesinh hmeromhnia, symfwna me to opoio parathreitai
shmantikh epitaxynsh eisrown toso gia to 1996 oso kai gia to 1995. Apo thn
pleyra toy o k. 'Ebert, kathgorhse ton ypoyrgo Eqnikhs Oikonomias oti
prospaqei na paraplanhsei to Swma.
<P>O epitimos Proedros ths ND, Kwnstantinos Mhtsotakhs, milwntas sth Boylh,
xarakthrise thn kybernhsh &quot;apotyxhmenh&quot; kai shmeiwse oti &quot;se ligo kairo qa
einai pantelws anisxyrh na efarmosei opoiadhpote politikh&quot;. Taytoxrona, o k.
Mhtsotakhs kathgorhse ola ta politika kommata oti den lene thn alhqeia ston
ellhniko lao kai toy apokryptoyn thn pragmatikothta. Sth synexeia, o
epitimos Proedros ths ND ekane anafora se &quot;afanh&quot;, opws eipe, &quot;elleimmata,
ta opoia dhmioyrgoyntai apo pashs fysews drasthriothtes toy kratoys, alla
den apeikonizontai ston proypologismo&quot;. Malista, anaferomenos eidikotera
sto etos 1996, tonise oti ektos apo to epishmo elleimma, ayjhqhke me ton
tropo ayto kai to dhmosio xreos, kata 220 disekatommyria draxmes apo
kataptwseis eggyhsewn, kata 100 dis apo agores metoxwn ths xreokophmenhs
ETBA, kata 126 dis apo analhch xreolysiwn gia logariasmo tritwn, kata 70
dis apo kefalaiopoihmenoys tokoys kai kata 248 dis apo synallagmatikes
diafores.
<P>''O ellhnikos laos mas edwse thn entolh na kybernhsoyme gia allh mia
tetraetia. Ayth th fora omws to nohma ths laikhs entolhs htan diaforetiko:
Den phrame entolh diaxeirishs. Phrame entolh sygkroyshs'', tonise h
Ypoyrgos Anaptyjhs, Basw Papandreoy, milwntas sth Boylh, kata th syzhthsh
epi toy proypologismoy. ''To PASOK exei labei entolh sygkroyshs me ola
ekeina ta mikra kai megala symferonta, poy kratoyn thn Ellada makria apo to
2000. Makria apo thn Enwmenh Eyrwph kai tis eykairies ths. Makria apo thn
anaptyjh. Makria apo ton eksygxronismo me anqrwpino proswpo. Kai ayth thn
entolh, qa thn thrhsoyme'', shmeiwse h k.Papandreoy kai prosqese oti h
kybernhsh einai etoimh na sygkroystei-kai to kanei hdh-gia osa
perilambanontai sto programma ths, opws kai me ton proypologismo.
<P>Gia proypologismo afellhnismoy ths ellhnikhs oikonomias kai koinwnias, poy
einai oikonomika adiejodos kai sthrizei mono toys ''exontes kai
katexontes'', enw parallhla rixnei ola ta barh stis plates twn xamhlwn kai
mesaiwn eisodhmatikwn strwmatwn ekane logo o Proedros toy DHKKI, Dhmhtrhs
Tsobolas. Proeblece oti qa syrriknwqei h paragwgikh bash ths xwras kai qa
kleisoyn xiliades mikromesaies epixeirhseis, enw anaferomenos sto dhmosio
xreos, kathgorhse tis kybernhseis toy PASOK kai ths ND, twn teleytaiwn 7
xronwn, legontas oti to mono poy petyxan htan na to ayjhsoyn se 36 tris
draxmes, dhladh se 120% toy Akaqaristoy Eqnikoy Proiontos (A.E.P.).
<P>Me ton Proedro ths Aigyptoy, Xosni Moymparak qa synanthqei to meshmeri sto
Proedriko Megaro sto Kairo, o Proedros ths Dhmokratias, Kwsths
Stefanopoylos, poy episkeptetai thn Aigypto, synodeyomenos apo ton Ypoyrgo
Ejwterikwn, Qeodwro Pagkalo. Stis synomilies qa paristatai kai o Ypoyrgos
Ejwterikwn ths Aigyptoy, Amr Moysa. Epikentro twn efolhs ths ylhs
synomiliwn twn dyo Proedrwn qa einai ta dimerh qemata. Idiaiterh synanthsh
qa exei o Ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn, k.Pagkalos me ton Aigyptio omologo toy Amr
Moysa, enan texnokrath politiko.
<P>Me th symmetoxh toy yfypoyrgoy Gewrgias, Basilh Geranidh, oloklhrwqhkan
stis Bryjelles oi ergasies toy Symboylioy Ypoyrgwn Alieias ths EE. To
Symboylio chfise kanonismo poy kaqorizei tis alieytikes dynatothtes gia
orismena apoqemata ixqywn, thn katanomh toys sta krath-melh, ta synolika
epitrepomena alieymata gia to 1997 kai orismenoys oroys, ypo toys opoioys
einai dynato na alieyontai, enw apofasise epishs, kata pleiochfia, th
qespish systhmatos elegxoy ths Koinotikhs Alieytikhs Politikhs, me thn
egkatastash enos doryforikoy systhmatos parakoloyqhshs twn alieytikwn
stolwn, olikoy mhkoys megalyteroy twn 20 metrwn.
<P>O programmatismos gia ton aqlhtismo kaqws kai to qema twn paranomwn
stoixhmatwn, htan ta kyria shmeia anaforas, kata th diarkeia ths synanthshs
toy Yfypoyrgoy Aqlhtismoy Andrea Foyra me ton Prwqypoyrgo Kwsta Shmith.
&quot;Enhmerwsa ton Prwqypoyrgo gia ton sxediasmo toy 1997, gia tis aqlhtikes
diorganwseis kai gia thn poreia diekdikhshs twn Olympiakwn Agwnwn toy 2004&quot;,
ypogrammise o k. Foyras, stoys dhmosiografoys.
<P>Th lhch ayjhmenwn astynomikwn metrwn enocei twn eortwn twn Xristoygennwn
kai ths Prwtoxronias, gia thn apotelesmatikh antimetwpish twn eidikwn
problhmatwn poy parathroyntai thn periodo ayth apofasise to Ypoyrgeio
Dhmosias Tajhs. Eidikotera, qa ayjhqoyn oi pezes peripolies astynomikwn, qa
lhfqoyn idiaitera metra asfaleias se xwroys xrhmatikwn synallagwn, enw
ystera apo synennohsh me toys Organismoys Topikhs Aytodioikhshs qa
epidiwxqei h sygkrothsh meiktwn synergeiwn elegxwn, anaforika me to qema
twn paranomwn mikropwlhtwn kai ths epaiteias.
<P>Mhnyma pros toys apodhmoys 'Ellhnes apesteile, me thn eykairia twn eortwn
twn Xristoygennwn kai toy Neoy 'Etoys, o anaplhrwths ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn,
Giwrgos Papandreoy. Sto mhnyma toy o k. Papandreoy ekfrazei tis eyxes toy
stoys apodhmoys kai shmeiwnei, metajy allwn, oti tis giortines aytes hmeres
h skech olwn &quot;strefetai entonotera pros ton Ellhnismo poy diabiei sthn
Oikoymenh kai poy, stis epaljeis toy Ellhnismoy kai ths Orqodojias, ths
paradoshs kai ths pisths, dinei kaqhmerina to fwteino toy parwn&quot;.
<P>Mexri kai 560 drx. ofelos mporei na exei o odhgos se kaqe &quot;foylarisma&quot; toy
rezerboyar toy aytokinhtoy toy, analoga me to benzinadiko poy epilegei. Se
deigmatolhptikh ereyna poy pragmatopoihse to Kentro Prostasias Katanalwtwn
(KEPKA) sta benzinadika toy nomoy Qessalonikhs, diapistwse &quot;anoigma&quot; timwn
poy anerxetai ews kai tis 14 drx. toso gia th super, oso kai gia thn
amolybdh. Sygkekrimena, gia th super kategrace katwtath timh 209 drx. kai
anwtath 223 drx., enw gia thn amolybdh 193 drx. kai 207 drx., antistoixa.
Ws ek toytoy, ena &quot;foylarisma&quot; twn 40 litrwn benzinhs mporei na kostisei
mexri kai 560 drx. akribotera h fqhnotera, analoga me thn periptwsh.
<P>Nwpa kai metapoihmena agrotika proionta ths xwras mas prowqei mesw
oloklhrwmenoy programmatos o Syndesmos Ejagwgewn Boreioy Ellados (SEBE),
stis agores ths Tsexias, ths Slobakias, ths Oyggarias, ths Roymanias, ths
Moldabias kai ths Oykranias. Sto programma -poy ylopoieitai se synergasia
me to ypoyrgeio Gewrgias kai me th xrhmatodotikh sthrijh ths Eyrwpaikhs
Enwshs- symmetexoyn 24 epixeirhseis kai agrotikoi synetairismoi apo olh thn
Ellada.
<P>Tria akomh diathrhtea ktismata , briskontai sthn idiokthsia toy Organismoy
Politistikhs Prwteyoysas ths Eyrwphs &quot;Qessalonikh 1997&quot;. Prokeitai gia
ktismata twn arxwn toy aiwna, ta opoia agorasthkan enanti toy posoy twn 60,
9 ekatommyriwn draxmwn kai briskontai stis odoys Hrodotoy 17A, Axillews kai
Qeofiloy 13. Parallhla, o Organismos Politistikhs Prwteyoysas, ypegrace
symbash gia thn kataskeyh enos neoy xwroy pente xiliadwn qesewn, o opoios
qa filojenei qeatrikes kai moysikes ekdhlwseis.
<P>Se oles tis nomimes energeies, prokeimenoy na apoperatwqei -to syntomotero
dynaton- to ergo ths epixwmatwshs kai ekbaqynshs toy ektoy problhta,
protiqetai na probei o Organismos Limenos Qessalonikhs (OLQ). Me anakoinwsh
toy, o OLQ tonizei oti h ektelesh toy ergoy exei stamathsei edw kai ena
mhna, enw h ylopoihsh toy exei -mexri shmera- proxwrhsei se baqmo 75%.
Jekaqarizei de, oti oi apaithseis twn ergazomenwn apo thn anadoxo toy ergoy
koinoprajia ARMOS, &quot;aforoyn th sygkekrimenh etaireia kai mono&quot;.
<P>Agnwstoi poy emfanizontai ws ypallhloi ths Nomarxias Qessalonikhs kai dhqen
pragmatopoioyn statistikh ereyna, thlefwnoyn se spitia Qessalonikewn kai
zhtoyn na maqoyn pote qa apoysiasoyn apo ta spitia toys, poy qa metaboyn
stis giortes kai poy qa kanoyn diakopes. Me anakoinwsh ths h Nomarxia
Qessalonikhs gnwstopoiei oti kamia yphresia ths de dienergei tetoioy eidoys
ereyna kai proeidopoiei toys katoikoys na exoyn ayjhmenh thn prosoxh toys,
dioti diatrexoyn kindyno na pesoyn qymata diarrhjewn kai toys kalei na
kataggelloyn kaqe ypopto thlefwnhma.
<P>Sto diorismo epta anwterwn stelexwn toy Leykoy Oikoy, metajy twn opoiwn kai
triwn ellhnikhs katagwghs, anaferontai dhmosieymata twn amerikanikwn
efhmeridwn. Ton Tzwrtz Stefanopoylo poy apoxwrei gia na didajei sto
Koloympia, na synergasqei me to ABC kai na gracei biblio, qa antikatasthsei
o Ram Emanoyel. Oi dyo apo toys treis ellhnikhs katagwghs neoproslhfqentes,
o Tzwn Pontesta kai h Sylbia Maqioys, diorisqhkan anaplhrwtes toy neoy
Proswparxh toy Leykoy Oikoy E.Mpooyls. H trith Biktoria Rant, diorisqhke
dieyqyntria toy Grafeioy toy k.Mpooyls.
<P>Sth Qessalonikh qa pragmatopoihqei apo 6 mexri 16 Martioy h 24h Dieqnhs
Synodos toy Eyrwpaikoy Koinoboylioy Newn, sthn opoia qa symmetasxoyn 250
maqhtes apo 22 toylaxiston xwres ths Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs kai ths Kentrikhs
kai Anatolikhs Eyrwphs. H synqesh ths ellhnikhs apostolhs, poy qa
symmetasxei sthn Synodo, qa kaqoristei meqayrio, Kyriakh, sth diarkeia ths
Genikhs Syneleyshs toy Eyrwpaikoy Koinoboylioy Newn Ellados. Antikeimena
ths Genikhs Syneleyshs qa einai oi sxeseis metajy Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs kai
Toyrkias meta tis teleytaies apofaseis ths Eyrwpaikhs Epitrophs kai toy
Eyrwkoinoboylioy, h perifereiakh sygkrothsh ths E.E. kai h arxh ths
epikoyrikothtas, h enarmonish ths eisagwghs twn maqhtwn twn xwrwn - melwn
ths Enwshs sta Panepisthmia kai h antitromokratikh politikh kai ta
Syntagmatika Dikaiwmata se eqniko kai atomiko epipedo.
<P>Apo thn Aqhna, th Qessalonikh, th Larisa, thn Komothnh kai thn Katerinh
proerxontai -kata kyrio logo- oi epixeirhseis poy exoyn dhlwsei symmetoxh
sthn 4h ekqesh ellhnikwn proiontwn sthn Kypro . Sthn ekqesh, poy
diorganwnei h HELEXPO sth Leykwsia apo 15 ews 19 Ianoyarioy 1997,
symmetexoyn epishs -omadika- pente Epimelhthria: Biotexniko Epimelhthrio
Qessalonikhs (BEQ), Epaggelmatiko Epimelhthrio Qessalonikhs, Emporiko kai
Biomhxaniko Epimelhthrio Komothnhs, Emporiko kai Biomhxaniko Epimelhthrio
Larisas, kaqws kai Emporiko kai Biomhxaniko Epimelhthrio Pierias. Malista,
to BEQ epidotei ta melh toy poy qa laboyn meros sthn ekqesh me to poso twn
200.000 drx.
<H4>BALKANIKES EIDHSEIS</H4>
Efqase xqes to apogeyma sto Beligradi h antiproswpeia toy OASE, h opoia qa
ejetasei th diadikasia poy akoloyqhqhke, kata tis dhmotikes ekloges ths
17hs Noembrioy. H antiproswpeia, ths opoias hgeitai o prwhn Prwqypoyrgos
ths Ispanias, Felipe Gkonzales, qa parameinei sth gioygkoslabikh prwteyoysa
ews ayrio.
<P>Syntonismenes epixeirhseis me th symmetoxh bombardistikwn aeroskafwn
enantion stratopedwn toy RKK sto Boreio Irak, alla kai th Notioanatolikh
Toyrkia, pragmatopoioyn oi toyrkikes dynameis asfaleias. Symfwna me thn
efhmerida &quot;Xoyrriet&quot;, eji polemika aeroskafh F-16 poy apogeiwqhkan apo thn
aeroporikh bash toy Ntigiarmpakir, pragmatopoihsan ejodoys stoys
&quot;tromokratikoys stoxoys&quot; Metina kai Xakoyr, stoys opoioys parathrhqhke
kinhtikothta. (Prokeitai gia ta dyo stratopeda opoy prospaqoyn na
stegastoyn ta melh toy RKK sto Boreio Irak).
<P>Tis eyxaristies toys pros tis Hnwmenes Politeies gia &quot;to endiaferon poy
deixnoyn gia thn epilysh toy problhmatos toy Kossyfopedioy&quot;, ejefrasan
amesws meta th synanthsh toys sta Tirana, o Albanos proedros, Sali Mperisa
kai o hgeths twn Albanofwnwn toy Kossyfopedioy, Impraxim Roygkoba. Opws
metedwse h Albanikh Thleorash, oi dyo politikoi xarakthrisan ws
&quot;aparaithth&quot; thn energopoihsh ths Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs kai ths Gallias gia thn
epilysh toy problhmatos aytoy kai xairetisan tis diamartyries twn foithtwn
toy Beligradioy, oi opoies, opws tonisan, &quot;ajizei na yposthrixtoyn&quot;.
<P>Boylgarikh koinoboyleytikh antiproswpeia elabe meros sth synedriash toy
grafeioy ths meikths Koinoboyleytikhs Epitrophs Boylgarias- Eyrwpaikhs
Enwshs, stis Bryjelles. Opws shmeiwse o epikefalhs ths antiproswpeias,
Nikolai Kamof, oi ekproswpoi ths Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs ejefrasan thn anhsyxia
toys gia thn poreia twn metarryqmisewn sth Boylgaria, kaqws kai thn elpida
toys oti h xwra qa deijei pio kathgorhmatikh kai syneph politikh sxetika me
thn epidiwjh ths gia entajh stoys eyrwpaikoys kai toys eyrwatlantikoys
qesmoys. H epomenh synedriash ths meikths Koinoboyleytikhs Epitrophs
Boylgarias- Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs, qa pragmatopoihqei stis 14 kai 15 Aprilioy
toy 1997, stis Bryjelles.
<H4>KAIROS</H4>
H ejasqenish twn anemwn kai oi topikes proskaires broxes qa einai ta kyria
xarakthristika toy shmerinoy kairoy. Sth Qessalonikh qa ekdhlwqoyn topikes
nefwseis me broxh, omws apo to meshmeri o kairos qa beltiwqei. Oi anemoi qa
pneoyn asqeneis enw h qermokrasia sthn polh qa kymanqei apo 6 ews 13
baqmoys Kelsioy.
