<H2>Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in Greek (PM), 96-12-18</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/mpeb">Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-18.mpeb.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-19.mpeb.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Macedonian Press Agency at <A HREF="http://www.mpa.gr">http://www.mpa.gr</A> and <A HREF="http://www.hri.org/MPA">http://www.hri.org/MPA</A>.</H4>
<HR>
<H4>Web Posted: 17:57 GMT+2</H4>
<H3>SYNTOMO BRADINO DELTIO EIDHSEWN - 18.12.1996</H3>
Apo ton Ianoyario qa arxisoyn na kataballontai apozhmiwseis stoys agrotes
twn opoiwn oi kalliergeies eplhghsan apo qeomhnies, tonise o Ypoyrgos
Gewrgias Stefanos Tzoymakas kata th diarkeia synenteyjhs Typoy sthn opoia
paroysiase ta apotelesmata toy Symboylioy twn ypoyrgwn Gewrgias ths
Koinothtas stis Bryjelles. Parallhla o k. Tzoymakas sygkalese gia tis 10
kai 11 Ianoyarioy to Eqniko Symboylio Agrotikhs Politikhs, thn enarjh toy
opoioy qa khryjei o prwqypoyrgos Kwstas Shmiths. Sto Symboylio metexoyn h
hgesia toy ypoyrgeioy Gewrgias, mia diakommatikh epitroph kai agrotikoi
foreis. &quot;H hgesia toy ypoyrgeioy Gewrgias exei proteinei programma
tetraetias me metarryqmiseis, kostologhsh aytoy toy programmatos, sxedia
nomwn, gia na diamorfwqei to neo qesmiko plaisio, opws kai alles politikes
gia na oloklhrwqei mia nea antilhch kai mia nea ejelijh ston tomea ths
gewrgias&quot; prosqese o k. Tzoymakas.
<P>Eleyqerh einai apo to apogeyma h dieleysh twn oxhmatwn apo th diastayrwsh
&quot;Prasina Fanaria&quot; sto dromo pros to aerodromio &quot;Makedonia&quot; ths Qessalonikhs.
Thn apofash gia termatismo toy apokleismoy ths diastayrwshs phre h
Syntonistikh Epitroph Agwna Makedonias - Qrakhs, kata th synedriash ths poy
pragmatopoihqhke to meshmeri sto ktirio ths PASEGES. H kinhsh ayth, kata
toys agrotes apotelei endeijh kalhs qelhshs enocei twn Xristoygennwn,
prokeimenoy na metakinhqei to koino aeroporikws xwris problhmata.
<P>Meiwsh toy kostoys paragwghs kata penhnta eji disekatommyria draxmes, ths
apasxolhshs kata 208.000 hmeromisqia poy antistoixoyn se dyo disekatommyria
draxmes, twn paradosewn kata 134 disekatommyria kai toy kefalaioy kinhsews
ths biomhxanias kata 20%, einai oi synepeies twn agrotikwn kinhtopoihsewn,
opws prokyptei apo ereyna toy Syndesmoy Ellhnikwn Biomhxaniwn poy
pragmatopoihqhke se 530 epixeirhseis. Ta apotelesmata ths ereynas edwse sth
dhmosiothta o Proedros toy Syndesmoy Ellhnikwn Biomhxaniwn Iaswn Stratos.
<P>Gia tis ejelijeis sth Synodo Koryfhs toy Doyblinoy, thn proodo kai tis
ejelijeis se sxesh me thn Eyrwpaikh Enwsh, ta qemata poy sxetizontai me tis
toyrkikes apaithseis kai thn epiqetikh politikh ths Toyrkias kai genika ola
ta qemata ths epikairothtas, enhmerwse to meshmeri ton Proedro ths
Dhmokratias Kwsth Stefanopoylo, o prwqypoyrgos Kwstas Shmiths. Ypodexomenos
ton prwqypoyrgo o k. Stefanopoylos ektimhse ws qetika ta apotelesmata ths
Synodoy Koryfhs ths Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs sto Doyblino enw o k. Shmiths tonise
oti epibebaiwqhke h politikh ths Komision apenanti sthn Toyrkia para to
gegonos oti h k. Tsiller diejhgage paraskhniakes diaboyleyseis gia na
allajei h paragrafos peri toyrkokoinotikwn sxesewn.
<P>Me ton Bretano omologo toy Malkom Rifkint synanthqhke shmera sto Londino o
ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn Qeodwros Pagkalos o opoios ton enhmerwse gia ta eqnika
mas qemata, ta ellhnotoyrkika kai to Kypriako. O k.Pagkalos zhthse
dieykriniseis gia ta deka shmeia - protaseis toy ypoyrgeioy ejwterikwn ths
M. Bretanias gia proodo sthn epilysh toy Kypriakoy. Problhmatismo
dhmioyrgei to dekato shmeio, h diatypwsh toy opoioy yponoei oti prepei
prwta na yparjei lysh toy Kypriakoy kai katopin na arxisoyn oi entajiakes
diapragmateyseis ths Megalonhsoy.
<P>Metra synolikoy kostoys 5,68 dis. draxmwn gia thn anakoyfish kai yposthrijh
twn plhgentwn apo tis plhmmyres kai toy paragwgikoy dynamikoy ths Janqhs
kai gia thn amesh apokatastash twn ypodomwn kai toy oikistikoy istoy twn
perioxwn poy katastrafhkan apo thn prosfath qeomhnia, ejhggeile o Ypoyrgos
PEXWDE, Kwstas Laliwths, o opoios pragmatopoihse episkech stis plhgeises
perioxes toy nomoy. H ylopoihsh twn metrwn aytwn anamenetai na oloklhrwqei
entos toy prwtoy tetramhnoy toy 1997. O k. Laliwths shmeiwse oti ta metra
poy ejhggeile einai symplhrwmatika toy programmatos anaptyjhs toy nomoy
Janqhs, synolikoy ycoys 112 disekatommyriwn draxmwn, poy jekinhse to 1994
kai problepetai na oloklhrwqei to 1999.
<P>Ekrhjh shmeiwqhke to apogeyma sto spiti toy Iapwna presbeyth sthn
prwteyoysa toy Peroy, Lima, opoy xqes to brady eisebalan 30 akroaristeroi
antartes kai katelaban to ktirio. Oi antartes kratoyn diakosioys peripoy
omhroys, metajy twn opoiwn sygkatalegetai kai o Ellhnas presbhs sto Peroy,
Alkibiadhs Karokhs.
<P>Timio kai antiproswpeytiko synedrio ths Neas Dhmokratias zhta o epitimos
Proedros toy kommatos Kwnstantinos Mhtsotakhs se synenteyjh toy se
ebdomadiaio periodiko. Shmeiwnei de oti an gia to epikeimeno synedrio ths
ajiwmatikhs antipoliteyshs den chfisei h bash toy kommatos gia thn eklogh
synedrwn, o idios den prokeitai na symmetasxei se ayto. &quot;An to synedrio den
ginei ton Febroyario me chfoforia apo th bash, h N.D. qa odhghqei se
aytoktonia&quot; tonizei o k. Mhtsotakhs.
<P>Anhsyxies kai problhmatismoys gia thn prooptikh toy SAE ejefrasan o
Proedros toy Symboylioy Apodhmoy Ellhnismoy kai tessera melh toy Proedreioy
toy se dhlwseis toys sto Makedoniko Praktoreio Eidhsewn, amesws meta th
lhjh ths triths synedriashs toys, poy oloklhrwqhke to meshmeri sth
Qessalonikh. Se apokleistikes toy dhlwseis sto MPE o Proedros toy SAE,
Antrioy Aqens, xarakthrise tis syzhthseis poy eixe to Proedreio, sth
diarkeia ths synedriashs toy, me thn politikh hgesia, ws ejairetika ygieis,
ekane, omws, logo kai gia &quot;anhsyxies&quot;.
<P>Ws megalh epityxia poy mporei na exei poly qetika apotelesmata panw sto
kypriako zhthma, xarakthrise o proedros ths kypriakhs dhmokratias, Glaykos
Klhridhs, thn apofash toy Dikasthrioy Anqrwpinwn Dikaiwmatwn toy Symboylioy
ths Eyrwphs, gia thn prosfygh ths Titinas Loizidoy, symfwna me thn opoia h
Toyrkia katadikazetai gia thn parabiash twn dikaiwmatwn idiokthsias ths
Ellhnokyprias. &quot;Kata analogia, stis periptwseis ekeines poy aforoyn
monimoys katoikoys, poy steroyntai tis perioysies kai tis katoikies toys,
oi epiptwseis ths apofashs ayths mporei na einai poly pio megales&quot; prosqese
o k. Klhridhs. Me thn apofash ayth, poy dhmioyrgei dedikasmeno, to
dikasthrio aporriptei toys isxyrismoys ths Toyrkias oti h synqhkh gia ta
anqrwpina dikaiwmata sthn Eyrwph den efarmozetai sthn periptwsh ths
toyrkikhs katoxhs sth boreia Kypro.
<P>Meiwsh stis times twn ygrwn kaysimwn poy qa isxysei apo ta mesanyxta
anakoinwse to meshmeri h Dhmosia Epixeirhsh Petrelaioy. H benzinh qa
pwleitai fqhnotera kata 2,80 draxmes to litro, to ntizel kinhshs kata 2.20
draxmes kai to ntizel qermanshs kata 2.72 draxmes. Oi meiwseis aytes
ofeilontai se ptwsh twn dieqnwn timwn logw ths eisrohs toy Irakinoy
petrelaioy sthn agora. Wstoso, symfwna me plhrofories, apo thn erxomenh
ebdomada qa yparjei kai pali ayjhsh twn timwn twn ygrwn kaysimwn.
<P>Enas shmantikos qesmos ths Qessalonikhs, to Festibal Kinhmatografoy, qa
apotelesei to qema ths synanthshs, stis 21 Dekembrioy, twn forewn poy
sxetizontai me th diorganwsh, oi opoioi qa metaferoyn tis apoceis twn
politwn kai qa diatypwsoyn protaseis gia to mellon. H hmerida, poy qa
filojenhqei sto kentro istorias toy dhmoy me prwtoboylia toy Organismoy
Politistikhs Prwteyoysas ths Eyrwphs Qessalonikh '97, einai idiaitera
epikairh, giati pragmatopoieitai se mia stigmh, kata thn opoia ekkremei to
nomosxedio poy proteine h Epitroph toy Ypoyrgeioy Politismoy gia th xarajh
eqnikhs politikhs gia ton kinhmatografo.
<P>Stadiakh beltiwsh toy kairoy se oloklhrh th xwra problepei gia ayrio h
Eqnikh Metewrologikh Yphresia. Gia th Dytikh Ellada problepontai liges
nefwseis. Sthn ypoloiph xwra arxika qa shmeiwqoyn topikes nefwseis me
sporadikes broxes kai sto aigaio kataigides. Stadiaka o kairos qa beltiwqei.
Oi anemoi qa pneoyn Dytikoi - notiodytikoi asqeneis ews metrioi enw h
qermokrasia qa kymanqei sta boreia hpeirwtika apo 5 ews 14 baqmoys, sto
Ionio kai ta ypoloipa hpeirwtika apo 8 ews 18 kai sta nhsia toy Aigaioy apo
13 ews 19 baqmoys Kelsioy. Sth Qessalonikh ayrio qa ekdhlwqoyn liges
nefwseis, ayjhmenes kyriws tis prwines wres enw oi anemoi qa pneoyn
asqeneis kai h qermokrasia sthn polh qa kymanqei apo 6 ews 13 baqmoys
Kelsioy.
<HR>
<H4>Complete archives of the Macedonian Press Agency bulletins are available
on the MPA Home Page at <A HREF="http://www.mpa.gr/">http://www.mpa.gr/</A> and on the U.S. mirror at
<A HREF="http://www.hri.org/MPA/">http://www.hri.org/MPA/</A></H4>
