<BODY>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<center><a href="/info"><IMG SRC="/gifs/hrnet.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="[HR-Net Banner]"></a><BR></center>

<H2>Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in Greek (PM), 96-12-21</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/mpeb">Macedonian Press Agency: Brief News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-21.mpeb.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-22.mpeb.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Macedonian Press Agency at <A HREF="http://www.mpa.gr">http://www.mpa.gr</A> and <A HREF="http://www.hri.org/MPA">http://www.hri.org/MPA</A>.</H4>
<HR>
<H4>Web Posted: 17:24 GMT+2</H4>
<H3>SYNTOMO APOGEYMATINO DELTIO EIDHSEWN - 21.12.1996</H3>
Prwtoboylia gia mesolabhsh sta ellhnotoyrkika dexetai na analabei o
Proedros ths Aigyptiakhs Dhmokratias Xosni Moymparak, opws dhlwse, to
meshmeri apantwntas se erwthsh toy Makedonikoy Praktoreioy Eidhsewn. Amesws
meta th syzhthsh toy Proedroy ths Ellhnikhs Dhmokratias Kwnstantinoy
Stefanopoyloy kai toy Aigyptioy omologoy toy Xosni Moymparak doqhke koinh
synenteyjh twn dyo andrwn sto Proedriko Megaro se proastio toy Kairoy,
paroysia apo ellhnikhs pleyras kai toy ypoyrgoy Ejwterikwn Qeodwroy
Pagkaloy kai toy Ellhna presbh sto Kairo k. Dhmhtrioy Bidoyrh. O k.
Stefanopoylos paroysiase ston k. Moymparak tis pagies ellhnikes qeseis peri
sebasmoy toy dieqnoys dikaioy kai twn dieqnwn synqhkwn enw kata th
synanthsh epibebaiwqhkan oi qetikes sxeseis twn dyo xwrwn.
<P>Me onomastikh chfoforia oloklhrwnetai ta mesanyxta h penqhmerh syzhthsh toy
proypologismoy gia to 1997. To endiaferon ths shmerinhs synedriashs
estiazetai to apogeyma, opoy qa milhsoyn o Prwqypoyrgos Kwstas Shmiths, o
arxhgos ths ajiwmatikhs antipoliteyshs Miltiadhs Ebert kaqws kai o proedros
toy Synaspismoy Nikos Kwnstantopoylos. Sth shmerinh prwinh synedriash o
yfypoyrgos eqnikhs oikonomias Giwrgos Drys yperaspisthke to neo
proypologismo enw ypogrammise oti sth fash ayth poy briskomaste den einai
dynath h timariqmopoihsh ths forologikhs klimakas h opoia an ginotane qa
apebaine wfelimh mono gia ta megala eisodhmata. Shmeiwse akomh oti h
kybernhsh qa epanejetasei thn eisodhmatikh politikh ths gia ta eisodhmata
toy 1997.
<P>Antiqeseis kai diafwnies epikrathsan stis sygkentrwseis twn agrotwn sth
Qessalia, otan koinopoihqhke h apofash ths syntonistikhs epitrophs, symfwna
me thn opoia, ta trakter qa parameinoyn sta odofragmata kai kata th
diarkeia twn eortwn. H synedriash ths epitrophs diekoph proswrina kai qa
synexistei meta tis eji to apogeyma. Pantws, eleyqerh qa einai apo tis 4 to
apogeyma h dieleysh twn oxhmatwn apo ton Almyro Boloy, afoy oi agrotes
apofasisan na lysoyn to mploko poy yparxei sthn perioxh, ystera apo
chfoforia poy egine xtes meta ta mesanyxta, kata thn opoia 138 taxqhkan
yper ths apoxwrhshs twn trakter kai mono 2 kata. O kybernhtikos ekproswpos
Dhmhtrhs Reppas dhlwse to meshmeri oti h odikh syndesh se olh th xwra
apokaqistatai enw sta shmeia poy paramenoyn omades agrotwn h metakinhsh twn
tajidiwtwn ginetai mesw parakampthriwn dromwn. O ypoyrgos Typoy diabebaiwse
oti lambanontai ola ta aparaithta metra wste na ejasfalizetai h prosbash
twn politwn se oloys toys proorismoys.
<P>Anesteile xqes brady tis kinhtopoihseis h Panellhnia Omospondia Naytikwn
meta thn yposxesh ths kybernhshs oti qa epanejetasei thn katarghsh twn
foroapallagwn twn naytikwn, prin kataqesei to forologiko nomosxedio stis 7
Ianoyarioy. Oi naytikoi proeidopoioyn me nees apergies ean h kybernhsh
epimeinei sthn katarghsh twn foroapallagwn toys. Ta dromologia twn ploiwn
se ola ta limania ths xwras diejagontai kanonika.
<P>Poreia diamartyrias gia ton proypologismo toy 1997, h syzhthsh toy opoioy
oloklhrwnetai ta mesanyxta sth Boylh , pragmatopoihsan stis 11 to prwi sto
kentro ths Qessalonikhs peripoy 300 ekproswpoi dekaepta prwtobaqmiwn
Swmateiwn Ergazomenwn toy nomoy.
<P>Thn pepoiqhsh toy oti enwmenos o Ellhnismos qa antimetwpisei me epityxia
tis toyrkikes proklhseis kai qa yperisxysei to dieqnes dikaio kai h logikh
ekfrazei o Proedros ths Boylhs, Apostolos Kaklamanhs, se mhnyma toy pros
ton Apodhmo Ellhnismo me thn eykairia twn eortwn twn Xristoygennwn kai toy
neoy etoys. Sto mhnyma toy o k.Kaklamanhs ejairei kat'arxhn thn omogeneia
gia ta epiteygmata ths kai ekfrazei ta aisqhmata agaphs ths Boylhs gia toys
apantaxoy Ellhnes. &quot;Toytes tis xroniares hmeres h paroysia sas sthn kardia
kai sthn poreia toy laoy mas ginetai akoma pio entonh. Oi patriwtes sas, oi
syggeneis sas kai oloi oi Ellhnes, me perhfania mnhmoneyoyn ta epiteygmata
sas, giati pragmati me thn pneymatikh kai ylikh sas anodo, lamprynete
pantoy to ellhniko onoma&quot;, anaferei sxetika.
<P>&quot;H epibiwsh ths xwras kai h qesh ths sthn pagkosmia oikonomia qa ejarthqei
apo thn ikanothta na drasoyme anaptyjiaka kai na meiwsoyme to xasma
paragwgikothtas&quot;. Ayto tonise o ypoyrgos Paideias, Gerasimos Arsenhs, sth
shmerinh omilia toy sth Boylh sto plaisio ths syzhthshs gia ton
proypologismo. Symfwna me ton k. Arsenh, treis einai oi proypoqeseis poy qa
katasthsoyn dynath thn proseggish twn stoxwn toy proypologismoy, mesa,
panta, apo ena plaisio mesoproqesmhs strathgikhs gia thn prowqhsh twn
eqnikwn symferontwn ths xwras, thn oikonomikh kai koinwnikh ths anaptyjh
kai th diasfalish ths koinwnikhs synoxhs: oi ajiopistes koinwnikes
symfwnies poy qa epimerizoyn oso pio dikaia ginetai to kostos stis
koinwnikes omades - ena oloklhrwmeno programma ikano na prowqei parallhla
tis oikonomikes, koinwnikes kai anaptyjiakes epiloges - ena oloklhrwmeno
sxedio gia th dieqnh qesh kai thn koinwnikh kai paragwgikh diarqrwsh ths
xwras.
<P>Synedriazei ayrio h ektelestikh epitroph ths Neas Dhmokratias, h opoia
anamenetai na apofasisei gia toys oroys diejagwghs toy synedrioy. O prwhn
ypoyrgos Giwrgos Soyflias me epistolh toy pros ta melh toy politikoy
symboylioy epishmainei oti to komma qa odhghqei se peripeteies ean lhfqoyn
apofaseis poy qa kaqistoyn amfisbhtoymeno to synedrio. Eikosi prwhn
boyleytes ths Neas Dhmokratias, metajy twn opoiwn oi kyrioi Koybelas,
Xatzhgakhs kai Tsiplakos me chfisma poy ejedwsan xqes brady, kathgoroyn ton
Miltiadh Ebert gia meqodeyseis me stoxo na prowqhsei th dikh toy
ypochfiothta sto synedrio.
<P>Sth Qessalonikh qa giortasei ayrio o Proedros toy Dhmokratikoy Koinwnikoy
Kinhmatos, Dhmhtrhs Tsobolas, thn prwth epeteio apo thn idrysh toy kommatos
toy. O k.Tsobolas qa ftasei sto aerodromio &quot;Makedonia&quot; ths Qessalonikhs
stis 10 to prwi kai amesws meta qa metabei sta kentrika grafeia toy
kommatos sthn polh. To apogeyma kai to brady o Proedros toy DHKKI qa einai
o kyrios omilhths sthn epeteiakh ekdhlwsh, poy qa pragmatopoihqei se
kentriko jenodoxeio ths polhs kai sth synestiash poy diorganwnei h Politikh
Organwsh Qessalonikhs toy kommatos.
<P>&quot;Strimwgmenh&quot; perissotero apo pote emfanizetai fetos h xristoygenniatikh
agora ths Qessalonikhs. H oloena enteinomenh oikonomikh dyspragia twn
katanalwtwn, se syndyasmo me ta ojymena problhmata toy emporikoy kosmoy,
alla kai me tis kaqe eidoys kinhtopoihseis (agrotwn kata kyrio logo, alla
kai naytergatwn kai dioikhtikoy proswpikoy twn limaniwn), synqetoyn thn
asxhmh eikona. Ypo ta dedomena ayta, shmantikos ariqmos -megalwn kyriws-
katasthmatwn sto kentro ths polhs proxwrhsan, aytepaggelta, se prosfores
(poy efqanan akomh kai to 50%), se mia prospaqeia na kerdisoyn kati apo to
xameno &quot;edafos&quot;. Achfwntas, bebaia, tis sxetikes agoranomikes diatajeis poy
apagoreyoyn rhta th dienergeia prosforwn xwris thn adeia toy Emporikoy
Syllogoy. Malista, to fainomeno phre megales diastaseis metajy twn
katasthmatwn kallyntikwn.
<P>Thn paraithsh ths boylgarikhs kybernhshs, anakoinwse ligo prin to meshmeri
o prwqypoyrgos, Zan Bintenof, sth diarkeia toy ektaktoy synedrioy toy
kybernwntos Sosialistikoy Kommatos, poy arxise shmera to prwi sth Sofia kai
enw h antiparaqesh anamesa stis diafores omades poy leitoyrgoyn mesa sto
komma, eftase sto anwtero shmeio toys. &quot;Apo shmera to prwi h Boylh qa exei
sth diaqesh ths thn epishmh paraithsh ths kybernhshs kai elpizw oi
sosialistes boyleytes na thn chfisoyn ews to telos toy 1996&quot;, tonise o k.
Bintenof. H paraithsh ths kybernhshs, kata ton k.Bintenof, qa dwsei th
dynatothta sth Dhmokratikh Aristera, stis arxes toy 1997 na sxhmatisei &quot;thn
kybernhsh apo thn opoia exei anagkh h xwra&quot;.
<P>Omofwnia ws pros th lysh toy kypriakoy yparxei metajy Eyrwphs kai Hnwmenwn
Politeiwn dhlwse o amerikanos bohqos ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn gia qemata Eyrwphs
kai Kanada Tzon Kornmploym. O k.Kornmploym anefere oti ola ta stoixeia poy
xreiazontai gia thn epilysh toy kypriakoy yparxoyn kai to mono poy apomenei,
einai h apofash apo thn pleyra twn endiaferomenwn merwn oti exei ftasei h
stigmh gia thn prowqhsh ths lyshs. Shmeiwse akomh oti o Bretanos ypoyrgos
Ejwterikwn Malkolm Rifkint, edwse oysiastikh wqhsh sto kypriako kai
prosqese oti molis topoqethqei h nea omada eqnikhs asfaleias twn HPA qa
ejetastei h analhch prwtoboylias.
<P>Th nea toy ekdosh &quot;H G' Ellhnikh Dhmokratia kai oi qesmoi ths&quot;, paroysiazei
ayrio Kyriakh, stis aiqoyses toy jenodoxeioy &quot;HLEKTRA&quot;, stis 12,30 to
meshmeri, to Makedoniko Praktoreio Eidhsewn.Thn paroysiash, qa kanoyn oi
neoi boyleytes Nikos Gkesoylhs kai Kwstas Karamanlhs kai oi palaimaxoi
koinoboyleytikoi Nikos Zarntinidhs, tews ypoyrgos kai Stefanos Tsaparas,
enw o ypoyrgos Makedonias-Qrakhs Filippos Petsalnikos se xairetisthrio
mhnyma toy ypogrammizei oti &quot;ayth h ajiepainh prospaqeia, deixnei to
endiaferon kai thn eyaisqhsia toy M.P.E. gia th leitoyrgia toy politeymatos
kai ths Boylhs twn Ellhnwn kai ekfrazei tis prwtoporiakes prwtoboylies toy
sto xwro ths enhmerwshs&quot;.
<P>Oi topikes omixles qa einai to kyrio xarakthristiko toy ayrianoy kairoy.
Gia ayrio problepetai sxedon aiqrios kairos kai mono sta Dytika to apogeyma
qa synnefiasei. Oi anemoi qa pneoyn apo dytikes dieyqynseis asqeneis ews
metrioi. Sta boreia hpeirwtika h qermokrasia qa kymanqei apo 5 ews 16
baqmoys, sto Ionio kai ta ypoloipa hpeirwtika apo 8 ews 19 baqmoys kai sta
nhsia toy Aigaioy apo 12 ews 20 baqmoys Kelsioy. Sth Qessalonikh ayrio qa
shmeiwqoyn liges nefwseis kai kata topoys omixles enw oi anemoi qa pneoyn
asqeneis kai h qermokrasia qa kymanqei apo 6 ews 15 baqmoys Kelsioy.
<HR>
