<H2>Cyprus PIO: Turkish Cypriot Press and Other Media, 96-12-18</H2>
<H4>From: &quot;HR-Net News Distribution Manager&quot; &lt;dist@hri.org&gt;</H4>
<H5><A HREF="/news/cyprus/tcpr">Cyprus Press and Information Office: Turkish Cypriot Press Review</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-17.tcpr.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-19.tcpr.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>TURKISH CYPRIOT PRESS AND OTHER MEDIA</H4>
<H4>No.229/96                                           18.12.96</H4>
<HR>
<H3>CONTENTS</H3>
<H4><A HREF="#A1">[A]</a> NEWS ITEMS</H4>
