<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</A> Oi HPA qa syzhthsoyn to Kypriako me thn Toyrkia</H3>
<STRONG>Oyasigkton, 20/12/1996 (KYPE - Dhmhtrhs Apokhs)</STRONG> -- O Amerikanos Ypoyrgos
Ejwterikwn Oyoren Kristofer, sthn kaqierwmenh synenteyjh Typoy kata thn
opoia kanei apologismo toy etoys, anefere oti ena apo ta qemata poy oi
Hnwmenes Politeies exoyn na syzhthsoyn me thn Toyrkia thn epomenh xronia
einai oi prospaqeies gia epilysh twn problhmatwn sthn Kypro.
<P>Apantwntas se erwthsh Toyrkoy dhmosiografoy gia to ean h Toyrkia
synexizei na paramenei xwra prwths grammhs oson afora sta amerikanika
symferonta, o k. Kristofer eipe oti h Toyrkia paramenei mia xwra megalhs
shmasias gia tis Hnwmenes Politeies, einai melos toy NATO kai brisketai se
ena poly strathgiko shmeio toy kosmoy.
<P>Opws eipe o Amerikanos Ypoyrgos h filia twn HPA pros thn Toyrkia einai
poly baqeia kai oi dyo xwres synergasqhkan kala prosfata se mia seira
qematwn.
<P>Eipe oti h Toyrkia bohqhse tis HPA sthn aposyrsh enos ariqmoy
Amerikanwn kai allwn apo to Boreio Irak.
<P>&quot;Synexizoyme&quot;, eipe, &quot;na exoyme dialogo mazi toys gia polla, polla
qemata. Kai exoyme polla qemata na dieyqethsoyme sth diarkeia toy epomenoy
xronoy. Ennow, symperilambanomenhs ths prospaqeias na epilysoyme ta
problhmata sthn Kypro&quot;.
<P>To oti o Amerikanos Ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn anaferqhke sth sygkekrimenh
apanthsh toy sthn Kypro, liges meres meta tis dhlwseis toy Proedroy Klinton,
deixnei th shmasia poy prosdidei h nea kybernhsh Klinton sto Kypriako kai
taytoxrona stelnei mhnyma pros thn Toyrkia oti oi HPA sxediazoyn mesa sto
1997 na qesoyn to Kypriako poly sobara sthn toyrkikh kybernhsh.
<H5>(KYPE/DA/GP)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</A> Sxedio chfismatos gia thn Kypro</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 20/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- Sxedio chfismatos gia thn katastash sthn
Kypro syzhthqhke xqes sto Londino, kata th synedria ths Politikhs Epitrophs
ths Koinoboyleytikhs Syneleyshs toy Symboylioy ths Eyrwphs.
<P>To sxedio chfismatos ypebale o eishghths gia to qema kai Proedros ths
Politikhs Epitrophs Oyggros Boyleyths k. Antras Mparsoni.
<P>O boyleyths Dwros Xristodoylidhs synodeyomenos apo to dieyqynth ths
Yphresias Dieqnwn Sxesewn Giannakh Gewrgiadh elabe meros sth synedria
ypoballontas tropologies gia arketes apo tis pronoies toy sxedioy
chfismatos.
<P>Me th staqerh yposthrijh melwn ths Epitrophs kai para to gegonos oti o
k. Mparsoni aperrice tis protaseis ths kypriakhs antiproswpeias,
yioqethqhkan tropologies poy epiferoyn beltiwseis kai anaskeyes pronoiwn
toy arxikoy keimenoy.
<P>Oi Ellhnes boyleytes Kwnstantinos Bretos kai Basilhs Magginas se stenh
synergasia me thn kypriakh antiproswpeia synebalan shmantika sthn koinh
prospaqeia poy analhfqhke.
<P>To keimeno chfismatos, opws diamorfwqhke apo thn Politikh Epitroph qa
syzhthqei sthn Olomeleia ths Koinoboyleytikhs Syneleyshs toy Symboylioy ths
Eyrwphs poy qa pragmatopoihqei sto Strasboyrgo sta telh Ianoyarioy.
<H5>(KYPE/KN/GP)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="03">[03]</A> Sobares anhsyxies twn syggenwn agnooymenwn</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 20/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- Sobares anhsyxies ekfrazoyn h Epitroph
Prosfygwn ths Boylhs kai oi Epitropes Syggenwn Agnooymenwn sxetika me tis
plhrofories oti o Genikos Grammateas twn Hnwmenwn Eqnwn se epistolh toy
ston Proedro ths Dhmokratias qa zhthsei opws 992 Ellhnokyprioi, klhrwtoi
kai efedroi stratiwtes twn opoiwn h tyxh agnoeitai apo ta pedia twn maxwn
ton Ioylio kai ton Aygoysto toy 1974 na khryxqoyn ypoqetika nekroi.
<P>Toso h Boylh oso kai oi ekproswpoi twn syggenwn twn agnooymenwn kaloyn
thn kybernhsh na zhthsei ejhghseis apo to Geniko Grammatea toy Dieqnoys
Organismoy.
<P>O Proedros ths Epitrophs Prosfygwn kai Agnooymenwn ths Boylhs
Aristofanhs Gewrgioy anefere oti prepei na dieykrinisqei h stash toy
Genikoy Grammatea, toso gia thn poreia ths Diereynhtikhs oso kai gia ta
mellontika sxedia ths Epitrophs Anqrwpinwn Dikaiwmatwn toy OHE, se sxesh
panta me to qema twn agnooymenwn.
<P>Apaithsh, prosqese, einai na doqei amesh lysh kai na arxisei
pragmatikh ereyna gia diakribwsh ths tyxhs twn agnooymenwn.
<P>O k. Gewrgioy eipe oti exoyn syzhthqei oi peraiterw energeies ths
Boylhs kai ths kybernhshs gia dieqnopoihsh toy problhmatos kai oi opoies qa
ejelixqoyn sthn poreia.
<H5>(KYPE/SD/GP)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="04">[04]</A> Dhlwseis Kasoylidh gia to Eyrwpaiko Dikasthrio</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 20/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> --  Den eixe prolabei na synennohqei me ton
omologo toy sthn Aqhna, dhlwse shmera o Kybernhtikos Ekproswpos Giannakhs
Kasoylidhs, protoy o k. Reppas kalesei me xqesinh dhlwsh toy kai alloys
Kyprioys, meta th dikaiwsh Titinas Loizidoy, na prosfygoyn omadika sto
Eyrwpaiko Dikasthrio.
<P>O k.  Kasoylidhs apantoyse se parathrhsh peri &quot;diglwssias&quot; metajy ths
ellhnikhs kybernhshs, h opoia xqes kalese kai alloys Kyprioys na kataqesoyn
prosfygh analogh me ayth ths Titinas Loizidoy kai ths kypriakhs kybernhshs,
poy einai se anamonh enocei sxetikhs gnwmateyshs toy Genikoy Eisaggelea.
<P>&quot;Den eixa prolabei na epikoinwnhsw me ton k. Reppa&quot;, eipe, &quot;gia to
skeptiko ths apochs mas, oti qa prepei protoy prostrejoyme, na melethsoyme
me kaqe sobarothta ton tropo me ton opoio qa proxwrhsoyme, en sxesei me thn
apofash toy Eyrwpaikoy Dikasthrioy&quot;.
<P>&quot;Den diafwnw me thn oysia ths dhlwshs Reppa&quot;, tonise o Ekproswpos,
&quot;aploystata  anaballw gia argotera tis dikes moy dhlwseis, poy qa einai
ap'oti fainetai paromoies, afoy prwta o Genikos Eisaggeleas melethsei kai
probei se ektimhseis kai nomikes symboyles pros thn kybernhsh&quot;.
<P>Anefere oti &quot;kakws&quot; xqes doqhke idiaitero baros sthn anafora toy gia
toys eidikoys apo to ejwteriko, epanalambanontas emfantika oti sthn Kypro
yparxoyn arketa ikanoi nomikoi kai eidikoi qewroyntai kai o Genikos
Eisaggeleas, h Nomikh Yphresia kai polla alla melh toy nomikoy kosmoy kai
asfalws, symplhrwse o Ekproswpos, kai oi synergates toy Genikoy Eisaggelea
apo to ejwteriko.
<H5>(KYPE/KK/GP)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="05">[05]</A> Dhlwseis Kasoylidh gia thn episkech Tsiler sth Mosxa</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 20/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- Oi dhlwseis twn ajiwmatoyxwn ths rwsikhs
kybernhshs gia toys xeirismoys ths Mosxas kata thn prosfath episkech ths
YPEJ ths Toyrkias Tansoy Tsiler, antapokrinontai sthn pragmatikothta,
dhlwse shmera o Kybernhtikos Ekproswpos Giannakhs Kasoylidhs.
<P>Ypenqymizetai, oti Rwsos ajiwmatoyxos dieceyse isxyrismoys ths k.
Tsiler oti katafere na apotrecei thn pwlhsh toy rwsikoy antiaeroporikoy
systhmatos S300, sthn Kypro, afoy opws h idia isxyristhke, ktyphse tesseris
fores to xeri ths sto trapezi.
<P>Milwntas meta th synedria toy Ypoyrgikoy Symboylioy, o k. Kasoylidhs
proebh, parallhla, se ekklhsh pros ta MME opws yparjei &quot;plhrhs syskotish&quot;
gyrw apo to ejairetika lepto qema twn ejoplismwn, gia logoys asfaleias.
<H5>(KYPE/KK/GP)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="06">[06]</A> Epistrefei ayrio o Proedros toy DHSY</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 20/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- Epistrefei ayrio sthn Kypro o Proedros toy
Dhmokratikoy Synagermoy Giannakhs Matshs, meta apo thn epityxh egxeirhsh
kardias sthn opoia ypoblhqhke prosfata sto Londino.
<P>Symfwna me anakoinwsh toy kommatos, o k. Matshs den endeiknytai na
epanadrasthriopoihqei protoy parelqei h synhqhs metegxeirhtikh periodos,
toylaxiston mexri to telos toy Ianoyarioy.
<P>O k. Matshs epeleje na epistrecei sthn Kypro prin ta Xristoygenna, gia
na perasei mazi me thn oikogeneia toy tis giortes, anaferei h anakoinwsh.
<H5>(KYPE/RAG/MM)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="07">[07]</A> H Rwsia epanabebaiwnei: Den diaforopoieitai h stash mas gia toys
ejoplismoys ths Kypriakhs Dhmokratias</H3>
Leykwsia, 20/12/1996 (KYPE-NOBOSTI - Xristos Gewrgioy)-- Den prokeitai na
yparjei diakoph ths kyprorwsikhs synergasias sta qemata poy aforoyn sthn
agora, apo rwsikoys oikoys stratiwtikoy amyntikoy ejoplismoy, gia tis
anagkes ths Kypriakhs Dhmokratias.
<P>To zhthma ayto jekaqarise meta thn shmerinh enhmerwsh poy egine sthn
kypriakh kybernhsh, mesw ths presbeias ths Dhmokratias sth Mosxa, apo toys
armodioys paragontes toy rwsikoy Ypoyrgeioy Ejwterikwn, anaforika me thn
apaithsh ths Ypoyrgoy Ejwterikwn ths Toyrkias, Tansoy Tsiler, na
pagopoihsei h Mosxa thn piqanh pwlhsh toy antiaeroporikoy pyraylikoy
systhmatos S300.
<P>Symfwna me egkyres plhrofories toy rwsikoy Praktoreioy Eidhsewn,
NOBOSTI, oi Rwsoi ajiwmatoyxoi epanabebaiwsan me ton pio kathgorhmatiko
tropo th qesh ths rwsikhs kybernhshs sto qema ayto, kati poy katesthsan
safes kai sthn k. Tsiler, h opoia paroysiasqhke, dhqen, aisiodojh oti
katafere na peisei th rwsikh kybernhsh na diaforopoihsei thn stash ths.
<P>Epiproqetes plhrofories toy KYPE gia to qema anaferoyn oti h Tansoy
Tsiler eqese, gia thn timh twn oplwn, to aithma ths enwpion ths rwsikhs
hgesias, afoy h Mosxa eixe jekaqarisei prin dyo ebdomades, me koinopoihsh
ths, dia ths diplwmatikhs odoy, thn proqesh ths na mhn syzhthsei kan to
qema ayto, kata th diarkeia ths episkechs Tsiler sthn rwsikh prwteyoysa.
<P>Me thn epishmh enhmerwsh poy etyxe shmera h kypriakh kybernhsh anoigei
oysiastika o dromos gia thn monografhsh ths kat' arxhn symfwnias gia thn
agora toy perifhmoy systhmatos S300.
<H5>(KYPE/XG/MM)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="08">[08]</A> Deikths Timwn Xrhmatisthrioy</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 20/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- O Deikths Timwn Metoxwn toy Xrhmatisthrioy
Ajiwn Kyproy diamorfwqhke sth shmerinh xrhmatisthriakh synanthsh ws
akoloyqws:
<PRE>
     Genikos Deikths Timwn Metoxwn          81.59 (-0.04)

     Deiktes Timwn ana Klado

     Trapezikoi Organismoi                  90.88 (-0.22)
     Egkekrimenoi Ependytikoi Organismoi    74.29 (+1.18)
     Asfalistikoi Organismoi                56.30 (+1.06)
     Biomhxanikes Etaireies                 83.54 (-0.36)
     Toyristikes Epixeirhseis               71.48 (+0.59)
     Emporikes Etaireies                    60.98 (+1.58)
     Alles Etaireies                        66.43 (-1.64)

     Ogkos Synallagwn                       LK 498690 .980
</PRE>
* H diafora stis parenqeseis antiproswpeyei thn posostiaia ayjhsh (+) h th
meiwsh (-) toy deikth apo thn prohgoymenh xrhmatisthriakh synanthsh.
<H5>(KYPE/MM)</H5>
