<H2>Cyprus News Agency: News in Greek, 96-12-19</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/cyprus/kype">Cyprus News Agency: News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-18.kype.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-20.kype.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Cyprus News Agency at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.cyna.org.cy">http://www.cyna.org,cy</A>&gt;</H4>

<HR>
<H3>PERIEXOMENA</H3>
<H4>
<DIR>
  <LI><A HREF="#01">[01]</A> YPEJ: To Martio toy 1998 qa arxisoyn oi entajiakes
  <LI><A HREF="#02">[02]</A> O Tom Koj epishmainei tis paraleiceis toy dekalogoy Rifkint
</DIR>
</H4>
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</A> YPEJ: To Martio toy 1998 qa arxisoyn oi entajiakes</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 19/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- Arxes toy 1998, me pio piqanh periodo to
Martio, qa arxisoyn oi entajiakes diapragmateyseis, ektima o Ypoyrgos
Ejwterikwn Alekos Mixahlidhs, ekfrazontas taytoxrona th bebaiothta, oti h
Kypros to 2000 qa einai melos ths E.E. &quot;anejarthta apo tis antirrhseis ths
Toyrkias kai tis epifylajeis tritwn&quot;.
<P>Milwntas kata th diarkeia synanthshs Ypoyrgwn ths kybernhshs, me melh
toy KEBE kai ths OEB, poy egine shmera to apogeyma sth Leykwsia, o YPEJ
epeshmane ejalloy, oti qa prepei na eimaste etoimoi na dexqoyme kai tis
synepeies.
<P>To gegonos oti h Ellada einai hdh isotimo melos, prosqese o
k. Mixahlidhs, &quot;einai to megalo xarti gia th Kypro kai osoi exoyn
epifylajeis otan fqasoyme ejw apo th porta ths E.E., qa einai adynato na
doyn alles xwres na eiserxontai, xwris na mpainoyme kai emeis&quot;.
<P>Alla einai anagkh, synexise, na eimaste etoimoi gia to neo bhma,
shmeiwnontas, oti ws isotimo melos ths E.E. qa prepei na dexqoyme tis
synepeies toy na zoyme se ena xwro oikonomika eniaio.
<P>Qa prepei, eipe, na eimaste etoimoi mexri tote na zhsoyme se ena poly
entona, antagwnistiko klima.
<P>H Eyrwmesogeiakh Diaskech, anefere o YPEJ, exei anoijei ena neo
kefalaio, me stoxo to 2011, na katalhjei se mia zwnh eleyqeroy emporioy, h
opoia na kalyptei th notia kai anatolikh Mesogeio.
<P>Epomenws poly syntoma qa breqoyme se ena neo kosmo, entona
antagwnistiko alla kai me poly megales eykairies.
<P>Gi' ayto to logo, anefere o k.  Mixahlidhs, h dikh moy enqarrynsh
peran twn problhmatwn poy h kaqe biomhxania antimetwpizei, einai me poio
tropo qa proetoimastei h kaqe biomhxania kai o kaqe klados xwrista kai
synolika olh mazi h biomhxania ths Kyproy, gia na epwfelhqei apo tis
megales eykairies kai tis dynatothtes poy qa breqoyn mprosta ths.
<P>Gia tis emporikes kai biomhxanikes dynatothtes poy paroysiazontai sto
xwro ths Meshs Anatolhs kai twn Balkaniwn, ypogrammise oti aytes einai
&quot;tromera megales&quot;, kai parotrynontas emmesws toys biomhxanoys pros aythn th
kateyqynsh, tonise oti &quot;twra prepei na jekinhsoyme protoy na einai arga kai
protoy trejoyn alloi&quot;.
<P>&quot;Qa prepei na kinhqoyme apo koinoy, katelhje o YPEJ, kai ws kybernhsh
kai ws organwseis kai atomika ws epixeirhmaties, dynamika, gia na
etoimastoyme gi' ayth th megalh poreia, th megalh eykairia poy mas
prosferetai poly syntoma&quot;.
<H5>(KYPE/KK/GP)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</A> O Tom Koj epishmainei tis paraleiceis toy dekalogoy Rifkint</H3>
<STRONG>Londino, 19/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- Thn paraleich toy Bretanoy YPEJ Malkolm
Rifkint na symperilabei sto dekalogo toy to rolo ths Toyrkias sto Kypriako,
kaqws epishs kai thn protash Klhridh gia apostratikopoihsh, epeshmane o
boyleyths toy Ergatikoy Kommatos ths Bretanias Tom Koj, se parembash toy se
synedria ths Boylhs.
<P>H parembash toy Ergatikoy boyleyth egine kata th Xristoygenniatikh
synedria ths Boylhs, sthn opoia o kaqe boyleyths exei to dikaiwma na
egeirei opoio qema epiqymei, xwris na labei ypoyrgikh apanthsh.
<P>Dystyxws, shmeiwse o k. Koj, h dhlwsh toy Ypoyrgoy Ejwterikwn den
perieixe to shmantiko qema toy roloy ths Toyrkias kai ths Agkyras se
opoiesdhpote synomilies gia to Kypriako.
<P>O Bretanos Ergatikos ypogrammise oti h Agkyra apotelei paragonta-
kleidi sto Kypriako, ejaitias twn stenwn ths desmwn poy exei me ton
katoxiko hgeth Raoyf Ntenktas.
<P>&quot;O Ser Nteibint Xanei, o Eidikos Antiproswpos ths Bretanias gia to
Kypriako, episkeptetai syxna thn Toyrkia gia synomilies. Anamenoyme, loipon,
oti h Toyrkia qa diadramatisei shmantiko rolo stis diapragmateyseis&quot;,
tonise o k. Koj.
<P>Anaferomenos sthn persinh symfwnia telwneiakhs enwshs EE-Toyrkias, o
Bretanos boyleyths ypenqymise pws &quot;yparxoyn kapoia antallagmata sthn
politikh&quot;.
<P>Ena kratos, prosqese, &quot;poy exei epityxei ton epiqymhto stoxo qa prepei
sth synexeia na symbalei qetika se qemata, sta opoia mporei na askhsei thn
epirroh toy, opws h Toyrkia sthn Kypro&quot;.
<P>Prepei, symplhrwse, h Bretania ws eggyhtria dynamh kai ws melos ths
Koinopoliteias na jekaqarisei sthn Toyrkia oti einai men eyprosdekth stis
diapragmateyseis, ejaitias toy roloy poy mporei na diadramatisei alla den
qa exei to dikaiwma ths arnhsikyrias toso sto qema ths lyshs toy Kypriakoy
oso kai sto qema ths entajhs ths nhsoy sthn Eyrwpaikh Enwsh.
<P>Ena allo qema prosqese, to opoio den exei anaferqei sth dhlwsh toy k.
Rifkint htan h protash toy Proedroy Klhridh gia apostratikopoihsh ths
Kyproy.
<P>O k. Koj, xarakthrise thn protash gia apostratikopoihsh ws ejelijh
zwtikhs shmasias ejaitias ths entonhs stratiwtikhs paroysias sto nhsi.
<P>&quot;Qa htan poly endiaferon na gnwrizoyme thn apoch toy Ypoyrgoy
Ejwterikwn kai ths kybernhshs anaforika me thn protash Klhridh gia
apostratikopoihsh&quot;, shmeiwse o Ergatikos boyleyths.
<P>Katalhgontas o Tom Koj anaferqhke sthn probolh ths episkechs Rifkint
apo to bretaniko Typo.
<P>Ystera apo 22 xronia dixotomhshs toy nhsioy, &quot;sigoyra epiqymoyme mia
dikaih dieyqethsh&quot;, tonise o Tom Koj, ekfrazontas parallhla thn elpida, oti
oi synomilies poy arxizoyn ton epomeno xrono qa epityxoyn.
<P>Wstoso, epeshmane &quot;exoyn hdh arxisei oi apaithseis toy Raoyf Ntenktas -
oi opoies synexizontai apo ta gegonota toy 1974- se sxesh me thn entajiakh
poreia ths Kyproy&quot;. O katoxikos hgeths, prosqese, einai epiqetikos apenanti
sto qema ths entajhs, enw exei apoceis gia thn kyriarxia, thn asfaleia kai
to edafiko.
<P>&quot;Toyrkikh cyxroloysia gia thn apostolh Rifkint&quot;, katelhje o Bretanos
Ergatikos, epanalambanontas titlo ths efhmeridas &quot;Intepentent&quot;.
<P>O ekproswpos ths bretanikhs kybernhshs dhlwse oti qa metaferei tis
apoceis stoys armodioys Ypoyrgoys.
<H5>(KYPE/KT/KN/GP)</H5>
