<H2>Cyprus News Agency: News in Greek, 96-12-21</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/cyprus/kype">Cyprus News Agency: News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-20.kype.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-22.kype.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: The Cyprus News Agency at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.cyna.org.cy">http://www.cyna.org,cy</A>&gt;</H4>

<HR>
<H3>PERIEXOMENA</H3>
<H4>
<DIR>
  <LI><A HREF="#01">[01]</A> Dhlwseis Kornmploym gia thn Kypro
  <LI><A HREF="#02">[02]</A> Kyprioi boyleytes se progeyma proseyxhs me ton Proedro Klinton
</DIR>
</H4>
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</A> Dhlwseis Kornmploym gia thn Kypro</H3>
<STRONG>Oyasigkton, 21/12/1996 (KYPE - Dhmhtrhs Apokhs)</STRONG> -- O Amerikanos Bohqos
Ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn gia qemata Eyrwphs kai Kanada, Tzon Kornmploym,
pragmatopoiwntas ton ethsio apologismo toy, anaferqhke sto Kypriako
legontas oti yparxei mia entonh omofwnia sthn Eyrwph, tis HPA, alla kai thn
Kypro sxetika me to oti to Kypriako prepei na lyqei twra.
<P>&quot;Qa elega oti yparxei mia entonh omofwnia sthn Eyrwph, stis HPA, kai
nomizw kai sthn Kypro, sxetika me to oti ayto einai ena qema poy xreiazetai
na lyqei twra&quot;, dhlwse stoys dhmosiografoys.
<P>Opws anafere o k. Kornmploym ola ta stoixeia poy xreiazontai gia
epilysh toy problhmatos yparxoyn, kai to mono poy apomenei einai h apofash
apo thn pleyra twn endiaferomenwn merwn oti exei fqasei h stigmh gia thn
prowqhsh lyshs.
<P>&quot;Nomizw oti exoyme ola ta stoixeia gia lysh ekei, kai enapokeitai twra
stoys symmetexontes, ayto perilambanei ta merh sto nhsi, thn Eyrwpaikh
Enwsh, tis HPA kai ta Hnwmena Eqnh, na apofasisoyn ean einai h katallhlh
stigmh gia thn prowqhsh lyshs&quot;, shmeiwse.
<P>Telos o k. Kornmploym epeshmane oti o Bretanos YPEJ Malkolm Rifkint
edwse oysiastikh wqhsh sto Kypriako me thn prosfath episkech toy sthn Kypro,
kai prosqese oti molis topoqethqei h nea omada eqnikhs asfaleias twn HPA qa
ejetasqei kata poso exei fqasei h stigmh gia analhch prwtoboylias me stoxo
th lysh.
<P>&quot;O Ypoyrgos Rifkint nomizw edwse mia poly shmantikh wqhsh me thn
episkech toy. Kai qa doylecoyme molis h nea omada mas topoqethqei. Qa
doylecoyme poly sklhra gia na doyme ean o xronos exei fqasei na analaboyme
thn prwtoboylia,'' prosqese.
<H5>(KYPE/DA/MM)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</A> Kyprioi boyleytes se progeyma proseyxhs me ton Proedro Klinton</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 21/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- Epafes me toys apodhmoys kai ta melh
toy Kogkresoy kai ths Geroysias, qa pragmatopoihsei h boyleyths toy
Dhmokratikoy Kommatos, Katerina Pasxalidoy, sthn Oyasigkton, sta plaisia
programmatos poy perilambanei programma proseyxhs me ton Amerikano Proedro,
Mpil Klinton.
<P>Toso h k. Pasxalidoy oso kai oi boyleytes toy DHKO, Markos Kyprianoy,
kai twn Enwmenwn Dhmokratwn, Androyla Basileioy, exoyn apanthsei qetika se
proswpikes prosklhseis gia na laboyn meros sto progeyma proseyxhs poy qa
pragmatopoihqei stis 6 Febroyarioy sto Oyasigkton Xilton.
<P>Oi Kyprioi boyleytes, qa parakaqhsoyn sto progeymma mazi me epishmoys
apo alles xwres, melh toy Kogkresoy kai to proedriko zeygos. To programma,
eipe se dhlwseis ths sto RIK shmera h k. Pasxalidoy, perilambanei epishs
deipno kai geyma ergasias kaqws kai epafes me Amerikanoys epishmoys.
<P>H prosklhsh, anefere, einai apo ta melh ths Geroysias kai toy
Kogkresoy, enw h epilogh, egine meta apo systaseis ths boyleyth toy
Dhmokratikoy Synagermoy, Kaith Klhridoy, h opoia elabe meros sto programma
ayto.
<P>H k. Pasxalidoy eipe, oti an kai den einai yper ths politikhs ths
epanaproseggishs, entoytois prokeitai gia &quot;mia poly kalh eykairia na dw ti
perilambanoyn ta programmata ayta, gia poio logo ginontai, kai kyriws gia
na exw epafes me toys Geroysiastes kai ta melh toy Kogkresoy gia to diko
mas qema (to Kypriako). Me ton tropo ayto, qa mporesei, eipe, na
diamorfwsei apoceis sxetika me thn amerikanikh prwtoboylia.
<P>To programma qa pragmatopoihqei apo tis 4 - 7 Febroyarioy. Symfwna me
thn k. Pasxalidoy, stis synanthseis aytes ginetai dialogos gia diafora
flegonta qemata ston kosmo, kaqws kai se tropoys eirhnikhs antimetwpishs
toys.
<P>H k. Pasxalidoy eipe oti den gnwrizei kata poso exoyn prosklhqei T/K.
Ta ejoda qa epibarynoyn toys boyleytes kai h paroysia twn Kypriwn boyletwn
den apotelei epishmh apostolh ths Boylhs.
<H5>(KYPE/AXR/MM)</H5>
<HR>
