<HR>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</A> Domhmenos Dialogos EE-Kyproy</H3>
<STRONG>Bryjelles, 18/12/1996 (KYPE - Nikos Mpellos)</STRONG> -- Thn ikanopoihsh toys gia th
shmantikh proodo poy emfanizei h Kypros ston tomea ths prosarmoghs ths sto
koinotiko kethmeno kaqws kai gia tis ikanopoihtikes epidoseis ths kypriakhs
oikonomias, ejefrase stis Bryjelles, toso h irlandikh proedria oso kai h
Eyrwpaikh Epitroph.
<P>Oi topoqethseis aytes eginan kata th diarkeia xqesinhs synanthshs, sto
plaisio toy domhmenoy dialogoy metajy Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs - Kyproy.
<P>Sth synanthsh ayth poy pragmatopoihqhke stis Bryjelles elaban meros
apo koinotikhs pleyras, o Irlandos Ypoyrgos proedreywn toy Symboylioy
Ypoyrgwn Oikonomias (ECOFIN) k. Ruairi Quin kai o armodios epitropos Yves-
Thibault de Silguy. Apo kypriakhs pleyras symmeteixan o Ypoyrgos
Oikonomikwn Xristodoylos Xristodoyloy, o Dioikhths ths Kentrikhs Trapezas
ths Kyproy Ayjenths Ayjentioy kai o monimos antiproswpos ths Kyproy sthn
Eyrwpaikh Enwsh, presbhs Mixalhs Attalidhs.
<P>Kata th diarkeia ths synanthshs h koinotikh antiproswpeia enhmerwse
thn kypriakh gia ta apotelesmata toy Eyrwpaikoy Symboylioy toy Doyblinoy
kai kyriws tis apofaseis poy lhfqhkan sto plaisio ths triths fashs ths
oikonomikhs kai nomismatikhs enwshs.
<P>Syzhthqhkan epishs makrooikonomika qemata, oi diarqrwtikes
metarryqmiseis kai h texnikh synergasia metajy Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs-Kyproy.
<P>Apo kypriakhs pleyras egine enhmerwsh gia thn poreia sygklishs ths
oikonomias stis apaithseis ths Synqhkhs toy Maastrixt gia to eniaio
nomisma.
<P>Sto shmeio ayto o Irlandos Ypoyrgos kai o Epitropos ejefrasan thn
plhrh ikanopoihsh toys oxi mono gia thn prosarmogh ths Kyproy sto koinotiko
kekthmeno alla xairetisan kai tis proqeseis ths Leykwsias na katarghsei to
nomo poy problepei  ton kaqorismo toy anwtatoy epitokioy kaqws kai na
apeleyqerwsei thn kinhsh twn kefalaiwn.
<H5>(KYPE/NM/GP)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="02">[02]</A> Synanthsh Klhridh - Kyprianoy</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 18/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- H episkech toy Bretanoy Ypoyrgoy Ejwterikwn
Malkolm Rifkint apotelese to antikeimeno prwinhs synanthshs toy Proedroy
ths Dhmokratias Glaykoy Klhridh me ton Proedro ths Boylhs kai Proedro toy
DHKO Spyro Kyprianoy.
<P>Opws metadidei to RIK, egine ektenhs anafora sta deka shmeia poy
paroysiase o Bretanos YPEJ.
<P>O k. Kyprianoy dhlwse stoys dhmosiografoys oti qewrei shmantiko to
gegonos oti den yphrje opoiadhpote desmeysh apo meroys ths kybernhshs gia
to olo qema.
<P>Parallhla ejefrase orismenes epifylajeis gia merika shmeia kai genika
th bretanikh politikh sto Kypriako, ypenqymizontas th qesh toy eidikoy
antiproswpoy ths Bretanias sto Kypriako, Ser Nteibint Xanei gia to qema twn
epoikwn.
<P>O Ser Nteibint eixe anaferei ston Proedro ths Boylhs oti kai oi
epoikoi exoyn apokthsei &quot;kapoia dikaiwmata&quot;, yponowntas oti den mporoyn na
fygoyn oloi se periptwsh lyshs.
<H5>(KYPE/MM/GP)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="03">[03]</A> Dikaiwnetai h Titina Loizidoy</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 18/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- To Dikasthrio Anqrwpinwn Dikaiwmatwn toy
Symboylioy ths Eyrwphs apofasise, me 11 chfoys yper kai eji kata, oti
yparxei synexizomenh parabiash twn anqrwpinwn dikaiwmatwn ths Ellhnokyprias
Titinas Loizidoy.
<P>Opws dhlwse sto KYPE o ek twn dikhgorwn ths k. Loizidoy, Axilleas
Dhmhtriadhs, sthn apofash toy to Eyrwpaiko Dikasthrio anaferei oti
synexizetai h parabiash twn anqrwpinwn dikaiwmatwn ths k. Loizidoy &quot;se
sxesh me thn akinhth perioysia ths sthn Keryneia, h opoia apo to 1974
brisketai katw apo ton elegxo toy toyrkikoy stratoy&quot;.
<P>O k. Dhmhtriadhs anefere oti h shmasia ths apofashs egkeitai sto oti
gia prwth fora h Toyrkia paroysiazetai dieqnws ypologh gia tis parabiaseis
anqrwpinwn dikaiwmatwn logw ths synexizomenhs katoxhs meroys ths Kypriakhs
Dhmokratias.
<P>Thn apofash toy Dikasthrioy qa analysoyn argotera shmera se synenteyjh
Typoy o Genikos Eisaggelas Alekos Markidhs kai o k. Dhmhtriadhs.
<H5>(KYPE/MA/GP)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="04">[04]</A> Sth Boylh gia egkrish to ejoplistiko programma</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 18/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- Sth Boylh parapempetai pros egkrish to
pentaetes ejoplistiko programma ths Eqnikhs Froyras, to opoio katartisthke
me bash tis eishghseis toy Ypoyrgeioy Amynas kai ths Eqnikhs Froyras.
<P>Se shmerinh syskech poy pragmatopoihqhke sto GEEF, kai sth opoia
symmeteixan to Eqniko Symboylio kai h armodia Epitroph Amynas ths Boylhs,
paroysiasthke to neo ejoplistiko programma se syndyasmo me tis anagkes ths
E.F.
<P>Opws dhlwse o Proedros ths Dhmokratias Glaykos Klhridhs, meta th
syskech, &quot;egine mia plhrhs enhmerwsh panw sth shmerinh katastash ths
Eqnikhs Froyras kai epejhghqh to epomeno pentaetes programma kai poies
einai oi anagkes&quot;. Anefere epishs oti to ejoplistiko programma proxwrei
kanonika.
<P>O proypologismos, prosqese, exei paei sth Boylh kai an qa ginoyn
allages qa ejarthqei apo th Boylh. Ekeino to opoio qa egkriqei, katelhje o
Proedros Klhridhs, qa einai to neo ejoplistiko programma, to opoio kai qa
ylopoihqei.
<H5>(KYPE/KK/MM)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="05">[05]</A> Megalh epityxia h dikaiwsh ths Titinas Loizidoy</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 18/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> --  Megalh epityxia, poy mporei na exei
terasties epiptwseis panw sto Kypriako, xarakthrise o Proedros ths
Dhmokratias Glaykos Klhridhs thn apofash toy Dikasthrioy Anqrwpinwn
Dikaiwmatwn toy Symboylioy ths Eyrwphs, sthn prosfygh ths Titinas Loizidoy.
<P>Poly shmantikh, xarakthrise thn apofash kai o Genikos Eisaggeleas
Alekos Markidhs, ypogrammizontas  oti ayth einai ametaklhth kai afora
parabiash dikaiwmatos idiokthsias. Oi dhlwseis eginan sto GEEF, meta th
syskech toy Eqnikoy Symboylioy kai ths Epitrophs Amynas ths Boylhs gia to
ejoplistiko programma kai afoy, kata th diarkeia ths syskechs, to Swma
enhmerwqhke apo th Genikh Eisaggelia gia thn apofash sto Strasboyrgo.
<P>Opws dhlwse o Proedros Klhridhs, sxoliazontas thn apofash, to
Dikasthrio apofasise oti para to gegonos oti h k. Loizidoy den katoikoyse
ekei, entoytois to gegonos oti ths esterhsan to dikaiwma na paei sto spiti
ths, apotelei parabiash kai oti prepei na plhrwsei h Toyrkia apozhmiwseis.
<P>Erwthqeis, gia tis epiptwseis poy h apofash dikaiwshs ths Titinas
Loizidoy mporei na exei sto Kypriako, o Proedros  Klhridhs tonise oti aytes
&quot;mporei na einai terasties, an laboyme ypoch oti yparxoyn kai ekeinoi poy
anagkasthkan na fygoyn apo ta spitia  sta opoia katoikoysan&quot;.
<P>&quot;Dioti&quot;, epeshmane, &quot;sth periptwsh Loizidoy prokeitai peri ejoxikhs
katoikias. Kat'analogia&quot;, prosqese o Proedros Klhridhs, &quot;stis periptwseis
ekeines poy aforoyn monimoys katoikoys poy steroyntai ths perioysias kai
ths katoikias toys, tote oi epiptwseis mporei na einai poly pio megales&quot;.
<P>Ejalloy, o Genikos Eisaggeleas Alekos Markidhs tonise stis dikes toy
dhlwseis oti &quot;prokeitai gia poly shmantikh apofash&quot;, poy brhke thn Toyrkia
enoxh parabiashs toy dikaiwmatos idiokthsias.
<P>O k. Markidhs apefyge na pei, apantwntas se sxetikh erwthsh, pws qa
ajiopoihqei h en logw apofash, parathrwntas oti  den einai ths paroysas
stigmhs na ginontai sxolia gia tis mellontikes proektaseis kai synepeies.&quot;
<P>&quot;Ayto qa einai to teleytaio sxolio poy qa ginei&quot;, tonise emfantika,
&quot;dioti h kypriakh kybernhsh&quot;, ejhghse o k. Markidhs, &quot;ekrine oti eprepe na
parei mia atomikh prosfygh politoy ths, poy den eixe ginei dekth apo thn
Epitroph, na th metabibasei dia ypomnhmatos enwpion toy Eyrwpaikoy
Dikasthrioy, toy opoioy h apofash einai ametaklhth&quot;.
<P>H oysia, katelhje, einai oti symfwna me thn apofash, h k. Loizidoy
paramenei idiokthtria ths ghs gia thn opoia exei ypobalei to sxetiko
parapono. Prokeitai gia parapono parabiashs toy dikaiwmatos idiokthsias.
<H5>(KYPE/KK/GP)</H5>
<H3><A NAME="06">[06]</A> Deikths Timwn Xrhmatisthrioy</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 18/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- O Deikths Timwn Metoxwn toy Xrhmatisthrioy
Ajiwn Kyproy diamorfwqhke sth shmerinh xrhmatisthriakh synanthsh ws
akoloyqws:
<PRE>
     Genikos Deikths Timwn Metoxwn          81.08 (+0.17)

     Deiktes Timwn ana Klado

     Trapezikoi Organismoi                  90.25 (+0.27)
     Egkekrimenoi Ependytikoi Organismoi    73.97 (+1.23)
     Asfalistikoi Organismoi                55.55 (+0.40)
     Biomhxanikes Etaireies                 83.27 (+1.10)
     Toyristikes Epixeirhseis               70.84 (-0.21)
     Emporikes Etaireies                    60.19 (-3.04)
     Alles Etaireies                        67.52 (-0.22)

     Ogkos Synallagwn                       LK 600870 .301
</PRE>
* H diafora stis parenqeseis antiproswpeyei thn posostiaia ayjhsh (+) h th
meiwsh (-) toy deikth apo thn prohgoymenh xrhmatisthriakh synanthsh.
<H5>(KYPE/MX)</H5>
