<HR>
<H3><A NAME="01">[01]</A> Ekqesh ths Gallikhs Arxaiologikhs Sxolhs Aqhnwn sthn Kypro</H3>
<STRONG>Leykwsia, 22/12/1996 (KYPE)</STRONG> -- Me thn eykairia twn 150 xronwn apo thn
idrysh ths Gallikhs Arxaiologikhs Sxolhs Aqhnwn, to Galliko Morfwtiko
Kentro, paroysiazei sthn Kypro thn ekqesh &quot;Xwros Ellhnikos - 150 xronia
anaskafwn ths Gallikhs Arxaiologikhs Sxolhs Aqhnwn&quot;.
<P>Ta egkainia ths ekqeshs, poy qa jekinhsei prwta apo thn Aqhna kai sth
synexeia metaferqei sthn Kypro, qa ginoyn stis 17 Ianoyarioy sthn Aiqoysa
Melinas Merkoyrh. H ekqesh qa parameinei sth Leykwsia mexri tis 9
Febroyarioy kai qa metaferqei sto Parisi kai alles eyrwpaikes prwteyoyses.
<P>H ekqesh qa paroysiazei tis maketes twn arxaiologikwn xwrwn poy exoyn
anaskafei apo th Gallikh Arxaiologikh Sxolh twn Aqhnwn kata ta teleytaia
150 xronia. Tetoioi xwroi einai oi Delfoi, to Argos, h Dhlos, kai h
Amaqoynta, opoy oi anaskafes arxisan prin apo 20 xronia.
<P>H Kypros ekproswpeitai sthn ekqesh me maketes poy paroysiazoyn thn
Akropolh ths Amaqoyntas, to nao ths Afrodiths kaqws epishs kai thn
palaioxristianikh periodo me th basilikh ths akropolhs.
<P>Ston xwro ths ekqeshs qa pragmatopoihqei epishs seira dialejewn me
qema ton arxaiologiko xwro ths Amaqoyntas kaqws kai thn paroysiash megalwn
arxaiologikwn xwrwn opoy ginontai anaskafes apo Kyprioys kai Galloys
arxaiologoys.
<H5>(KYPE/AXR/MM)</H5>
