<H2>Cosmos Nea - Eidhseis (Dec. 20)</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/greek/cosmos">Cosmos News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-17.cos.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-23.cos.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: G.A.E.P.I.S. &lt;<A HREF="http://www.gaepis.org">http://www.gaepis.org</A>&gt;</H4>
<H4>* Prosfora toy mh kerdoskopikoy organismoy Meswn Enhmerwshs G.A.E.P.I.S.*</H4>
<H4>* <A HREF="mailto:cosmos@panix.com">cosmos@panix.com</A> - Tel 718 728-1500, P.O. BOX 828 Suffern, NY 10901 *</H4>
<HR>
<H4>
<UL>
<LI>Na parameinoyn sta mploka apofasisan oi agrotes ths Qessalias.
Anesteilan tis kinhtopoihseis oi synadelfoi toys ths Makedonias kai
Qrakhs. Sthn idia kateyqynsh kai oi agrotes ths Peloponhsoy.
<LI>Lynoyn ta ploia, anastelloyn tis kinhtopoihseis toys oi naytikoi,
meta th qetikh synanthsh me toys armodioys ypoyrgoys.
<LI>Metra gia thn prostasia twn katanalwtwn apo toys foyskwmenoys
logariasmoys ths EYDAP, ejhggeile h kybernhsh.
<LI>Neo xastoyki ths Tansoy Tsiler apo th Mosxa. Den katafere na
apotrecei thn pwlhsh oplikwn systhmatwn sthn Kypro.
<LI>Thn Kyriakh epi taphtos sthn Ektelestikh Epitroph ths Neas
Dhmokratias, oi diadikasies gia ton tropo diejagwghs toy synedrioy.
<LI>Dyo nekroi kai dyo traymaties se sygkroysh trenoy me IX aytokinhto
sthn Pella.
<LI>Sthn Aigypto o proedros ths Dhmokratias gia tetrahmerh epishmh
episkech.
<LI>To xrisma twn efedrwn ajiwmatikwn twn Enoplwn Dynamewn, phran
shmera oi Olympionikes mas ths Atlanta.
<LI>Arsh toy trapezikoy aporrhtoy ths Ellhs Stah, zhta h ejetastikh
epitroph ths boylhs.
<LI>Krisimh h katastash twn omhrwn sto Peroy, meta thn arnhsh ths
kybernhshs na ikanopoihsei ta aithmata twn antartwn.
<LI>Alla 15 atoma kratoyntai omhroi sto Tatzikistan apo aytonomistes
antartes.
<LI>Gia 33h mera synexizei h antipoliteysh sto Beligradi tis
kinhtopoihseis ths.
<LI>Ptwsh 0,58% sto Xrhmatisthrio.
<LI>Beltiwsh apo ta dytika qa paroysiasei ayrio o kairos. Metrioi oi
anemoi, to qermometro qa deijei apo 6 mexri 19 baqmoys.
</UL>
</H4>
<HR>
<H3>OI EIDHSEIS MAS ANALYTIKA</H3>
Anypoxwrhtoi oi agrotes ths Qessalias, epimenoyn stis
kinhtopoihseis toys kai arga to apogeyma h syntonistikh epitroph
agwna apofasise omofwna na parameinoyn ta trakter sta mploka. Mexri
stigmhs den exei dieykrinistei an oi agrotes qa epitrecoyn th
dieleysh twn ekdromewn, pros thn eparxia, enocei twn eortwn twn
Xristoygennwn. Oi agrotes ths Larisas epanelaban to aithma toys gia
synanthsh me ton prwqypoyrgo, gegonos poy epaneilhmmena exei
aporricei h kybernhsh, oso paramenoyn apokleismenoi oi dromoi.
Antiqeta, oi agrotes ths Makedonias kai ths Qrakhs apofasisan shmera
thn anastolh twn kinhtopoihsewn toys ki etsi apo tis 4 to apogeyma
apeleyqerwqhkan oi dromoi kai mesw toy Nomarxh zhthsan synanthsh me
ton prwqypoyrgo, h opoia symfwna me plhrofories qa pragmatopoihqei
tis prosexeis hmeres. Analogo klima epikratei kai sthn perioxh ths
Peloponnhsoy, opoy oi agrotes apeleyqerwsan th syragga toy Artemisioy,
enw sthn idia kateyqynsh prosanatolizontai oi agrotes toy Aigioy. O
kybernhtikos ekproswpos xarakthrise eyglwth th siwph twn politikwn
arxhgwn, sto qema twn epizhmiwn kai proklhtikwn, opws eipe, agrotikwn
apokleismwn, ektimwntas oti me ton tropo ayto toys apodexontai. O
k. Reppas prosqese oti o kaqenas mporei na diatypwnei ta aithmata toy,
alla ayth poy xarazei thn politikh einai h kybernhsh, symfwna me thn
ierarxhsh twn qematwn.
<P>Thn anastolh twn apergiakwn kinhtopoihsewn twn Ellhnwn naytikwn
apofasise se polywrh synedriash ths h Ektelestikh Epitroph ths PNO
poy prohgoymena mazi me omada efoplistwn eixe episkefqei sto grafeio
toy ton yfypoyrgo Oikonomikwn, Giwrgo Dry. Me thn idia apofash ths h
Panellhnia Naytikh Omospondia qa prokhryjei nea 48wrh apergia gia thn
8h Ianoyarioy 1997 ean h kybernhsh den ylopoihsei th desmeysh ths.
Meta th lhjh ths apergiakhs kinhtopoihshs mono apo to limani toy
Peiraia qa apopleysoyn mexri tis prwtes prwines wres panw apo 15
aktoploika ploia metaferontas sta nhsia toy Aigaioy, thn Krhth kai ta
Dwdekanhsa panw apo 5. 000 epibates, 2. 000 ntalikes kai dekades
stratiwtes oi opoioi prepei na paroysiasqoyn egkaira stis monades
toys.
<P>Tria metra, poy qa teqoyn se efarmogh apo to telos Ianoyarioy kai
exoyn stoxo thn prostasia twn katanwlwn ths EYDAP, anakoinwse o
yfypoyrgos PEXWDE Xrhstos Berelhs. Symfwna me ton yfypoyrgo qa
sygkrothqoyn se kaqe pararthma ths EYDAP, oligomelh synergeia texnikwn
prokeimenoy na ejyphretoyn ayqhmeron toys katanalwtes gia kaqe
problhma poy dhmioyrgeitai. Parallhla, den qa ekdidontai logariasmoi
an to mhxanografiko systhma entopizei oti einai ayjhmenoi kata 50%,
se sxesh me to antistoixo perysino trimhno kai ycoys anw twn 50. 000
draxmwn. Stis periptwseis aytes qa eidopoieitai amesws o katanalwths,
prokeimenoy na diapistwqei poy yparxei problhma. Telos, sthn epitroph
poy ejetazei toys foyskwmenoys logariasmoys qa symmetexei kai
ekproswpos ths Topikhs Aytodioikhshs.
<P>Me patagwdh apotyxia stefqhke h prospaqeia ths ypoyrgoy Ejwterikwn
ths Toyrkias, Tansoy Tsiler na apotrecei thn pwlhsh toy pyraylikoy
systhmatos S-300, apo th Rwsia sthn Kypro. Epistrefontas sthn Agkyra
apo th Mosxa, h kyria Tsiler dhlwse oti phre th diabebaiwsh apo th
Rwsikh kybernhsh, pws den qa pwlhqoyn ta opla ayta, legontas
xarakthristika oti ktyphse th groqia ths sto grafeio toy rwsoy
prwqypoyrgoy. H dhlwsh ayth diaceysqhke kathgorhmatika apo th Rwsia,
enw sthn Aqhna o kybernhtikos ekproswpos dhlwse pws den yparxei
kanena problhma metajy Kyproy kai Rwsias gia thn promhqeia twn S-300.
<H3>EJWTERIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
Koryfwnetai h agwnia gia thn tyxh twn 400 jenwn diplwmatwn poy
kratoyntai ws omhroi sthn iapwnikh presbeia toy Peroy, sth Lima, apo
aristeristes antartes, kaqws h peroybianh kybernhsh anakoinwse oti
arneitai na ikanopoihsei to aithma twn antartwn na apeleyqerwsei
toys 500 kratoymenoys maxhtes ths organwshs toys. To prwi, o proedros
toy Peroy, Almperto Foytzimori, synanthqhke me ton ypoyrgo ejwterikwn
ths Iapwnias, alla opws dhlwse iapwnas ajiwmatoyxos, yparxoyn
diaforetikes apoceis metajy twn dyo xwrwn oson afora thn antimetwpish
toy problhmatos. Thn idia wra, h katastash twn omhrwn einai dramatikh
kaqws hdh exoyn paroysiasqei problhmata ygeias. Sthn Oyroygoyah, to
kinhma Toypamaros zhthse apo thn kybernhsh ths xwras na analabei
prwtoboylies gia na epilyqei eirhnika h krish, enw o proedros toy
Ekoyador, se mia prospaqeia ektonwshs ths katastashs, dhlwse oti
einai etoimos na xorhghsei asylo stoys antartes. Dieykrinise wstoso,
oti den prokeitai gia politiko asylo. Sthn Aqhna, o kybernhtikos
ekproswpos dhlwse oti o presbhs mas sto Peroy, Aristeidhs Karokhs,
eixe entolh apo thn ellhnikh kybernhsh, na diafylajei ton eayto toy
kai oxi na diapragmateyqei me toys antartes, dioti se aytes tis
periptwseis, opws yposthrije, den yparxoyn kanones dikaioy.
<P>To idio skhniko diadramatizetai kai sto Tatzikistan, opoy mia
enoplh omada aixmalwtise 15 atoma, metajy twn opoiwn kai oktw
stratiwtikoys parathrhtes toy OHE, kai apeilei na toys skotwsei
ean den ginoyn dekta ta aithmata toys entos dyo hmerwn. Oi drastes
katelaban mia aytokinhtopomph pente aytokinhtwn, me proswpiko twn
Hnwmenwn Eqnwn, ejw apo thn prwteyoysa Ntoysanmpe kai zhtoyn thn
apeleyqerwsh toy adelfoy toy arxhgoy twn antartwn, poy ton perasmeno
mhna syntaxqhke me tis kybernhtikes dynameis.
<P>Sth Serbia, gia 33h hmera oi foithtes synexisan tis kinhtopoihseis
toys sto kentro toy Beligradioy, se endeijh diamartyrias gia thn
eklogikh noqeia toy kybernwntos sosialistikoy kommatos. Saranta
xiliades atoma breqhkan antimetwpa me tis eidikes dynameis ths
astynomias, kaqws apekleisan mia gefyra sto kentro ths polhs.
<P>Stenos synergaths toy prwqypoyrgoy toy Israhl, Mpenzamin
Netaniaxoy, dhlwse se synenteyjh toy oti to Israhl endexomenws qa
apodexotan mia palaistiniakh ontothta poy qa apokaleito kratos, ypo
orismenes omws proypoqeseis, metajy twn opoiwn oti den qa exei
aperioristh kyriarxia, oti den qa mporei na exei strato 250. 000
atomwn kaqws kai oti den qa mporei na paragei dika toy symbatika h mh
symbatika opla.
<P>Sthn Tsetsenia, oi dynameis asfaleias proebhsan se aqroes
syllhceis ypoptwn gia th dolofonia twn eji melwn toy Eryqroy Stayroy,
thn perasmenh Trith sto xwrio Nobi Atatzi. Xqes, oi aytonomistes
antartes eperrican thn eyqynh se rwsikes mystikes yphresies.
<H3>ALLES ESWTERIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
Synedriazei thn Kyriakh h Ektelestikh Epitroph ths Neas
Dhmokratias gia na syzhthsei tis protaseis sxetika me ton tropo
diejagwghs toy synedrioy. O k. Ebert feretai apofasismenos na thrhsei
sklhrh stash apenanti stoys eswkommatikoys toy antipaloys kai
protiqetai na apodexqei thn protash Barbitsiwth me orismenes allages
poy exei proteinei o k. Soyflias. Den apodexetai omws, thn eklogh twn
epipleon ekproswpwn apeyqeias apo ta melh toy kommatos. Mexri stigmhs
den exei dieykrinistei ean h Ektelestikh Epitroph qa labei oristikh
apofash thn opoia qa eishghqei sthn Kentrikh Epitroph, h qa
diatypwsei enallaktikes eishghseis. O k. Soyflias protiqetai, opws
anaferoyn synergates toy, na antidrasei entona toso gia th
meqodologia lhchs ths apofashs oso kai gia ayth kaq'eayth thn
apofash.
<P>Tetrahmerh epishmh episkech sthn Aigypto pragmatopoiei apo to prwi
o Proedros ths Dhmokratias, Kwsths Stefanopoylos, synodeyomenos apo
ton ypoyrgo Ejwterikwn, Qeodwro Pagkalo. Ayrio to meshmeri o
k. Stefanopoylos qa exei synomilies me ton Aigyptio omologo toy, Xosni
Moymparak, sth diarkeia ths opoias qa ejetasqoyn oi ejelijeis sto
Mesanatoliko, oi dimereis sxeseis, kaqws kai to Kypriako. Se mhnyma
toy, pros toys apodhmoys, enocei twn eortwn, o k. Stefanopoylos
tonizei pws o xronos poy perase afhnei se problhmatikh ekkremothta ta
eqnika mas qemata, an kai kateblhqhsan ikanes prospaqeies kai
shmeiwqhkan bhmata qetikhs antimetwpishs toys. O k. Stefanopoylos
ejairei th drasthriopoihsh twn apodhmwn gia thn prowqhsh twn eqnikwn
mas qematwn kai synista omocyxia, egrhgorsh kai synergasia olwn gia
na dikaiwqoyn oi prosdokies mas.
<P>Loyketo gia 3 ews 25 meres bazei to ypoyrgeio oikonomikwn se 10
epixeirhseis kai eleyqeroys epaggelmaties poy meta apo elegxo
diapistwqhke oti ekanan forodiafygh. Apo ton katalogo poy doqhke sth
dhmosiothta prokyptei oti stis 4 apo tis epixeirhseis epiblhqhkan
poines kleisimatos apo 20 ws 25 meres. Oi kyrwseis aytes arxisan na
trexoyn apo tis 16 Dekembrioy. Se alles 3 h poinh einai gia 12 ws 18
meres, enw gia tis ypoloipes 3 gia 3 mexri 5 meres.
<P>Frikto qanato brhkan o 48xronos Xaralampos Ermidhs kai h peqera
toy, Elpida Aqanasakh, otan to aytokinhto sto opoio epebainan,
parabiase thn mpara kai ton fwteino shmatodoth, se diabash konta
sthn Arnissa toy nomoy Pellas, me apotelesma na parasyrqei apo
dierxomenh amajostoixia poy ekteloyse to dromologio
Qessalonikh-Flwrina. Sobara traymatismenoi einai h syzygos toy
Kwnstantina, kaqws kai o 14xronos gios toy Alejandros.
<P>Allo ena omws qanathforo troxaio shmeiwqhke, ayth th fora ejw
apo to xwrio Xiona Axaias, me apotelesma na skotwqoyn o 60xronos
Alejandros Mpisias kai h syzygos toy Oyrania, 52 xronwn, enw sobara
traymatias einai o 29xronos gios toys Loykas. To dystyxhma synebh otan
to IX poy odhgoyse o gios, jefyge, apo agnwstoys mexri stigmhs
logoys, kai sygkroysthke me IX forthgo poy odhgoyse o Panagiwths
Katsaniwths.
<P>Efedroi ajiwmatikoi twn triwn oplwn twn Enoplwn Dynamewn,
onomasthkan shmera oi olympionikes mas kata th diarkeia eidikhs
teleths poy egine sth Lesxh Ajiwmatikwn Enoplwn Dynamewn. Kata thn
diarkeia ths teleths poy egine paroysia sysswmhs ths politikhs kai
stratiwtikhs hgesias twn Enoplwn Dynamewn, oi Nikos Kaklamanakhs,
Akakios Kaxiasbili, Iwannhs Melissanidhs kai h Nikh Mpakogiannh,
onomasqhkan efedroi yposmhnagoi, o Lewnidas Kokkas efedros ypoloxagos,
o Balerios Lewnidhs efedros ypoploiarxos kai o Pyros Dhmas loxagos.
Parallhla, o ypoyrgos Eqnikhs Amynas toys apeneime diamnhmoneysh
ajias kai timhs.
<P>Thn arsh toy trapezikoy kai forologikoy aporrhtoy, ths
dhmosiografoy Ellhs Stah, zhta h ejetastikh epitroph ths Boylhs, poy
diereyna thn ypoqesh toy kazino sto Floisbo. H epitroph apofasise
epishs na kalesei gia nea kataqesh ton antiproedro toy Areioy Pagoy,
Eyaggelo Riko, o opoios prohdreye sthn epitroph kazino, poy xorhgoyse
tis adeies.
<P>Qrasytath lhsteia shmeiwqhke to meshmeri ston Paradeiso
Amaroysioy, otan agnwstoi arpajan tsanta me 10 ekat. drx. apo ton
ypallhlo toy radiothleoptikoy staqmoy SKA`I`, Dhmhtrh Moro. Oi lhstes
htan dyo, epebainan se motosikleta kai plhsiasan to aytokinhto toy
Moroy, poy htan stamathmeno se fanari kai afoy espasan me losto to
tzami toy synodhgoy arpajan thn tsanta me ta xrhmata kai
ejafanisqhkan.
<A NAME="sports"></A><H3>AQLHTIKES EIDHSEIS</H3>
O Entoyarnt Iorntaneskoy, gios toy Roymanoy omospondiakoy proponhth
Anxel, einai o jenos paikths poy qa antikatasthsei ton Argentino
Xoyan-Xose Mporeli ston Panaqhnaiko, symfwna me thlegrafhma toy
Gallikoy praktoreioy eidhsewn. H symfwnia anamesa stis dyo pleyres
ekleise prin dyo peripoy mhnes, kata thn diarkeia ths synanthshs poy
eixan o Anxel Iorntaneskoy me ton proedro ths PAE Panaqhnaikos Giwrgo
Bardinogiannh, o opoios eixe proteinei parallhla ston Roymano
proponhth na analabei thn texnikh hgesia twn prasinwn, alla o
Iorntaneskoy protimhse na krathsei to posto toy omospondiakoy
proponhth. Opws anaferetai sto thlegrafhma toy Gallikoy Praktoreioy, o
Entoyarnt Iorntaneskoy prokeitai na ypogracei syntoma symbolaio ston
Panaqhnaiko.
<H3>XRHMATISTHRIO</H3>
Mikrh ypoxwrhsh shmeiwse o genikos deikths timwn kata th shmerinh
synedriash toy Xrhmatisthrioy, meta apo tesseris synexeis anodikes
synedriaseis, opoy eixe katagracei kerdh se pososto 4,18%. O deikths,
ekleise stis 938,20 monades, shmeiwnontas ypoxwrhsh se pososto 0,58%.
H ajia twn synallagwn kymanqhke se idiaitera ychla epipeda kai
sygkekrimena diamorfwqhke sta 55,187 dis. drx kyriws logw
metabibasewn paketwn metoxwn. Oi epimeroys deiktes paroysiasan tis
ejhs metaboles: Trapezes ptwsh 0,64%, Asfaleies anodos 1,45%, Lhzingk
1,37%, Ependyseis anodos 0,90%, Kataskeyes ptwsh 0,68%, Biomhxanies
ptwsh 0,68%, Diafores ametablhtes, Symmetoxwn 0,07%. O deikths ths
parallhlhs agoras shmeiwse mikrh ypoxwrhsh 0,28%. Se ebdomadiaia bash
o genikos deikths timwn paroysiase kerdh se pososto 3,57%.
<H3>KAIROS</H3>
Sto Aigaio qa periorisqoyn ayrio oi broxes kai oi sporadikes
kataigides, grhgora omws o kairos qa beltiwqei apo ta dytika pros ta
anatolika. Oi anemoi qa einai notioi metrioi kai topika sto Aigaio
isxyroi, stadiaka omws apo ta dytika qa strafoyn se boreiodytikoys
kai qa ejasqenhsoyn. H qermokrasia sta boreia qa kymanqei 6 me 14
baqmoys, sto Ionio kai ta ypoloipa hpeirwtika 8 me 18 kai sto Aigaio
13 me 19 baqmoys Kelsioy. Arxika nefwseis me topikh broxh, alla
grhgorh beltiwsh, metrioys anemoys kai qermokrasia 10 me 16 kai 6 me
13 antistoixa, qa exoyn ayrio Aqhna kai Qessalonikh.
