<H2>MILS: News from the FYROM, 96-12-20</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/balkans/mils">Macedonian Information Liaison Service</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-19.mils.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-23.mils.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: &quot;Macedonian Information Liaison Service&quot; &lt;<A HREF="mailto:mils@mils.spic.org.mk">mils@mils.spic.org.mk</A>&gt;</H4>
<HR>
<H3>CONTENTS</H3>
<H4>
