<H2>OMRI: Daily Digest, Vol. 2, No. 243, 96-12-18</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/balkans/omri">Open Media Research Institute: Daily Digest</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-17.omri.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-19.omri.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: Open Media Research Institute &lt;<A HREF="http://www.omri.cz">http://www.omri.cz</A>&gt;</H4>
<H4>Vol. 2, No. 243, 18 December 1996</H4>
