<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Logos News from Cyprus, 96-12-20</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<center><a href="/info"><IMG SRC="/gifs/hrnet.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="[HR-Net Banner]"></a><BR></center>

<H2>Logos News from Cyprus, 96-12-20</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/cyprus/logos">Logos News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-19.logos.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-21.logos.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: LogosNet at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.logos.cy.net">http://www.logos.cy.net</A>&gt;</H4>
<HR>
<P>Apanthsh, apo to pleon epishmo atomo, ton Proedro ths Dhmokratias, phran
shmera, Hnwmena Eqnh, Bretania kai Hnwmenes Politeies, sxetika me thn
diamorfwsh koinoy edafoys.
<P>O Proedros Klhridhs dhlwse oti h prooptikh ths enarjhs synomiliwn, xwris
thn yparjh koinoy edafoys, einai dysoiwnh.
<P>Oi synomilies qa odhghqoyn se adiejodo, prosqese o Proedros, efoson oi dyo
pleyres qa paraqetoyn tis gnwstes qeseis toys.
<P>H dhlwsh toy Proedroy ektimatai oti apeyqynetai, toso ston Gkoystab Feissel,
o opoios ejefrase thn apoch oti to koino edafos mporei na ejeyreqei kata
thn diarkeia twn diapragmateysewn, oso kai sthn xqesinh dhlwsh toy Bretanoy
Ypatoy Armosth, o opoios eipe oti ta deka shmeia toy Malkom Rifkint mporoyn
na ginoyn koinws apodekta kai apo tis dyo pleyres.
<P>Sxetika me tis anhsyxies poy ekfrazoyn dieqneis paragontes, gia toys
ejoplismoys sthn Kypro, o Proedros Klhridhs anefere ws aitia ths anhsyxias
toys, to gegonos oti twra ginetai katanohto oti h Kypros einai ena
hfaisteio poy mporei na ekragei kai na apostaqeropoihsei ta Balkania kai
thn Eyrwph.
<P>Emeis, pantws, prosqese o Proedros ths Dhmokratias, oso kalytera
ejoplismenoi eimaste, toso ligotero prepei na anhsyxoyme.
<HR>
Pisteyoyme, oti oi ejoplismoi sthn Kypro den prosferoyn, kat'anagkh, sthn
prowqhsh ths diadikasias epilyshs toy kypriakoy, eipe shmera o presbeyths
twn Hnwmenwn Politeiwn, sthn Leykwsia, Keneq Mpril.
<P>O kyrios Mpril eixe eqimotypikh, opws thn xarakthrise, synanthsh me ton
Proedro Klhridh, apofeygontas na apokalycei to periexomeno ths.
<P>Apantwntas, wstoso, se erwthseis, eipe oti h apofasistikothta twn Hnwmenwn
Politeiwn na ergastoyn gia to kypriako, ekfrasthke apo tis dhlwseis toy
Mpil Klinton, meta apo thn synanthsh poy o Amerikanos Proedros eixe me ton
Proedro ths Eyrwpaikhs Epitrophs, Zak Santer kai ton Irlando prwqypoyrgo,
Tzwn Mproyton, sthn Oyasigktwn.
<P>Ta eggrafa poy dhmosiopoihqhkan meta thn synanthsh toy Mpil Klinton me thn
hgesia ths Eyrwpaikhs Enwshs, prosqese o Keneq Mpril, anaferoyn oti stoxos
einai h prowqhsh ameswn synomiliwn, sto prwto ejamhno toy 1997.
<HR>
Ikanopoihsh gia thn proodo twn ergasiwn anergershs twn stratiwtikwn
egkatastasewn sthn Pafo, ejefrase h Epitroph Amynhs ths Boylhs.
<P>H koinoboyleytikh Epitroph episkefqhke to prwi tis egkatastaseis oi opoies
entassontai sto plaisio toy eniaioy amyntikoy sxediasmoy kai enhmerwqhke
gia thn poreia ylopoihshs toy programmatos.
<HR>
Entonh anhsyxia ekfrazei h Epitroph Agnooymenwn ths Boylhs, gia tis
plhrofories sxetika me to periexomeno ths epistolhs toy aperxomenoy
Genikoy Grammatea twn Hnwmenwn Eqnwn Mpoytros Gkali, gia toys
agnooymenoys.
<P>O kyrios Gkali eishgeitai thn khryjh ws ypoqetika nekrwn, xiliwn peripoy
agnooymenwn, oi opoioi xaqhkan kata thn wra ths drashs.
<P>Meta to telos ths synedrias ths Epitrophs h opoia egine kekleismenwn twn
qyrwn, o Proedros ths Epitrophs Aristofanhs Gewrgioy, dhlwse oti to
problhma qa parameinei anoikto mexris otoy diakribwqei h tyxh enos ekastoy
twn agnoymenwn mas.
<P>H nea ejelijh sto problhma twn agnooymenwn anamenetai na apotelesei to
kyrio qema syskechs sto proedriko, stis 27 Dekembrioy.
<HR>
Epta paidia egklwbismenwn qa perasoyn ta Xristoygenna makria apo tis
oikogeneies toys.
<P>Gi' allh mia fora o katoxikos hgeths edeije to apanqrwpo proswpo toy,
apagoreyontas th metabash sta katexomena twn paidiwn poy exoyn symplhrwsei
to legomeno orio hlikias, to opoio qetei to katoxiko kaqestws.
<P>En tw metajy h daskala Elenh Fwka, h opoia synexizei na paramenei omhros
toy katoxikoy hgeth, se epistolh ths pros to Proedro ths Dhmokratias zhtei
thn parembash toso twn Hnwmenwn Eqnwn oso kai toy Symboylioy
Asfaleias.
<HR>
Metaseismikes donhseis eixan oi xqesines kataggelies toy boyleyth Kikh
Giagkoy afoy toso o Kybernhtikos Ekproswpos oso kai o Ypoyrgos Dikaiosynhs
edwsan shmera synexeia sto qema kai estrecan ta pyra toys kata toy
boyleyth.
<P>O kyrios Kasoylidhs dhlwse oti den parakoloyqeito o kyrios Giagkoy apo thn
Astynomia alla o kyrios Antwnhs Fanieros, me ton opoio o boyleyths symfwna
me ton Kybernhtiko Ekproswpo synantato kai synagelazeto.
<P>Apo thn pleyra toy o Ypoyrgos Dikaiosynhs dieceyse oti synetrwge me
egklhmaties enw kalese ton kyrio Giagkoy na dwsei tis plhrofories poy exei
ston anejarthto Poiniko Anakrith.
<HR>
Epwfelhs xarakthrisqhke h synergasia ths EDEK me ta ypoloipa aristera
kommata stis dhmotikes ekloges.
<P>O Proedros ths EDEK Basos Lyssaridhs ejefrase thn ektimhsh oti to komma
toy shmeiwse anodo.
<P>O kyrios Lyssaridhs se dhlwseis toy meta thn synedria toy Politikoy
Grafeioy toy kommatos toy, apanthse sthn oysia qetika se ena dialogo gia
synexish ths synergasias stis eperxomenes proedrikes ekloges.
<P>O Proedros ths EDEK anefere oti h ypochfiothta toy den apotelei proypoqesh
gi' ayth thn synergasia.
<HR>
Sthn Ellada twra, opoy gia prwth fora apo enarjews twn dynamikwn agrotikwn
kinhtopoihsewn, arxisan na diafainontai kapoies elpides, gia epilysh ths
krishs.
<P>Oi syntonistikes epitropes twn agrotwn sthn Makedonia kai th Qrakh,
apofasisan shmera na aroyn ton apokleismo twn eqnikwn odwn, kai na
synexisoyn ton dialogo toys me thn kybernhsh.
<P>Oi agrotes ths Qessalias, apo thn allh, oi opoioi mexri twra thrhsan
sklhroterh stash enanti ths kybernhshs Shmith, syskeptontai gia na
apofasisoyn ean qa termatisoyn h qa synexisoyn tis kinhtopoihseis
toys.
<HR>
Me aisqhmata entonotaths anhsyxias, to pagkosmio parakoyloyqei thn
synexizomenh omhria 380 atomwn, sto ktirio ths Iapwnikhs Presbeias sth Lima
toy Peroy.
<P>Toys foboys ths dieqnoys koinothtas, gia thn tyxh twn omhrwn enisxyse kai
h shmerinh apofash ths kybernhshs toy Peroy, na aporricei ta aithmata twn
antartwn.
<P>Me th sklhrh stash ths kybernhshs ths Lima, fainetai na diafwnei kaqeta to
Tokyo, to opoio kai epimenei sthn epideijh elastikothtas, foboymeno, oti oi
antartes dynato na ylopoihsoyn tis apeiles toys kai na arxisoyn na ekteloyn
toys omhroys.
<P>Xqes brady oi antartes, afhsan eleyqeroys tessereis diplwmates metajy twn
opoiwn kai o Presbhs ths Ellados sto Peroy, Alkibiadhs Karokhs.
<P>O kyrios Karokhs, brisketai hdh kaqodon pros thn Ellada.
<HR>
Xqes brady diarrhktes ktyphsan kentriko taxydromiko grafeio sto Strobolo,
para ta ejwterika iatreia.
<P>Oi drastes eishlqan sto ktirio apo mikro paraqyro kai prospaqhsan
anepityxws na anoijoyn to xrhmatokibwtio ktypwntas to me baria ergaleia kai
lostoys.
<P>Wstoso, apo grafeio sto opoio yphrxan nomismata, grammatoshma kai omologies
ajias endeka xiliadwn lirwn, eklecan kermata ajias penhnta lirwn.
<P>Th diarrhjh diapistwse ypallhlos toy taxydromeioy, o opoios anefere oti
sto xrhmatokibwtio yphrxan alles treis xiliades lires tis opoies eixe
aposteilei sto kentriko taxydromeio.
<P>To idio brady diepraxqhkan alles treis diarrhjeis se isariqma katasthmata
sth Leykwsia.
<HR>
Oloklhrwnoyme to deltio mas me thn prognwsh gia ton kairo.
<P>Apoce kata diasthmata oi nefwseis qa pyknwnoyn kai anamenontai topikes
broxes kai piqano katiagides. Oi anemoi qa einai boreioanatolikoi ws
boreioi asqeneis 3 Mpofor kai stis perioxes twn kataigidwn eymetablhtoi
dynatoi mexri 5 Mpofor. H qalassa qa einai ligo taragmenh kai stis
proshnemes perioxes mexri taragmenh. H qermokrasia qa pesei stoys ennea
baqmoys sto eswteriko kai gyrw stoys 11 sta paralia.
<P>Ayrio topikes nefwseis anamenetai kai pali na dwsoyn topikes broxes kai
piqano memonwmenes kataigides. Oi anemoi qa einai to prwi boreioanatolikoi
asqeneis, 3 Mpofor kai to apogeyma notioanatolikoi ws notioi asqeneis mexri
metrioi 3-4 Mpofor. H qalassa qa einai ligo taragmenh kai topika mexri
taragmenh. H qermokrasia qa anelqei stoys 19 peripoy baqmoys.
<P>Shmera sth Leykwsia h pio chlh qermokrasia htan 18 baqmoi kai h pio xamhlh
9, sthn Ammoxwsto kai th Larnaka 19 me 11, sth Lemeso 21 me 12, sthn
Keryneia kai thn Pafo 20 me 10, kai telos ston Prodromo 11 me
4.
<HR>
