<H2>Logos News from Cyprus, 96-12-21</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/cyprus/logos">Logos News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-20.logos.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-22.logos.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: LogosNet at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.logos.cy.net">http://www.logos.cy.net</A>&gt;</H4>
<HR>
<P>Sto Symboylio Asfaleias twn Hnwmenwn Eqnwn, synexizontai apo xqes brady oi
diaboyleyseis panw se prosxedio chfismatos, sxetika me thn ananewsh ths
qhteias ths OYNFIKYP, oi opoies qa oloklhrwqoyn th Deytera.
<P>Opws egnwsqh ek meroys twn Hnwmenwn Politeiwn askoyntai pieseis gia na
diatypwqei sto chfisma h anhsyxia toy Symboylioy gia thn anabaqmish toy
ejoplistikoy programmatos ths Eqnikhs Froyras.
<P>Symfwna de diplwmatikoys kykloys, Hnwmenes Politeies kai Bretania,
klimakwnoyn tis pieseis toys, wste na symperilhfqei sto sxedio chfismatos,
paragrafos sthn opoia na ekfrazetai emmesa h anhsyxia toy Swmatos, gia thn
agora toy Rwsikoy pyraylikoy systhmatos ES 300.
<P>Wstoso meta apo entones Rwsikes antidraseis kai diafwnia ths Gallias, sto
chfisma qa ginetai mneia mono se eisagwgh ypersygxronwn oplikwn
systhmatwn.
<P>Sto sxedio chfismatos katagrafontai oi ektimhseis ths ekqeshs toy
aperxomenoy Genikoy Grammatea twn Hnwmenwn Eqnwn sxetika me tis pthseis kai
thn ayjhsh twn ejoplismwn, kaqws kai h dysforia toy gia thn adynamia twn
dyo pleyrwn, na symfwnhsoyn se metra apoklimakwshs ths entashs sthn grammh
antiparatajhs.
<P>Apodokimazontai epishs ta tragika gegonota toy perasmenoy Aygoystoy sto
odofragma ths Deryneias, xwris wstoso na ginetai katamerismos
eyqynwn.
<HR>
To programma ths amyntikhs qwrakishs ths Kyproy den exei parekklinei apo
toys arxikoys sxediasmoys, para tis opoiesdhpote pieseis h enstaseis.
<P>Ayto synagetai apo dhlwseis toy Ypoyrgoy Amynhs Kwsta Hliadh, kata th
diarkeia episkechs toy, se stratiwtikes egkatastaseis ston Pyrgo Thllyrias,
sthn Pafo.
<P>Ton kyrio Hliadh synodeyan o Arxhgos ths Eqnikhs Froyras, Antistrathgos
Nikolaos Borbolakos kai melh ths Epitrophs Amynas ths Boylhs.
<P>O Proedros ths Epitrophs Takhs Xatzhdhmhtrioy ekfrazontas thn ikanopoihsh
ths Epitrophs gia to epipedo ths amyntikhs qwrakishs ths Thllyrias,
anaferqhke sthn askhsh piesewn pros thn Kybernhsh ek meroys twn twn
Amerikanwn kai twn Bretanwn.
<P>H Kypriakh Dhmokratia, epeshmane o kyrios Xatzhdhmhtrioy, exei kaqe
dikaiwma na probainei stoys ejoplismoys poy qewrei anagkaioys gia th dikh
ths amyna kai kaythriase to gegonos o dieqnhs paragontas den antedrase otan
o Ntentkas kai to kaqestws toy, metetrecan ta katexomena edafh se
stratokratoymena.
<HR>
Yparxoyn ola ta stoixeia gia lysh toy kypriakoy, eipe o Amerikanos bohqos
Ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn, Tzwn Kornmploym, kanontas ton ethsio apologismo toy,
prosqetontas oti ayto poy apomenei, einai h apofash apo meroys twn
endiaferomenwn pleyrwn, oti exei fqasei h stigmh gia thn prowqhsh
lyshs.
<P>Parallhla, o kyrios Kornmploym epeshmane oti o Bretanos Ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn
Malkolm Rifkint edwse oysiastikh wqhsh sto kypriako.
<P>Apo pleyras twn Hnwmenwn Politeiwn, prosqese o Amerikanos ajiwmatoyxos, qa
ekdhlwqei energoterh drash, molis dioristei h nea omada eqnikhs asfaleias
ths amerikanikhs kybernhshs.
<HR>
Efqase prin apo ligo apo to Londino o Proedros toy Dhmokratikoy Synagermoy
Giannakhs Matshs, o opoios eixe ypoblhqei se parakampthrio egxeirhsh
arthriwn sto nosokomeio Xammersmiq.
<P>Ton kyrio Matsh o opoios synodeyeto apo thn syzygo toy, ypodexqhkan sto
aerodromio Larnakas o Anaplhrwths Proedros toy DHSY Nikos Anastasiadhs kai
alla anwtera stelexh toy kommatos.
<P>Se dhlwseis toy o kyrios Matshs, anefere oti qa epanalabei ta kaqhkonta toy
meta to telos Ianoyarioy.
<P>DHLWSH
<HR>
.O Proedros toy Kommatos Giannakhs Matshs htan o stoxos twn antartwn toy
Dhmokratikoy Synagermoy.
<P>Sthn apokalych ayth proebh o Anaplhrwths Proedros toy DHSY Nikos
Anastasiadhs, me dhlwseis toy ston Logo, klhqeis na sxoliasei thn
apeiqarxia stelexwn stis apofaseis toy kommatos gia tis dhmotikes
ekloges.
<P>Ayto diemhnyqh ston idio, opws apekalyce o kyrios Anastsiadhs.
<P>Anaforika me tis eyqynes poy epirriptoyn stelexh sthn hgesia kai ston idio
proswpika gia thn apotyxia sthn eklogh dhmarxwn se paradosiakoys dhmoys toy
Dhmokratikoy Synagermoy, o kyrios Anastasiadhs, tonise oti se kammia
periptwsh den eyqynetai h hgesia.
<P>Dieykrinise wstoso, oti ean h Politikh Epitroph toy Kommatos ektimhsei to
antiqeto, o idios einai etoimos na paraithqei.
<P>En tw metajy h Eparxiakh Epitroph toy DHSY Lemesoy taxqhke yper ths
tropopoihshs toy syntagmatos gia apofygh anaplhrwmatikhs ekloghs gia
plhrwsh ths kenwqeisas boyelytikhs edras.
<P>H apofash elhfqh se xqesinobradynh synedria ths Epitrophs paroysia toy
kyrioy Anastasiadh..
<HR>
Poreia ananewshs, anasygkrothshs alla kai dieyrynshs toy Dhmokratikoy
Kommatos proanhggeile o Proedros toy Spyros Kyprianoy enocei toy
Pagkyprioy Synedrioy poy qa pragmatopoihqei telika stis enteka
Maioy.
<P>H apofash lhfqhke omofwna kata thn diarkeia ths shmerinhs synedrias toy
Ektelestikoy Grafeioy.
<P>O kyrios Kyprianoy anefere oti anoigoyn oi portes toy kommatos se nea melh
ta opoia ews thn pragmatopoihsh toy synedrioy qa exoyn to dikaiwma toy
eklegein kai eklegesqai.
<P>En tw metajy, to Ektelestiko Grafeio asxolhqhke epishs me to qema ths
ekloghs antidhmarxwn kai apofasise na paraxwrhsei aytonomia stis
eparxiakes epitropes na xeiristoyn to qema se synergasia me toys
dhmotikoys symboyloys toy kommatos.
<HR>
Ws sobarh alla ektos kindynoy, perigrafetai h katastash ths ygeias toy
eqnofroyroy Panagiwth Pitrakkoy apo ton Agio Dometio, o opoios
traymatisqhke apo sfaira sthn aristerh katw koiliakh xwra, se Stratopedo
Pyrobolikoy ths Eqnikhs Froyras.
<P>O dekaenniaxronos eqnofroyros o opoios noshleyetai sto Geniko Nosokomeio
Leykwsias ypoblhqhke se xeiroyrgikh epembash.
<P>Opws egnwsqh, ligh wra afotoy o Pitrakkos epestrece sth monada toy apo
adeia dianyktereyshs, akoysthke enas pyrobolismos, gegonos to opoio ek
prwths ocews, fainetai oti prokeitai gia aytotraymatismo.
<P>To Geniko Epiteleio Eqnikhs Froyras, dietaje thn diejagwgh anakrisewn gia
tis synqhkes traymatismoy toy eqnofroyroy.
<HR>
Xilies ejakosies dekaennea kitrines kordeles deqhkan sto Xristoygenniato
dentro to opoio topoqethqhke ston xwro toy Odofragmatos toy Lhdra Palas,
panw stis opoies anagrafontan ta onomata twn agnooymenwn.
<P>H symbolikh ayth xeironomia entassotan sto plaisio twn antikatoxikwn
ekdhlwsewn oi opoies pragmatopoioyntai kaqe Sabbatokyriako sto odofragma
gia diafwtish twn jenwn perihghtwn.
<P>Ektos apo syggeneis agnooymenwn kai melh kai stelexh toy Pagkyprioy
Antikatoxikoy Kinhmatos, sto odofragma edwsan to paron toys shmera kai ta
melh toy Prosfygikoy Swmateioy Assiwtwn kai ths Epitrophs Allhleggyhs pros
toys Egklwbismenoys.
<P>Se omilies toys oi epikefalhs twn swmateiwn poy symmeteixan sthn ekdhlwsh
ejefrasan thn apaithsh gia swsth diereynhsh ths tyxhs enos ekastoy twn
agnooymenwn.
<HR>
Sto Peroy, oi antartes toy kinhmatos Toypak Amaroy, ejakoloyqoyn na exoyn
ypo ton elegxo toys to ktirio ths Iapwnikhs Presbeias sth Lima, kratwntas
peri ta 350 atoma ws omhroys.
<P>Xqes brady oi antartes apeleyqerwsan akomh 38 omhroys, metajy twn opoiwn
kai oi presbeytes ths Brazilias, ths Notioy Koreas kai ths Aigyptoy.
<P>Ej'alloy, h Peroybianh Thleorash metedwse shmera binteotainia, sthn opoia
fainontai oi antartes, na proetoimazontai gia thn epixeirhsh katalhchs ths
Iapwnikhs Presbeias.
<P>Sth binteotainia poy estalh apo toys antartes, fainetai enas maskoforos, o
opoios deixnei gyrw apo ena trapezi se alloys, mia maketa ths katoikias
toy Iapwna presbeyth.
<P>Apo thn binteotainia diafainetai epishs oti o maskoforos einai o hgeths toy
kinhmatos Toypak Amaroy, Nestor Tserpa Kartolini.
<HR>
Ton kanoniko ths ryqmo arxise na janabriskei h Ellada meta thn apofash ths
syntonistikhs epitrophs Agrotwn Makedonias-Qrakhs na anasteilei tis
kinhtopoihseis en'ocei twn Xristoygennwn.
<P>Ta mploka twn agrotwn ena meta to allwn dialyontai h xalarwnoyn, enw mono
sth Qessalia oi agrotes epimenoyn sth synexish kinhtopoihsewn.
<P>En tw metajy th Deytera o Prwqypoyrgos Kwstas Simhths qa exei synanthseis
me ekproswpoys twn agrotwn.
<P>Apokatasthmenh plhrws einai kai h kinhsh sta Limania meta thn apofash kai
twn naytikwn na anasteiloyn thn apergia.
<HR>
Oloklhrwnoyme to deltio mas me thn prognwsh gia ton kairo.
<P>Apoce o kairos qa einai merikws synnefiasmenos me endexomeno na pesoyn
merikes topikes broxes. Oi anemoi qa einai boreiodytikoi sqeneis 2 ews
tria Mpofor kai h qalassa qa einai ligo taragmenh. H qermokrasia qa pesei
tis aygines wres stoys 9 baqmoys sto eswteriko kai stoys 12 baqmoys sta
paralia.
<P>Ayrio o kairos qa einai kyriws aiqrios me parodikes nefwseis kata
diasthmata. Oi anemoi qa einai dytikoi ws notiodytikoi metrioi 3 ws 4
Mpofor. H qermokrasia qa anelqei stoys 19 baqmoys sto eswteriko kai stoys
21 sta paralia.
<P>Shmera, sth Leykwsia h pio chlh qermokrasia htan 18 baqmoi kai h pio xamhlh
8, sthn Ammoxwsto kai th Larnaka 20 me 11, sth Lemeso 21 me 14, sthn
Keryneia kai thn Pafo 20 me 11 kai telos ston Prodromo 9 me 5.
<P>.
<HR>
