<HEAD>
<TITLE>Logos News from Cyprus, 96-12-22</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<center><a href="/info"><IMG SRC="/gifs/hrnet.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="[HR-Net Banner]"></a><BR></center>

<H2>Logos News from Cyprus, 96-12-22</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/cyprus/logos">Logos News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-21.logos.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-23.logos.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: LogosNet at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.logos.cy.net">http://www.logos.cy.net</A>&gt;</H4>
<HR>
H kentrikh idea ths neas strathgikhs ths Ellhnikhs kybernhshs gia to
Kypriako, einai oti h Toyrkia qa synainesei sth lysh toy problhmatos, mono
otan diapistwsei oti den mporei na epityxei toys stoxoys ths sthn Kypro,
kai oti qa pollaplasiazontai ta problhmata poy antimetwpizei stis sxeseis
ths, me thn Eyrwph.
<P>Symfwna me dhmosieyma ths Aqhnaikhs efhmeridas &quot;To Bhma", h qesh ayth
periexetai se makroskelh eishghsh poy etoimasan o Yfypoyrgos Ejwterikwn
Xristos Rozakhs kai o Ekproswpos ths Elladas sthn diakybernhtikh,
eyrwboyleyths Giannos Kranidiwths.
<P>H eishghsh paroysiasthke thn perasmenh Trith se mia apo tis shmantikoteres,
symfwna me thn efhmerida, syskeceis gia to Kypriako ypo thn proedria toy
Prwqypoyrgoy Kwsta Shmith, me thn symmetoxh toy Ypoyrgoy Ejwterikwn
Qeodwroy Pagkaloy kai toy Anaplhrwth Ypoyrgoy Ejwterikwn Giwrgoy
Papandreoy.
<P>Symfwna me thn ekqesh h opoia egine dekth sto synolo ths xwris epifylajeis,
h Aqhna yioqetei gia prwth fora rhta thn qesh, oti an h Agkyra yioqethsei
mia pio paragwgikh qesh, dikaioytai na exei synolika pio eynoikh
antimetwpish, apo thn Eyrwpaikh Enwsh.
<P>H diplh ayth proseggish qa parei toys epomenoys mhnes thn morfh
sygkekrimenwn prwtoboyliwn ths Aqhnas, pros oles tis emplekomenes
pleyres.
<P>Sthn eishghsh ekfrazetai h ektimhsh oti to etos poy qa shmatodothsei thn
strofh sth lysh toy Kypriakoy qa einai to 1998, opote kai qa dromologhqoyn
oi diadikasies oysiastikoy dialogoy.
<P>Symfwna me to idio dhmosieyma, ta deka shmeia Rifkint ekanan kalh entypwsh
sthn Aqhna, h opoia ta qewrei xrhsima, gia ton epomeno kyklo
syzhthsewn.
<HR>
To dogma toy eniaioy amyntikoy xwroy apotelei syndyasmenh prospaqeia twn
enoplwn dynamewn ths Elladas kai ths Kyproy gia thn enisxysh twn
apotreptikwn dynatothtwn toys, dhlwse o Ypoyrgos Eqnikhs Amynhs Akhs
Tzoxatzopoylos.
<P>Se synenteyjh, poy dhmosieyetai shmera sthn Kyriakatikh Aqhnaikh efhmerida
Eleyqerotypia, o kyrios Tzoxatzopoylos tonizei oti to Kypriako apotelei
dieqnes problhma eisbolhs kai katoxhs apo thn Toyrkia, tmhmatos toy edafoys
ths Kypriakhs Dhmokratias.
<P>Epishmainei epishs oti h anaqewrhtikh politikh poy efarmozei h Toyrkia sth
Qrakh, to Aigaio kai thn Kypro, ypoxrewnei thn Ellada se yperogkes
amyntikes dapanes, gia na ejasfalisei thn anagkaia stratiwtikh
yperoxh.
<P>Anaferomenos sth stash ths dieqnoys koinothtas enanti twn eqnikwn mas
qematwn, o kyrios Tzoxatzopoylos dhlwnei oti den einai aisiodojos, afoy thn
politikh kaqorizoyn ta oikonomika symferonta kai oxi to dieqnes
dikaio.
<HR>
Meta apo eikosipente hmeres termatisthkan to prwi oi kinhtopoihseis twn
agrotwn sthn Ellada.
<P>H kykloforia arxise na apokaqistatai se olh th xwra, epeita apo thn
apoxwrhsh twn agrotwn kai th metakinhsh twn gewrgikwn elkysthrwn kai
mhxanhmatwn apo ta odofragmata stis kyrioteres eqnikoys odoys.
<P>Wstoso, oi agrotes diemhnysan sthn Kybernhsh oti an den epilyqoyn ta
problhmata toys, qa epanelqoyn sta odofragmata meta tis giortes.
<P>Apo thn pleyra ths h Kybernhsh dia toy prwqypoyrgoy Kwsta Shmith, se mia
prospaqeia ejeyreshs lyshs, qa exei synanthsh ayrio me thn hgesia twn
agrotwn.
<P>Dedomenhs, wstoso, ths topoqethshs toy kyrioy Shmith, kata thn diarkeia ths
syzhthshs twn proypologismwn, oti den yparxoyn periqwria paroxwn, qewreitai
poly dyskolo na breqei h xrysh tomh sthn ayrianh synanthsh.
<HR>
Proklhtikoi oi andres ths Eirhneytikhs Dynamhs prospaqhsan shmera na
fwtografisoyn kryfa toys motosykletistes poy symmeteixan se antikatoxikh
ekdhlwsh, sto odofragma toy Lhdra Palas.
<P>H adikaiologhth energeia prokalese dynamikh apanthsh kai afairesh toy film
apo thn fwtografikh mhxanh.
<P>Logw toy epeisodioy poy prokalesan oi andres ths eirhneytikhs dynamhs, sto
odofragma parathrhqhke entonh kinhtikothta ths Oynfikyp kai ths
Astynomias.
<P>Sto xwro toy odofragmatos edwsan to paron toys ektos apo ta melh kai
stelexh toy Pagkyprioy Antikatoxikoy Kinhmatos kai prosfyges apo to
katexomeno xwrio Assia.
<P>Sthn plateia Eleyqerias, ejalloy, oi syggeneis twn agnooymenwn esthsan
dentro me 1619 kitrines kordeles, gia na qymizei thn tragikoterh ptyxh toy
kypriakoy dramatos.
<HR>
H apoysia stenografoy sto Eparxiako Dikasthrio Lemesoy, htan o logos
anabolhs ths diadikasias ekdoshs diatagmatos krathshs triwn ypoptwn gia
katoxh kai emporia narkwtikwn.
<P>Oi ypoptoi qa epanaprosaxqoyn sto Dikasthrio ayrio gia ta peraiterw.
<P>Prokeitai gia ton Giwrgo Panagiwtoy 21 xronwn, sthn katoxh toy opoioy
breqhke ena kilo xasis kai toys Iwshf Giagkoy kai Niko Xaralampoys, oloi
apo th Lemeso.
<HR>
Apopeiraqhke na kacei to spiti twn peqerikwn toy, epeita apo entonh
logomaxia poy eixe me th syzygo toy.
<P>Ejerxomenos ktyphse sthn porta kai katelhje sto nosokomeio me sobaro
traymatismo sto xeri.
<P>Prokeitai gia ton Albino Zampa apo th Lemeso, o opoios synelhfqh me
dikastiko entalma kai froyreitai.
<P>Opws egnwsqh o Zampas metebh sto spiti twn peqerikwn toy ligo meta ta
mesanykta, afoy espase th jylinh eisodo.
<P>Akoloyqws klwtshse anammenh qermastra gkazioy, prokalwntas pyrkagia thn
opoian katesbesan argotera andres ths pyrosbestikhs yphresias.
<HR>
Epikindynh troph, elabe h ypoqesh ths synexizomenhs katalhchs ths Iapwnikhs
Presbeias sth Lima toy Peroy, meta thn arnhsh toy Proedroy ths xwras,
Almperto Foytzimori na proselqei se dialogo me toys katalhcies.
<P>Se thleoptiko diaggelma toy, o peroybianos Proedros, katasthse safes, oti h
kybernhsh toy, emmenei sthn apofash ths na aporriptei xwris syzhthsh ta
opoia aithmata twn antartwn, kai ayto para tis apeiles toys, oti qa
ektelesoyn toys omhroys.
<P>O Foytzimori, dieykrinise oti h monh odos gia thn epilysh ths krishs,
einai h apeleyqerwsh olwn twn omhrwn, kai h -aney orwn- paradosh twn
antartwn.
<P>Pantws, o peroybianos Proedros, paresxe stoys syggeneis twn omhrwn th
diabebaiwsh, oti oi eidikes dynameis ths Astynomias poy exoyn perikyklwsei
to ktirio, den prokeitai na epixeirhsoyn thn katalhch toy.
<HR>
Neo kyklo epafwn me ton israhlino Ypoyrgo Ejwterikwn Ntabint Lebi kai ton
palaistinio hgeth Giaser Arafat, egkainiase shmera o eidikos apestalmenos
twn Hnwmenwn Politeiwn gia to Mesananatoliko Ntenis Ros.
<P>Sto epikentro twn synomiliwn toy amerikanoy ajiwmatoyxoy, brisketai to
zhthma ths anaqermanshs toy eirhneytikoy dialogoy, o opoios exei perielqei
se plhres adiejodo, kyriws logw ths stashs poy threi h israhlinh
kybernhsh.
<P>Thn idia wra, sth Xebrwna, dekades palaistinioi sygkroysthkan me thn
Israhlinh Astynomia.
<P>Oi taraxes arxisan otan palaistinioi erican dyo bombes molotwf, enantion
oikias Ebraiwn sthn polh, xwris wstoso na proklhqoyn qymata h
zhmies.
<HR>
Oloklhrwnoyme to deltio mas me thn prognwsh gia ton kairo.
<P>Apoce qa emfanizontai parodikes nefwseis poy endexetai na dwsoyn merikes,
topikes broxes. Oi anemoi qa einai dytikoi, metrioi 3 ews 4 Mpofor kai h
qalassa qa einai taragmenh stis proshnemes perioxes. H qermokrasia qa pesei
stoys 7 baqmoys sto eswteriko kai stoys 9 sta paralia.
<P>Ayrio qa emfanizontai kai pali parodikes nefwseis. Oi anemoi qa einai
notiodytikoi metrioi 3 ews 4 mpofor kai h qalassa qa einai kai pali
taragmenh stis proshnemes perioxes. H qermokrasia qa anelqei stoys 19
baqmoys sto eswteriko kai stoys 21 sta paralia.
<P>Shmera sthn Leykwsia h pio chlh qermokrasia htan 20 baqmoi kai h pio xamhlh
8, sthn Ammoxwsto kai thn Larnaka 21 me 10, sthn Lemeso 22 me 15, sthn
Keryneia kai thn Pafo 21 me 11 kai telos ston Prodromo 10 me 4.
<HR>
<H4>From the LogosNet Server at <A HREF="http://www.logos.cy.net">http://www.logos.cy.net</A></H4>
