<H2>European Commission Spokesman's Briefing for 96-12-19</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/europe/midex">Midday Express: News from the EU Commission Spokesman's Briefings</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-18.midex.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-20.midex.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: EUROPA, the European Commission Server at &lt;<A HREF="http://europa.eu.int">http://europa.eu.int</A>&gt;</H4>

<H4>MIDDAY EXPRESS</H4>
<H4>News from the Spokesman's midday briefing</H4>
<H4>Nouvelles du rendez-vous de midi du Porte-Paroleb</H4>
<H4>19/12/1996</H4>
<HR>
<H3>CONTENTS / CONTENU</H3>
  <H4><A HREF="#I">[I]</A> Rsultats de la Commission du 18 dcembre -Outcome of Commission
meeting of 18 December</H4>
