<H2>European Commission Spokesman's Briefing for 96-12-20</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/europe/midex">Midday Express: News from the EU Commission Spokesman's Briefings</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-19.midex.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="97-01-07.midex.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: EUROPA, the European Commission Server at &lt;<A HREF="http://europa.eu.int">http://europa.eu.int</A>&gt;</H4>

<H4>MIDDAY EXPRESS</H4>
<H4>News from the Spokesman's midday briefing</H4>
<H4>Nouvelles du rendez-vous de midi du Porte-Paroleb</H4>
<H4>20/12/1996</H4>
