<H2>Logos News from Cyprus, 96-12-18</H2>
<H5><A HREF="/news/cyprus/logos">Logos News in ASCII Greek</A> Directory - <A HREF="96-12-17.logos.html">Previous Article</A> - <A HREF="96-12-19.logos.html">Next Article</A></H5>
<H4>From: LogosNet at &lt;<A HREF="http://www.logos.cy.net">http://www.logos.cy.net</A>&gt;</H4>
<HR>
<P>Istorikh xarakthrise, o Genikos Eisaggeleas ths Dhmokratias, Alekos
Markidhs, thn katadikastikh gia thn Toyrkia, apofash toy Eyrwpaikoy
Dikasthrioy Anqrwpinwn Dikaiwmatwn, sthn periptwsh ths prosfyghs ths
Titinas Loizidoy.
<P>Opws einai gnwsto, h Titina Loizidoy prosefyge, meta apo nomikh symboylh
ths Nomikhs Yphresias toy kratoys, sto Eyrwpaiko Dikasthrio Anqrwpinwn
Dikaiwmatwn, zhtwntas katadikh ths Toyrkias, h opoia ths afairese to
dikaiwma xrhshs kai prosbashs sthn perioysia ths, sta katexomena.
<P>H shmasia ths apofashs, kata ton Geniko Eisaggelea, alla kai symfwna me ton
dikhgoro ths kyrias Loizidoy, Axillea Dhmhtriadh, egkeitai triwn
stoixeiwn:
<P>Prwton, oti h Toyrkia einai ypeyqynh gia to ti symbainei sto katexomeno
tmhma ths Kyproy,
<P>deyteron, oti to ceydokratos den exei kamia apolytws nomikh isxy,
<P>kai triton, oti ta nomika dikaiwmata twn politwn ths Kypriakhs Dhmokratias
isxyoyn, anejarthtws politikwn h stratiwtikwn ejelijewn.
<P>O Genikos Eisaggeleas tonise, oti h prosfygh einai atomikh, enw
jekaqaristhke oti, h kyria Loizidoy den epizhtei mono apozhmiwseis, alla
kai thn efarmogh toy dikaiwmatos xrhshs kai prosbashs sthn perioysia ths,
sthn katexomenh Keryneia.
<P>O Proedros Klhridhs xarakthrise thn apofash ws megalh epityxia kai ejefrase
thn ektimhsh oti mporei na exei terastio antiktypo sto Kypriako, dedomenoy
oti xiliades nomimoi kai monimoi idiokthtes perioysiwn sta katexomena
anagkasthkan apo ton toyrkiko strato na tis egkataleicoyn.
<HR>
Xwris allages proxwrei to ejoplistiko programma ths Eqnikhs Froyras.
<P>To Eqniko Symboylio kai h Epitroph Amynas ths Boylhs enhmerwqhkan to prwi
sto G.E.E.F. apo toys stratiwtikoys empeirognwmones kai to Ypoyrgeio
Oikonomikwn gia tis anagkes ths Eqnikh Froyras.
<P>O Proedros ths Dhmokratias Glaykos Klhridhs dhlwse meta th syskech oti
egine plhrhs enhmerwsh anaforika me th shmerinh katastash ths Eqnikhs
Froyras kai epejhghqh to epomeno pentaetes programma.
<P>O proypologismos, prosqese, exei paei sth Boylh kai ean ginoyn allages qa
ejarthqei apo thn armodia koinoboyleytikh epitroph. Ekeino to opoio qa
egkriqei katelhje qa einai to neo ejoplistiko programma to opoio kai qa
ylopoihqei kanonika.
<HR>
Qetika kai arnhtika stoixeia stis protaseis toy Bretanoy Ypoyrgoy
Ejwterikwn Malkom Rifkint diapistwnei o Proedros ths Dhmokratias.
<P>O Proedros Klhridhs apofeygontas na prosdiorisei ta arnhtika stoixeia sto
dekalogo Rifkint eipe oti ta apotelesmata ths episkechs toy Bretanoy
Ypoyrgoy Ejwterikwn qa fanoyn argotera, ean kai otan arxisoyn oi
diapragmateyseis.
<P>En tw metajy, diabebaiwseis oti h Kypriakh Kybernhsh den anelabe
opoiesdhpote desmeyseis, kata thn diarkeia ths episkechs Rifkint, phre o
Proedros toy Dhmokratikoy Kommatos Spyros Kyprianoy, o opoios synanthqhke
to prwi sto Proedriko me ton Proedro Klhridh.
<HR>
O Ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn ths Ellados Qeodwros Pagkalos synantatai shmera sto
Londino me ton Bretano omologo toy Malkom Rifkint.
<P>H synanthsh proslambanei idiaitero endiaferon afoy pragmatopoieitai dyo
molis meres meta thn episkech toy Bretanoy Ypoyrgoy sthn Kypro, kai thn
ypobolh twn deka shmeiwn - protasewn toy gia to Kypriako.
<P>Opws ektimoyn politikoi parathrhtes, o kyrios Pagkalos qa metaferei ston
Malkom Rifkint, thn kaqeth diafwnia ths Aqhnas, epi toy sygkekrimenoy
shmeioy twn protasewn, to opoio pronoei thn entajh ths Kyproy sthn
Eyrwpaikh Enwsh, meta thn epilysh toy Kypriakoy.
<P>O Ypoyrgos Ejwterikwn ths Ellados, anamenetai na syzhthsei me ton Bretano
omologo toy, en ektasei, kai ta ypoloipa ennea shmeia twn protasewn.
<P>Peran toy Kypriakoy, sth synanthsh Rifkint - Pagkaloy, anamenetai na teqoyn
oi legomenes ellhnotoyrkikes diafores, kaqws kai oi dimereis sxeseis
Ellados - Hnwmenoy Basileioy.
<P>Milwntas sto dialeimma twn synomiliwn, o Bretanos Ypoyrgos, apedwse toys
foboys toys opoioys eixe diatypwsei, xqes, gia to Kypriako, sta gegonota
toy kalokairioy kai epanelabe thn anhsyxia toy gia thn katastash sthn
Kypro.
<P>O kyrios Rifkint, xarakthrise ejalloy, yperbolikh th paroysia saranta
xiliadwn Toyrkwn stratiwtwn sto nhsi.
<P>Oi synomilies synexizontai, enw argotera shmera, o kyrios Pagkalos, qa
synanthqei kai me ton skiwdh Ypoyrgo Ejwterikwn twn Bretanwn Ergatikwn
Rompin Koyk.
<HR>
Synelhfqh to prwi o Loizos Stayroy ebdomhnta epta xronwn, drasths ths
xqesinhs apopeiras fonoy, kata ths syzygoy toy Loyllas.
<P>O Loizoy entopisthke se ypogeio kinhmatografoy kai proshxqh enwpion toy
Eparxiakoy Dikasthrioy Lemesoy to opoio ejedwse enantion toy diatagma
krathshs oktw hmerwn.
<P>O drasths o opoios paradexqhke se kataqesh toy oti ktyphse th syzygo toy,
probale ton isxyrismo oti odhghqhke sto egklhma apo oikonomikes diafores
kai oti meta prospaqhse na qesei terma sth zwh toy.
<P>En tw metajy, krisimh paramenei h katastash ths Loyllas Stayroy, h opoia
noshleyetai sthn monada entatikhs parakoloyqhshs toy Genikoy Nosokomeioy
Leykwsias.
<HR>
Se tragwdia par' oligo na katalhjei laqrokynhgi lagwn sto eqniko parko
Aqalassas ta mesanykta.
<P>Sygkekrimena, dyo proswpa laqrokynhgoysan sthn kleisth gia to kynhgi
perioxh toy parkoy Aqalassas, xrhsimopoiwntas klemmeno oplo, probolea kai
jenh motosykletta.
<P>Wstoso, kata thn ejodo toys apo to parko, h astynomia h opoia eixe
eidopoihqei apo perioikoys, epexeirhse na toys anakocei.
<P>O odhgos ths motosykletas aneptyje taxythta kai sthn prospaqeia toy na
diafygei epepese biaia se staqmeymeno aytokinhto ths Astynomias.
<P>Apo th sygkroysh aneflegh h motosykleta, me apotelesma o enas laqrokynhgos
na ypostei sobara egkaymata, enw o allos katafere na diafygei kai
katazhteitai apo thn Astynomia.
<P>O syllhfqeis einai o Antwnhs Braximhs 27 xronwn, apo ton synoikismo
Strobolos dyo, o opoios noshleyetai sto Geniko Nosokomeio Leykwsias, me
egkaymata deyteroy baqmoy sto proswpo kai to swma kai me katagma sto
podi.
<P>Enas astynomikos ypesth elafra egkaymata sto xeri sthn prospaqeia toy na
sbhsei th fwtia sto Braximh.
<P>Logw ths sobarothtas ths ypoqeshs, th diereynhsh ths anelabe to TAE
Leykwsias.
<HR>
Sto Peroy antartes toy Epanastatikoy kinhmatos Toypak Amaroy katelaban to
brady thn katoikia toy Iapwna Presbh sthn prwteyoysa Lima, kratwntas ws
omhroys diakosia atoma.
<P>Sthn oikia  briskontan kai melh toy diplwmatikoy swmatos afoy paretiqeto
dejiwsh gia ta geneqlia toy Iapwna Aytokratora.
<P>Anamesa stoys  omhroys einai kai o Ellhnas  presbeyths sto Peroy Alkibiadhs
Karokhs, enw h gynaika toy afeqh eleyqerh.
<P>Oi antartes zhtoyn apo thn kybernhsh toy Peroy thn apeleyqerwsh
tetrakosiwn me pentakosiwn fylakismenwn synagwnistwn toys, perilambanomenoy
kai toy Biktwr Polai, hgetikoy stelexoys ths organwshs.
<P>Epishs zhtoyn thn anaqewrhsh toy dikastikoy systhmatos ths xwras.
<P>En tw metajy, opws mexri stigmhs egnwsqh, prin apo ligo shmeiwqhke isxyrh
ekrhjh sthn oikia toy Iapwna presbh kai akoloyqhsan pyrobolismoi.
<HR>
Xristoygenna makria apo toys goneis toys qa perasoyn allh mia fora paidia
egklwbismenwn.
<P>Oyte kai fetos o katoxikos hgeths qa epitrecei th metabash sta katexomena
twn paidiwn poy exoyn jeperasei to legomeno epitrepto orio hlikias, to
opoio einai ta 16 xronia gia ta agoria kai ta 18 gia ta koritsia.
<P>Wstoso, se mia teleytaia prospaqeia ta paidia twn egklwbismenwn qa
briskontai thn Paraskeyh sto Odofragma toy Lhdra Palas, me thn elpida oti
telika o katoxikos hgeths qa epideijei katanohsh se ayto to anqrwpistiko
qema, epitrepontas toys th metabash toys sta katexomena.
<P>En tw metajy shmera, h Ypoyrgos Paideias synanthqhke me paidia
egklwbismenwn kai syzhthse ta problhmata poy antimetwpizoyn stis eleyqeres
perioxes kai toys epedwse me thn eykairia twn Xrisotygennwn symbolika
dwra.
<HR>
Ayjanontai ta epidomata gia enoikiash spitiwn apo prosfyges kai paqontes
apo thn prwth toy neoy xronoy kata 10%.
<P>To kybernhtiko nomosxedio melethse h Epitroph Prosfygwn ths Boylhs, h
opoia wstoso apofasise na egkrinei ejamhniaia diarkeia toy sxedioy kai oxi
dieth opws htan h kybernhtikh protash.
<P>Synolika epidotoyntai 2,837 atoma me ena poso 128 xiliadwn lirwn to
xrono.
<P>Ta epidomata jekinoyn apo 39 lires kai fqanoyn tis 63 to mhna.
<P>Peraiterw, h Epitroph stoxeyei, symfwna me ton proedro ths, na piesei thn
kybernhsh na melethsei tropoys epidothshs twn newn zeygariwn ta opoia den
mporoyn na ejasfalisoyn stegh se kybernhtikoys oikismoys.
<P>Ejalloy, h Epitroph apofasise na synelqei thn erxomenh Deytera ektaktws gia
na melethsei thn proqesh toy Genikoy Grammatea toy OHE na khryjei 1000
agnooymenoys san nekroys.
<HR>
Oloklhrwnoyme to deltio mas me thn prognwsh gia ton kairo.
<P>Apoce o kairos qa einai kyriws aiqrios me parodikes nefwseis. Oi anemoi qa
einai boreioanatolikoi asqeneis 2-3 Mpofor kai h qalassa ligo taragmenh. H
qermokrasia qa pesei stoys 8 baqmoys sto eswteriko kai gyrw stoys 10 sta
paralia.
<P>Ayrio qa yparxoyn araies nefwseis oi opoies to apogeyma qa pyknwsoyn kai
dynato na dwsoyn liges broxes. Oi anemoi qa trapoyn stadiaka se
notioanatolikoys metrioys 3-4 Mpofor kai h qalassa qa parameinei ligo
taragmenh. H qermokrasia qa anelqei stoys 18 baqmoys sto eswteriko kai gyrw
stoys 20 sta paralia.
<P>Shmera sth Leykwsia h pio chlh qermokrasia htan 18 baqmoi kai h pio xamhlh
7, sthn Ammoxwsto kai thn Larnaka 19 me 10, sthn Lemeso 19 me 11, sthn
Keryneia kai thn Pafo 20 me 9 kai telos ston Prodromo 8 me 3.
<HR>
<H4>From the LogosNet Server at <A HREF="http://www.logos.cy.net">http://www.logos.cy.net</A></H4>
